en_US_description: Fashioned from summery Damier Azur canvas, this compact Victorine Wallet gives you a stylish way to carry your daily essentials. Tiny yet very functional, it has six credit cards slots, two pockets for receipts and a large pocket for non-folded bills.

This collectible piece features our iconic Petite Malle - a Louis Vuitton icon since Nicolas Ghesquière's first show. With delicate details that express the Maison's finest know-how, it can also be personalized with hot-stamped initials on its backside, making it the perfect gift.

The perfect summer companion, this effortlessly chic Girolata in Mahina calfskin is versatility incarnate. You can wear it in two ways, with the drawstring open, it can be carried as a large casual tote and without, it is an on-trend bucket bag.

The perfect summer companion, this effortlessly chic Girolata in Mahina calfskin is versatility incarnate. You can wear it in two ways, with the drawstring open, it can be carried as a large casual tote and without, it is an on-trend bucket bag.
This distinctive charm necklace reinterprets details of advertising posters from the Louis Vuitton archives in an uptown spirit inspired by the Fall/Winter 2017 men's show.

Eye-catching, isn’t it? The new Kimono tote combines Monogram canvas with fine calf leather for a riveting graphic effect. Why “Kimono”? The name alludes to the V-cross motif, inspired by the Japanese robe. In the purest tradition of House craftsmanship the bag features long Toron leather handles, a distinctive metallic V signature inspired by an historical advertising of the brand and impeccable edge-dyeing. Both roomy and remarkably light, the Kimono is a pleasure to carry.

Precious miniatures of the iconic padlock and key from our trunks tell the story of Louis Vuitton and the art of travel. The exquisite craftsmanship on a variety of materials -- metal, enamel and sparkly strass -- is a testament to the House's know-how.

An essential addition to any wardrobe, this elegant wool scarf is discreetly woven with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern. Finished with fringes, it is warm on one side and soft and silky on the other.
Ideal for casual and urban wear, this belt in supple calf leather features a new Western-inspired version of the iconic LV Initiales buckle.
Featuring the iconic LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt comes in two contrasting shades of supple and grained Taurillon leather, effectively offering two looks in one.

Featuring a colorful design and artistic drawings, this medium-format Agenda Refill includes daily poetry to accompany its owner throughout the year. This functional version contains only essential diary elements.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian authenticity for Fall-Winter 17 with this futuristic creation. The re-purposed Louis Vuitton Vs and the matte metallic touches offer a sporty and playful look for a new interpretation of the Palm Spring
Compact yet ample, in smart and elegant Epi leather, the new version of the Clémence Wallet is offered in playful and high-fashion shades.

Fashioned in Damier Graphite Canvas, the iPhone7 Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, hold the phone perfectly to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.
This classic business tie subtly references Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern with discreet Monogram motifs printed in lines within the stripes.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with bright red leather for a highly colored silhouette.
Featuring feminine round shapes, this elegant key holder combines historical Monogram Flowers and a distinctive "Louis" wire, tribute to Louis Vuitton himself.

A bag to fit any mood or silhouette, the new Cléry Pochette in Epi leather can be worn on the shoulder, cross-body (merci, adjustable strap) or carried by the finely detailed top handle. Surprisingly roomy, it is offered in a bouquet of fashionable shades.

This chic city bag marries exceptional style with flawless functionality. The V stitching signature on the strap and the contrast between sleek and grained leather bring refined elegance. But the large capacity – and quick access to personal belongings thanks to the back pocket – is what makes it a must-have daily companion.

In creating the Fragrance Travel Cases, Louis Vuitton applies its savoir-faire and mastery in custom-designing the perfect case for transporting and protecting each item of one’s personal belongings. The 100ML travel case conserves and protects your perfume bottle, closing securely with a buckle. Slip it into your bag in every situation.The 100ml travel case can also be personalized in store to the initials of your choice.

Inspired by the Hockenheim signature from our shoes collection, this wide, masculine bracelet's LV initials have been reworked inside a frame for a modern look. It is available in timeless colors that can be worn with any tone or outfit.
This playful pouch contains an elegant pack of Louis Vuitton playing cards. The perfect companion for a nomadic lifestyle, it features bright red leather and a contrasting lining for a playful look.
In deep navy blue Mahina leather, this Iris wallet is both refined and timeless. Crafted from sumptuously soft calfskin with a perforated Monogram design, it is as luxurious as it is functional.

Crafted of supremely supple Monogram Empreinte leather, the Ponthieu shoulder tote makes a stylish daily companion. Effortlessly chic (note the hoop detail on the handles and signature zip pulls), the roomy MM model provides ample space for essentials.
Ideal as a gift, this silk jacquard tie transforms Louis Vuitton's V motif into a graphic diamond pattern for a vibrant, modern look.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature, this elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

For the second time, Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 Fashion Show. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros and Elephant.

Proposed for the fist time in black smooth leather, the elegant EW size has been delicately embellished with bicolour metallic staples on its edges, as a tribute to couture stitches. This animation underlines the Louise EW sleek design & gives a rich twist to this evening essential. Louise EW Staples sublimates every evening looks thanks to its elegant hand-carry.

Effortlessly styllish thanks to the iconic Supreme logo features on the supple Epi leather, this clutch is for those who want an ultra-fashionable portfolio with which to transport documents, and other daily essentials.

This colorful silk bandeau reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers in a graphic, Japan-inspired spirit: "kamon" means coat-of-arms in Japanese. Featuring the iconic Monogram pattern on the reverse, it makes a perfect gift.
The Pallas is so much more than a chic bag. It’s an alluring fusion of Monogram canvas, natural cowhide leather trim and coloured calf leather, giving it a distinctive look and a very supple feel.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the POCHETTE VOYAGE MM combines both House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity with fine details -  two reflective bands and a black one, lozine edging, pocket stitching, colored Rainbow hardware - for a result both sporty and fashion. The Pochette Voyage MM can either slip into a bag or be carried by hand. Its generous volume thanks to the gusset will give you an easy access to all your belongings.

Inspired by the Amazon rainforest, this Twist Exotic Birds limited edition is adorned with a hummingbird motif, intricately embroidered in multi-colored sequins. Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 20 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

This modern stole features an eye-catching design of dynamic lines, bright colors and race numbers to evoke the America's Cup universe against a background of Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern. Its soft, lightweight blend of silk and cotton makes it ideal for mid-season temperatures.

Fresh and stylish for winter, the new Sunset accessory feature an allover Monogram Flowers motif in a modern gradiant effect. Knitted in a warm wool-cashmere blend, it's a perfect accessory  to protect from the cold

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

The perfect summer companion, this effortlessly chic Girolata in Mahina calfskin is versatility incarnate. You can wear it in two ways, with the drawstring open, it can be carried as a large casual tote and without, it is an on-trend bucket bag.

The LV League collection combines heritage labels with college-style patches inspired by Kim Jones' menswear shows. Fusing style and functionality, the District messenger bag is an ideal companion for every day.

Available in three colors that match the FW17 color range, this modern reinterpretation of the Monogram shawl will light up any winter outfit. Its eye-catching blurry design is inspired by set of lights.

Crafted from waxed calf leather, this new version of the Maison's iconic LV Initiales model is a perfect match for our LV Montaigne loafers. Available in two timeless colors, it will complement business suits and as well as more casual looks.

This colorful silk square reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers in a graphic, Japan-inspired spirit: "kamon" means coat-of-arms in Japanese. This elegant accessory will add a sophisticated, feminine touch to any outfit.

Crafted from waxed calf leather, this new version of the Maison's iconic LV Initiales model is a perfect match for our LV Montaigne loafers. Available in two timeless colors, it will complement business suits and as well as more casual looks.
Ideal for mid-season, this versatile wool and silk stole combines the iconic Monogram pattern with stripes in muted colors for a fashionable vintage look.

This colorful silk bandeau reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers in a graphic, Japan-inspired spirit: "kamon" means coat-of-arms in Japanese. Featuring the iconic Monogram pattern on the reverse, it makes a perfect gift.

With its two removable interior pockets, the Pochette Felicie in Epi leather is the stylish solution to carry and organize your daily essentials. Much more than a wallet, it can be transformed into a glamorous shoulder bag or clutch thanks to its removable silver chain.

The 2017 LV League collection reveals a tribute to Louis Vuitton history both past and present. It associates iconic labels inspired from Gaston-Louis Vuitton collection and college style ones.This Brazza wallet exudes playful sophistication. Its generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket.
Ideal for everyday use, this luxuriously soft Monogram Neo Denim shawl is subtle and very feminine. Entirely weaven in jacquard, it features the Louis Vuitton signature and the Monogram pattern.

Featuring a colorful design and artistic drawings, this medium-format Agenda Refill includes daily poetry to accompany its owner throughout the year. Extra features comprise a directory, traveler's guide and world map.

The Petite Malle Epi beautifully mixes Louis Vuitton craftsmanship with a bold, stylish statement. Reflecting the Maison’s heritage in trunk making, it is adorned with the crosses signature of world traveller Albert Kahn. Ageless and perfect for day to night chic. The Epi leather, historical heritage of the House, is reinterpreted in a modern and fashionable colour with studded Epi leather trimming.

Bearing all the hallmarks of the 35th America’s Cup Collection – oversized  new Damier Latitude canvas, historic “V Gaston” signature, regatta-red accents – this limited-edition toiletry bag is generously sized, to hold a man’s grooming gear in sporty style.

Inspired by the romantic vibe of Louis Vuitton's Spring/Summer 2017 fashion show, the Flower Lace theme transposes the collection's key lace story into an intricately crafted design on leather, incorporating Monogram Flowers and the LV Circle logo. Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the Pochette Voyage  created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the new Damier Coastline pattern, for a modern and fashion piece. You can slip the Pochette Voyage MM  into your bag as a travel pouch or hand carry it for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.
This envelope-style Sarah wallet combines an exterior in discreetly embossed Monogram Empreinte leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The Japanese-inspired Bento Box is the statement shape from Cruise 18. Crafted of classic Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas with leather trim and gleaming golden hardware, it features both a handle and a strap for hand, shoulder or cross-body wear.

In black leather with contrasting hot pink edge dyeing, this iconic wallet’s pure design gets a daring twist. Its well-organized functionalities make it the optimal answer for the vagaries of urban living.

Ideal to brighten up any look, this soft shawl in silk and wool is a study in versatility: highlight the plain part of the pattern for a more classic feel or feature the flower motif for a fancier occasion.

A must-have office accessory, this playful pencil pouch combines iconic Louis Vuitton signatures with an elegant look. Monogram canvas, VVN leather and the LV Circle motif add branded touches, while the color will brighten up your desk.

In time to bring a touch of delicate color to winter wardrobes, here is the Pochette Metis in new Rose Bruyère, a perfect shade of pink. Crafted of embossed Monogram Empreinte leather, it’s both practical and stylish: an ideal “go-to” bag for daily wear.

The Canyon briefcase in Utah calfskin features a mix of smooth and grained finishes, accented with double-stitching and aged-silver hardware. A light, compact business bag, it’s designed for convenience, with comfortable Toron handles and a removable strap.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. As practical as it is sophisticated, it fits comfortably into your pocket or handbag and holds credit cards, bills and papers.
An ideal gift, this adorable bag charm and key holder comes in luxurious mink, playfully adorned with tiny wings.

Make your Louis Vuitton bag your own with a peppy pop of colour thanks to this shoulder strap in Epi leather. Fun and versatile: it’s super easy to put on and remove thanks to the practical snap hook.

Available in a slimmer version, the Historic bracelet in Monogram Canvas is declined in two new hues of pink  as well as in the classic  Monogram canvas. Made to mix, match and stack, these signed pieces are perfect for gifting.

Smart and practical, the Jeanne Wallet in Monogram canvas offers endless possibilities. This envelop wallet in Monogram canvas is both ultra feminine and highly adaptable thanks to its three-in-one construction with removable card holder and coin pocket.

Fashioned in our new iconic black and grey Monogram Eclipse canvas, this resolutely masculine iPhone 7 Plus & 8 Plus Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface holds the phone perfectly in place to protect it.

Slim and sober, the iPhone 7 & 8 Folio has two inside flat pockets for daily essentials like business or credit cards. It easily fits in a pocket or a briefcase. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.
Matching our Leather Goods, this new belt suits both business silhouettes and more modern looks. The buckle features a sleek tone-on-tone plaque, with an LV logo adding a subtle signature.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with bright red leather for a highly colored silhouette.

The Palm Springs PM backpack gets a sophisticated new look thanks to Louis Vuitton’s feminine Matelasse Flower pattern: this delicate embroidery subtly reproduces the iconic Monogram flower on the bag’s ultra-soft black lambskin for a lightly quilted effect.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17 with this fresh take of the now-classic City Steamer, adorned with small studs on edges that highlight its architectural shape. This bag brings a fashionably edgy feel to any look.

Decorated with a print evoking the glamour of Louis Vuitton during the golden age of Transatlantic travel, this Zippy Wallet in coated canvas combines versatility, generous space and an all-round zip. It's perfect for carrying and organizing your daily essentials.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.
A playful piece that will create a playful wintry vibe to any silhouette. The design offers a new twist on the Monogram Flower motif, inspired by traditional winter jacquard pattern.
Ideal for jeans, this stylish belt in Monogram canvas features a new buckle finely engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature.

Easy chic silhouette maker, the Tournelle PM is a go-anywhere carryall for work and play. Thanks to the leather piping, its shape changes depending on whether you hold it by the handles or wear it over the shoulder with its long removable strap.

This fashionable Capucines BB is softened by a delicate and feminine cut inspired by the lace croquets technique. The chiseled edges, with a precious stud at their center, are inspired by the iconic Monogram Flower and by the nails on historic House Trunks.

The famous Louis Vuitton silk square becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a silk twill base embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

Woven of wool, silk and cashmere, the Storm stole wraps the wearer in softness and warmth. The design, linked to the Cruise show, is an artful take on camouflage motifs, in neutral black and white for ultimate wearability, with a contrasted “Louis Vuitton” signature on the bottom edge.

With its refined buckle in golden-finished brass, this sleek new belt pays tribute to the House's trunk-making ("Malletier") heritage. A  LV Circle detail at the end of the strap adds the finishing touch to a timeless and elegant accessory.

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 25 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

This statement ring extends our iconic alphabet motif to spell love, with a subtle nod to our emblematic LV initials. A perfect gift, this playful piece is embellished with trunk studs on the letters for an extra twist.
The stylish Ecu tie combines Petit Damier checks with a contrasting narrow stripe in shiny silk. It is finished with the LV initials in a discreet escutcheon.

Inspired by an imagined trip to Tahiti, this Neverfull MM in Monogram canvas brings new energy to classic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. The quintessence of the summer spirit, the bag’s design is completed by a manuscript ‘Knokke’ on the side.
This silk square captures the spirit of summer with its pattern of pink Monogram flowers as if hand-painted on a Damier Azur background. It is perfect to wear around the neck or in the hair.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian authenticity for Fall-Winter 17 with this futuristic version of the Speedy 25. Ideal for every day, this updated iconic bag offers an audacious style.

A contemporary take on the classic schoolbag, the updated Mylockme is a sleek, ultra-fashionable model crafted of soft, supple calf. Versatile and functional, with a well-organized interior, it can be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body.

This modern mask shape features an Essential V insert in the middle of the lens, a tribute to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton. The cylinder-shape temples, engraved with the Monogram design, complete the iconic style. Statement sunglasses for a wow effect, their mask shape is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. New shape specifically designed for this collection, the chain bag mixes iconic elements from the House (lock, envelop shape, leather patch) and specific signatures of the collaboration: a new chain, gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected/surprising collaboration.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature, this elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials.

With its distinctive shape and refined details, the Avenue Backpack in supple Damier Infini leather brings casual sophistication to any look. It's practical and keeps your belongings secure thanks to its zipped compartments.

Featuring an archive drawing that evokes Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this feminine key holder is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods. A perfect gift, it can be personalized with hot-stamped initials on its rear side.

The Multiple Wallet is ideal to hold credit cards, bills and receipts in a very compact format. The smart mix between Damier Graphite canvas and colored leather lining adds an extra veneer of sophistication.

This Zippy Organizer in Damier Ebène coated canvas, featuring a whimsical illustration of a zebra, is a study in playful elegance. Ideal for those who like everything in one place: it easily holds a checkbook, plane tickets, papers and pen.

Fashioned in Monogram coated canvas customized with Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquiere’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, this large toiletry pouch boasts a spacious interior and gusset sides for easy storage.

With their bubble shape and neon colors, these adorable bag charms are playful must-haves. Two feminine color options in luxurious mink fur will add a pop touch to any bag. Versatile, these "BB" size bag charms offer new usage and can be hooked to the zip-puller of a small Leather Good item.

Crafted in Monogram Savane canvas with a whimsy illustration of a zebra, this compact Multiple Wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts and slips easily into your pocket.  As stylish as it is functional.

With its easy-to-wear acetate design, this classic style will suit all wardrobes. Iconic studs evoke the Maison's historic trunks, while metallic Essential V inserts pay homage to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton.

Incomparably thin, this sophisticated Compact Wallet is fashioned from a mix of grained and smooth leather with double stitching. It’s compact enough to easily slip in the back pocket of a pair of jeans.The LV signature ton on ton makes it very refined and discreet.
The finishing touch for ultra-chic sophistication: this pure silk square with its modern take on our heritage, a trunks and luggage pattern, signed Louis Vuitton.

Incomparably thin, this Pocket Organizer with its mix of grained and smooth Utah leather, and double stitching, marries sophisticated style with easy functionality:  the perfect way to carry your credit cards and bills.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life. For those who love the Popincourt, the Pallas is another classic Monogram shoulder bag with a pop of color for your collection.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.

Designed in collaboration with Hiroshi Fujiwara, this graphic and trendy piece mixes urban codes with the Maison's emblematic Monogram Eclipse canvas to create a strong visual impact. Ideal for modern and edgy silhouettes. The plaque buckle is engraved with a Fragment Design logo.

A bag to fit any mood or silhouette, the new Cléry Pochette in Epi leather can be worn on the shoulder, cross-body (merci, adjustable strap) or carried by the finely detailed top handle. Surprisingly roomy, it is offered in a bouquet of fashionable shades.

Inspired by the iconic rabbit, often played by Jeff Koons in his work, this bag charm will spice up any Louis Vuitton bag thanks to its original shape and bright colours. Louis Vuitton’s refinement is expressed through the work of the metallic structure and the choice of the leather.

Must-have pieces for the Monogram lover, these statement accessories are engraved with our iconic pattern. The seasonal range includes an edgy thin cuff as well as a tie clip and cufflinks to complement business attires and our permanent  locket on charm necklace and signet ring.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. The Multiple wallet in Taiga leather is ideal for holding credit cards, bills and receipts.

A fashionable piece that will not go unnoticed, the arty Paint Splash stole is generous in size, to wear stylishly around the neck. The cotton-silk blend is soft and light, in an easy-going Navy or in a summery Light Grey.

The glamorous Pallas BB combines iconic Monogram canvas with colourful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colourful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.
The sporty Zack Backpack in coated canvas has a roomy interior and a classic Louis Vuitton look. The flap, drawstring closing, and metal buckle evoke so many the House classics.

The Malle Fleurs silk square was inspired by the Louis Vuitton tradition of sending flower-filled trunks to its best clients. Its feminine design features two open trunks amid a scattering of Monogram flowers and LV Circle logos.
The simple yet fine craftsmanship of this classic cardholder is highlighted by the vibrant pop art Monogram flower remix that adorns it.

This chic city bag marries exceptional style with flawless functionality. The V stitching signature on the strap and the contrast between sleek and grained leather bring refined elegance. But the large capacity– and quick access to personal belongings thanks to the back pocket– is what makes it a must-have daily companion.

The new St Germain belt features a slimmer version of the LV Initiales buckle. Embedded in the waxed calf leather, the signature adds a sleek  touch to the belt for a sophisticated look. Designed for the connoisseur, it enhances business suiting and off-duty outfits.

Featuring the light frame and flex hinges that make the Attraction model so comfortable to wear, these sunglasses boast a pilot frame meticulously covered with TAIGA leather, along with mirrored Monogram lenses for a moden, seasonal style.

A true collector's item, this Damier-pattern stole is printed with a motif of African animals created for Louis Vuitton by the renowned British artists Jake and Dinos Chapman. The luxurious blend of cashmere, wool and silk adds to the desirability of this striking design.

The whimsical Chapman Brothers giraffe illustration that adorns the Damier Ebène coated canvas brings a visually playful feel to this elegant wallet. The Brazza Wallet’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine is an optimal compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquière’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, it offers quick access to credit cards and personal belongings.

Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried like a clutch or over the shoulder thanks to its gorgeous silver chain. Accessorized with delicate flowery leather patches perforated with eyelets and decorated with silver studs, this exceptional version brings a fashionable touch to any outfit. As always, it is accessorized with the playful Twist turn-lock, featuring an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. For the collaboration, the House developed a stylish solution to organize daily essentials. The flat pouch perfectly wears gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. A new chain has been created to enable to wear the pouch outside as inside a bag. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected/surprising collaboration.

This blooming Alma Flower tells a romantic story of the House’s savoir-faire. Individually cut and coloured leather blossoms are set with metal rivets on glamorous Monogram Vernis patent calf, for a very exclusive edition of the iconic Alma.

Featuring our iconic Damier Ebene pattern, this colorful belt is adorned with a serigraphy of a savannah animal exclusively designed by the Chapman Brothers. Available in two color options and two animals, it is the ideal complement for a relaxed silhouette.

The 2017 LV League collection reveals a tribute to Louis Vuitton history both past and present. It associates iconic labels inspired from Gaston-Louis Vuitton collection and college style ones. The Multiple Wallet is compact yet highly functional, fitting into any pocket.

Inspired by an imagined trip to Tahiti, this Neverfull MM in Monogram canvas brings new energy to classic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. The quintessence of the summer spirit, the bag’s design is completed by a manuscript ‘Mykonos’ on the side.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Pouch combines both House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity - with the shape - for a result both sporty and fashion. Practical to carry by hand thanks to the removable chain or directly in the bag, this pouch will carry your Ipad with style.

The Petite Malle Epi beautifully mixes Louis Vuitton craftsmanship with a bold, stylish statement. Reflecting the Maison’s heritage in trunkmaking, it is adorned with the crosses signature of world traveler Albert Khan. Ageless and perfect for day to night chic.

Fashioned in Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquieres playful take on classic hotel stickers which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels, the Palm Springs Mini is the essential accessory for sporty urban nomads. This stylish backpack also can be carried cross-body thanks to multi-positional shoulder strap.

With details inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship, this handy accessory will accompany every nomadic lifestyle. Available in a range of colors, its playful design is perfect for a bag or pocket.

The Avenue Sling Bag in Damier Graphite canvas fits urban lifestyles perfectly: compact and sporty, with a cool and casual attitude. Its “smart” strap adjusts for left- or right-side carry. The body-friendly shape and double zip keep valuables close and secure.

model: PTE CLES NEO LV CLUB TAIGA ST.
en_US_description: Inspired by the stripes historically used to personalize Louis Vuitton trunks, this key holder reinterpreted in an emblematic Taiga leather perfectly matches the leather goods line. It can be personalized with the owner's initials.

Color brings a fresh twist to the LV Initiales reversible belt in Damier canvas and black calf leather. The handsomely crafted buckle features a lacquered LV Initiales frame inlayed with a palladium piece; the same hue is echoed in the strap’s dyed edge.
The Pearlygram collection revisits the must-have feminine white pearl with iconic Louis Vuitton signatures, from the Monogram flower petals, to the LV Circle and Monogram pattern engraved.

The pattern on this silk bandeau playfully references all Louis Vuitton's emblematic locks and clasps. It can be worn as a scarf or headband, while its narrow shape makes it easy to tie around the handles of a bag.
Inspired by the handle-fasteners on Louis Vuitton's bags, the Nanogram pendant necklace features a trompe-l'œil buckle and loop. It is finely engraved with the Monogram pattern.

2015 brings a fresh new reading of the Lockme. Crafted in a natural soft calf leather with a supple hand, the bag’s on-trend silhouette lends a youthful cachet to any look – especially when carried cross-body or slung casually over the shoulder. The over-scale LV Twist closure in shiny Palladium brass adds an edgy touch.

With its fashionable round shape and double contrasting coloured lenses, this trendy design features an engraved Monogram flower motif on the bridge for a playful look. With small studs inspired by the Maisonês trunks on the end pieces, it is perfect for square and oval faces.

New GM size with folded construction brings casual elegance to the Twist signatures. This oversized and supple shape enriches the family with new functionalities. Its large capacity makes for the perfect day-to-office bag while back zipped pocked  allows easy access to belongings

Inspired by the House’s first wallets, the Josephine wallet is a playful and modern variation of a classic design. This exceptionally elegant version is crafted in supple Monogram Empreinte leather. As always, it fits easily into most small bags and clutches.

Fashioned in Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquieres playful take on classic hotel stickers which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels, this Neverfull MM is effortlessly stylish and eminently practical. An ideal tote when its laces are open, tighten them and it becomes a more compact, chic city bag.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

This silk jacquard tie reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern in a modern, miniaturised version. Discreetly signed with the LV initials, it is a timelessly stylish accessory that makes an ideal gift.

Spotted several times at the Cruise 18 show, the Kabuki Masks Pochette is richly crafted of colorful Epi leather paired with Monogram Reverse canvas. It is fitted with a heavy chain handle and adjustable strap, for a host of fashionable carry options.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The iconic Neverfull is twisted within this collaboration with refinement and femininity through exclusive know-how: gold Monogram serti, flower shapes, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration. Ultimate luxury, the internal zipped clutch is animated and can be worn by itself as a clutch.

The iconic Monogram Shawl becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a new, soft and airy monogram jacquard material embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

A charming compact version of one of the house’s great designs, the Petit Noé is elegance itself. Its durable Epi leather means it is ideal for daily use, whilst still being effortlessly stylish and elegant.
This sophisticated shawl, woven with a tone-on-tone Monogram pattern, is given a subtle shimmer by the use of a soft shine yarn.
With its sleek, classic lines, the Anton Messenger in Taiga leather moves smoothly from office to off-duty pursuits. Plenty of pockets make it practical; discreet House signatures add refined style.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The trendy and bold shape of the Palmsprings backpack are the perfect base for the gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings distinctive of this collaboration. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17 with a disruptive reinterpretation of the iconic Pochette Métis in an ultra-stylish mini size. The double gold key chain combined with the shiny Epi leather adds fashion flair.

Proving that functionality and style can go together, the versatile Emilie Wallet in exquisite Monogram Empreinte leather is elegance itself.Numerous pockets and an attractive shape make it irresistible.

A great day-to-evening bag, the Wight mixes emblematic Damier Ebène canvas with a generous stripe of colorful Cuir Taurillon leather for easy elegance. The thin golden chain and signed eyelets and delicate lock further embolden this study in casual chic.

This playful and feminine necklace features a duet of dice as lucky charms. It offers refined details with the numbers coming as shiny strass and our distinctive Monogram pattern engraved on metal, complemented by the chain's graphic 'V' signature.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. For the collaboration, the House developed a stylish solution to organize daily essentials. The flat pouch perfectly wears gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. A new chain has been created to enable to wear the pouch outside as inside a bag. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

The sleek City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. It’s a city bag that takes care of business too, with ample room for papers and files.
The Monogram shawl is embelished with a lush fur centerpiece. The perfect cocooning accessory to face cold.

The essential accessory for the modern traveller, this passport cover in coated canvas combines style with practicality. It boasts four credit card slots and two flying pockets for easier access to your passport.

A stylish choice for the man about town, the Bumbag cross-shoulder bag in supple, Monogram Eclipse canvas combines a pared-down design with numerous practical features, including an adjustable strap, a top handle for clutch carry, and external zippered pockets for quick and secure access to belongings.

The Kasai is the ideal accessory for today's man. Suitably compact yet practical with many sophisticated details, its Monogram Macassar canvas sports a finish for a refined, masculine look.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Generous yet light, this must-have piece combines impactful branding with an easy-going, low-key design. Inspired by the Monogram Eclipse signature from the Maison's Leather Goods, it reproduces a canvas effect on a cotton base.

This silk jacquard tie reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern in a modern, miniaturised version. Discreetly signed with the LV initials, it is a timelessly stylish accessory that makes an ideal gift.
Colorful and trendy, the Emilie case in Monogram canvas and VVN leather protects precious sunnies from scratches. The LV Circle charm on the zip pull adds a chic signature touch.
The elegant and delicate Clemence Wallet is given a fresh and feminine feel for summer in Damier Azur canvas overlaid with a splashy Monogram print adapted from the Louis Vuitton archives.
A modern interpretation of a classic design, this elegant tie combines tiny dots with a discreet Monogram jacquard background, making it the perfect choice to accessorise a range of looks.
For the dynamic businesswoman, the Montaigne MM is ideal. Its smartly designed interior is structured to carry all the essentials, while Monogram Empreinte leather adds a touch of sophistication.
With its sleek, classic lines, the Anton Messenger in Taiga leather moves smoothly from office to off-duty pursuits. Plenty of pockets make it practical; discreet House signatures add refined style.
Effortlessly stylish whether carried across the body, on the shoulder or by hand, the Speedy Bandoulière 25 is the epitome of timeless design. The Epi Leather adds to its allure.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Normandy makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Functional, very body friendly, and soft to the touch, this is the perfect companion for everyday life. The supple Damier Infini leather makes it ultra-wearable and a myriad of compartments keep things organized.

These striking, feminine sunglasses are embellished with delicate Monogram flower ornaments fitted all around the lenses. The quirky style is perfect to stand out in the crowd. The original round shape is ideal for square and oval faces.
With numerous carry options, the Montaigne BB is a compact alternative for businesswomen who don’t wish to carry too much. And of course it looks beautiful in Monogram Empreinte leather.

In iconic Monogram canvas with a brightly colored lining inspired by the covers of Louis Vuitton City Guides, the iPhone 7 Plus & 8 Plus Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life

With its two removable interior pockets, the Pochette Felicie in Monogram Empreinte is the stylish solution to carry and organize your daily essentials. Much more than a wallet, it can be transformed into a glamorous shoulder bag or clutch thanks to its removable gold chain.

A stylish and easy-to-wear messenger bag, the new District PM is the ideal companion for everyday life. With its elegant details, lightweight and surprisingly spacious interior, it's the perfect combination of functionality and elegance.

The Pallas is so much more than a chic bag. It’s an alluring fusion of Monogram canvas, natural cowhide leather trim and coloured calf leather, giving it a distinctive look and a very supple feel.

The stylish and ultra-secure Zippy wallet looks glamorous in glossy Monogram Vernis leather. Combining well-organized functionalities with a pure design, it is the perfect choice for an urban lifestyle.

The Vosges bag presents a supple yet structured shape. Its refined design will enhance every elegant silhouette. The Blackberry Braided detail is a playful hint to the Couture spirit of the House and the contrast of colors adds a luminous touch to the feminine Cerise bag.

Louis Vuitton brings the discreet charm of Monogram Empreinte leather to the 6-Key Holder. Embossed with the House’s iconic Monogram pattern and featuring gold-color hardware, it can hold six keys and includes a flat pocket.

This elegantly oversized square design brings a touch of sophistication with its refined mix of materials. Featuring our emblematic Epi leather, it is a perfect match for oval and round face shapes.
Featuring our emblematic LV initials frame, this functional key-holder is a man's must-have. It comes in three of our iconic materials matching the Maison's Leather Goods range.
Perfect for men seeking an understated look, this Taurillon leather belt features an original metal loop cut out with the LV logo. A timeless model available both in Black and Bordeaux.
Woven with the Monogram pattern in a contrasting shade, this timelessly elegant stole comes in a soft, warm blend of silk and wool.

Twist Mechanical Flowers reinterprets the Monogram Flowers through a mix of materials and high craftsmanship. Flowery leather patches are delicately applied on Epi leather base and embellished by 14 eyelets & 122 golden or silver color studs both engraved with "Louis Vuitton" signature. This creation brings a fashionable appeal to must-have Twist bag.
The Brazza Wallet is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men. It is a practical companion with several different pockets, slots and compartments.
This striking silk square combines bold color-blocking with a graphic pattern of Louis Vuitton chains, straps and handles in the shape of a Monogram flower.

Our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Its practical layout will appeal to those seeking a strictly functional companion.

Smart and practical, the Jeanne Wallet in Monogram canvas offers endless possibilities. This envelop wallet in Monogram canvas is both ultra feminine and highly adaptable thanks to its three-in-one construction with removable card holder and coin pocket.

Eye-catching, isn’t it? The new Kimono tote combines Monogram canvas with fine calf leather for a riveting graphic effect. Why “Kimono”? The name alludes to the V-cross motif, inspired by the Japanese robe. In the purest tradition of House craftsmanship the bag features long Toron leather handles, a distinctive metallic V signature inspired by an historical advertising of the brand and impeccable edge-dyeing. Both roomy and remarkably light, the Kimono is a pleasure to carry.

This elegant bag charm and key holder combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram flowers with graphic stripes inspired by those used to personalize the historic trunks.

Reflecting the playful universe of Louis Vuitton, this ring is adorned with a pair of dice as lucky charms. With numbers made of feminine strass and an engraved Monogram pattern adding an iconic touch, it is a perfect gift.

This silk pocket square features motifs of African animals with negative photographic effect, created by the ChapmanÕs brothers. Its bold design will give any look a sophisticated, fashion-forward edge.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.

The Long Beach MM in high-shine Monogram Vernis offers sleek design and practical features: it’s the perfect modern tote. A pair of smooth leather tassels adds a playful touch; a removable zipped pouch keeps small necessities secure and accessible.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's Twist bag, the Twist Lock bracelet in iconic Monogram canvas or Epi leather is accessorized with a feminine tinkling charm, a perfect miniature replica of the emblematic bag.
Ideal for jeans, this stylish belt in Monogram canvas features a new buckle finely engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature.

The same twin Toucans who adorn this season’s Twist handbag appear on this playful bag charm and keyholder. Accented with a palladium “V” signature, the colorful pair will add a personal, summery touch to any bag.
Louis Vuitton's Essential V buckle adds a bold, graphic touch to this stylish and versatile belt in Monogram Reverse canvas. The strap is cut diagonally for a strong visual statement.

Reinterpreting Louis Vuitton's classic Obsession line, which is distinguished by sophisticated Monogram marquetry in the arms, these outsize square-framed sunglasses are a timelessly feminine, glamorous style.
With numerous carry options, the Montaigne BB is a compact alternative for businesswomen who don’t wish to carry too much. And of course it looks beautiful in Monogram Empreinte leather.

Bring even more glamour to your Louis Vuitton bag with this shoulder strap in Monogram coated canvas with an Epi grained cowhide leather lining. It’s super easy to attach and remove thanks to the practical snap hook.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

The new Mahina Asteria unites a chic, feminine look with the generous size that a woman wants in her favorite go-to bag. Made of remarkably supple perforated leather, its voluptuous lines and fine braided work give this model a timeless, elegant allure.

With a printed stripe that cuts across its Damier Graphite coated canvas, this Vasco Wallet is both sporty and sophisticated. The perfect size to fit in a small bag, it boasts all the essential functionalities you'll find in a Long Wallet: a zipped coin pocket, 10 credit card slots, an internal flat pocket and a large compartment for bills.

The season’s big “college spirit” story plays out on this light-hearted bag charm and key ring. Superbly crafted in varsity hues of red and blue calfskin, it makes a stylish gift: the Calf Leather back can be personalized with hot-stamped initials.

This new calf-leather bracelet reprises the LV buckle of the best-selling Neogram belt. With its stylish double-wrap strap, the Neogram is a timeless yet modern masculine accessory, available in three elegant colors.
This fashion-forward version of the Twist Wallet is crafted from shiny metallic Epi leather. As always the playful Twist turn-lock features an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

The fashionable mini size of Capucines PM lends an intense pop of contrasting colors to wardrobe styles from classic to daring. Finished with shiny color accents, the Capucines PM comes with a removable shoulder strap for casual shoulder or cross-body wear.

2015 brings a fresh new reading of the Lockme. Crafted in a natural soft calf leather with a supple hand, the bag’s on-trend silhouette lends a youthful cachet to any look – especially when carried cross-body or slung casually over the shoulder. The over-scale LV Twist closure in shiny Palladium brass adds an edgy touch.

This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.

With details inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship, this handy accessory will accompany every nomadic lifestyle. Available in a range of colors, its playful design is perfect for a bag or pocket.

This season the House launches Freedom, an exclusive calfskin tote with an edgy, moto vibe. It can be styled with zippers open or closed, to change the bag’s shape and reveal side flaps that match contrast handles. The perfect piece for urban lifestyles, finished with a leather-and-metal LV signature.

Artistic and colorful, our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Designed for clients seeking a strictly functional approach.

Slim and chic, the reversible Slender 35mm belt in Taiga leather comes in two timeless and versatile color combinations. The ideal accessory for business suits, it features a finely crafted ardillon buckle in palladium-finished brass.

The successful Charlotte model is modernized with a bold mix of materials, including mirror lenses. They’re also supremely practical thanks to an innovative hinge system that means they can be easily folded flat and carried in a bag or clutch.

Combining the Nemeth rope design on our iconic Damier canvas with black calf leather, this reversible belt can accompany fashion forward statements and more formal silhouettes. A perfect match for our new product lines.

New this season, the Capucines BB in Noir tells an elegant color story: the soft burgundy-gray of the signature flap is a subtle counterpoint to the black Taurillon leather, for an effect as versatile as a neutral, but with a fashion-forward twist.

The printed stripe that cuts across the Damier Graphite coated canvas brings a fun and strong twist to one of our most classical wallets. Large enough to fit your daily essentials, the Brazza slips easily into almost any pocket.

This reversible belt in two complementary shades of Taurillon leather features a leather-covered LV Initiales buckle for a contrasted or tone on tone look. The discreet signature and timeless colors make this belt ideal for both formal and casual wear.

Matching the emblematic Capucines bag, this feminine wallet is ornamented with a delicately crafted iris flower, inspired by the stained glass windows in the historic Vuitton family home in Asnières. Its sleek design is large enough to hold all everyday essentials.

This colorful stole reinterprets the famous universal bandana pattern to incorporate Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers. In soft, airy cotton, it is perfect for hot days in the city and can also be worn as a pareo at the beach.

A stylish and easy-to-wear messenger bag, the new District PM is the ideal companion for everyday life. With its elegant details, lightweight and surprisingly spacious interior, it's the perfect combination of functionality and elegance

These casual-sport style sunglasses feature a playful design mixing gold color with translucent details. The lightweight injected frame is confortable and easy-to-wear, while the aviator shape especially suits square and oval faces.
This reversible scarf in soft, warm wool transforms Louis Vuitton's V motif into a graphic diamond pattern, which is knitted in bold colors for a vibrant, modern look.

Compact, versatile and totally on-trend, this Pochette Voyage MM in Taiga leather can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.
Modern, playful and practical, the Lockme backpack in soft calf leather is given a fresh, summery twist with gradated perforations in the shape of Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers.

With pure lines, a fresh shape, and exquisite details like its leather corners, the Flandrin in Monogram canvas and colorful leather is for those looking for an iconic yet casual bag. It can be carried by hand, on the elbow, or over the shoulder for a more easy-going look.

Available in a range of color options, these fashionable notebooks offer a playful way of taking Louis Vuitton wherever you go. Featuring high quality watermarked paper and Epi leather covers, they are adorned with a metallic LV Circle signature.

With their bubble shape and neon colors, these adorable bag charms are playful must-haves. Two feminine color options in luxurious mink fur will add a pop touch to any bag. Versatile, these "BB" size bag charms offer new usage and can be hooked to the zip-puller of a small Leather Good item.

The season’s stylish colorway features satiny, silvery leather set off with bi-metal eyelets and the signature LV Twist Lock. Bold and modern, the bag is practical too, with a well-organized interior and removable shoulder strap.
As an elegant, modern bag for city living, the Roman PM in cross grained Taïga leather has no parallel. With its specially designed iPad pocket, it also makes an excellent choice for short trips.

Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 collection. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros.    A graphic zebra paired with bicolor stripes give a cool and nomadic look to the vintage Amazone, a compact, functional city bag.

Available in a slimmer version, the Historic bracelet in Monogram Canvas is declined in two new hues of pink  as well as in the classic  Monogram canvas. Made to mix, match and stack, these signed pieces are perfect for gifting.

Louis Vuitton's classic Clémence wallet is an elegant and compact design offering multiple practical features. In iconic Monogram canvas, it is given a playful, feminine feel by its brightly colored leather zipper and lining.

On the season’s accessory A-list is this collectible Bandoulière, finely crafted in multi-hued patent and smooth Epi leather. Designed to customize almost any Louis Vuitton bag, the hook-on strap adds a playful pop of tropical color to neutral outfits.

Must-have pieces for the Monogram lover, these statement accessories are engraved with our iconic pattern. The seasonal range includes an edgy thin cuff as well as a tie clip and cufflinks to complement business attires and our permanent  locket on charm necklace and signet ring.
Thin yet very functional, this Brazza Wallet in Taiga Leather is large enough for all your essentials and still fits easily into a jacket pocket. The two-tone interior adds a touch of fun.

Feminine and playful, the Victorine is also a very practical wallet. Every detail, such as the zipped coin pocket on the edge, has been carefully designed to create an optimal small wallet able to contain as much as a long wallet.
Woven from a blend of cashmere and wool, this fashionable piece features a paisley pattern reinterpreted with lucky charms, sprinkled into a Monogram Flower bouquet.

Featuring an archive drawing that evokes Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this feminine key holder is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods. A perfect gift, it can be personalized with hot-stamped initials on its rear side.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature, this elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials.

Designed in collaboration with iconic NYC skate brand Supreme, this version of the iPhone 7 Folio brings downtown style to a highly functional case. The adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, securely holds the phone to protect it.
The iconic Speedy bag is given a fresh, feminine feel for summer in Damier Azur canvas overlaid with a  surprising Monogram print adapted from the Louis Vuitton archives.

Product available in select stores only Meticulously crafted, this leather tab key holder references Louis Vuitton's leather goods heritage. A perfect gift, it may be personalized with the owner's initials on the back.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine is a optimal compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Monogram canvas featuring an adorable bird motif composed of classic House details, it offers quick access to credit cards and personal belongings.

This chic little bag has a secret: it's roomier than it looks. The cleverly designed "wave" base provides extra space for storing necessities. The new Twist features an updated version of the signature turn-lock. Rendered with a 3D bombé effect, the metal closure has a modern, architectural feel. To open the bag, a single smooth twist fits the letter "L" into the "V", with a satisfying click. The convertible chain handle can be worn cross-body or hung gracefully from the shoulder.

A must-have office accessory, this playful pencil pouch combines iconic Louis Vuitton signatures with an elegant look. Monogram canvas, VVN leather and the LV Circle motif add branded touches, while the color will brighten up your desk.
Ideal for everyday use, this luxuriously soft Monogram Neo Denim shawl is subtle and very feminine. Entirely weaven in jacquard, it features the Louis Vuitton signature and the Monogram pattern.

This Smart Wallet in Damier Graphite is as functional as it is sophisticated. Compact, it offers a quick access to the bills and cards inside while an external zipped gusset pocket makes it easy to get to your coins.
This Alma BB has a metallic finish that makes it perfect for evening wear. Femininity and elegance combine beautifully in one of the House's most iconic shapes.
Made from supple Utah calf leather fitted with aged-silver hardware, the Canyon Messenger unites a relaxed, urban vibe with craftsmanship, comfort and functionality. The PM holds a day’s essentials;
This elegant silk square is printed with a romantic pattern inspired by the beauty of coral and featuring a stylized Monogram flower in the center.

Kabuki-style graphics were the breakout story of Cruise SS 18. This new charm features a mask detail from the show; it slides to reveal a second disc with the reverse Monogram motif. The silver-finished metal is finely engraved with House signatures.
This elegant bag charm and key holder combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram flowers with graphic stripes inspired by those used to personalize the historic trunks.

These striking sunglasses feature luxurious Taiga leather details, including a removable part on the top bar. The large aviator shape is ideal for square and oval faces. Available with plain colour or monogram lenses.

This modern mask shape features an Essential V insert in the middle of the lens, a tribute to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton. The cylinder-shape temples, engraved with the Monogram design, complete the iconic style. Statement sunglasses for a wow effect, their mask shape is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

A genuine fashion accessory, this bandoulière strap will turn any bag into an object of desire. True to the codes of the House, the craftsmanship pays tribute to Louis Vuitton’s heritage of fine leatherwork.

Perfect for every day, the Lockmeto in soft calfskin combines a spacious, functional design with sophisticated, feminine details, including swinging tassels and the LV twist-lock, a signature of the Lockme line.

Trendy and elegant, the Sorbonne perfectly incarnates Louis Vuitton’s tradition of “travelling with style”. Its urban yet feminine design, small size and flawless functionality will make it your go-to bag for everyday life.

This finely detailed bag charm and key holder comes in the shape of a cute bird designed with Louis Vuitton historic rivets and iconic V signature on Monogram canvas. It can be personalized on the back with the owner's initials, making it an ideal gift.

Celebrating the Chinese New Year, this beautifully crafted chain bracelet features a rooster whose design plays with iconic Louis Vuitton details, including corners and studs referencing the historic trunks.

Braiding and beads give this new Epi Twist bag a cool, creative edge. House craftsmanship shines in the intricate leather embroidery and finely wrought metal accents. On-trend and ultra-covetable, it can be carried over the shoulder or worn cross-body.

Easy chic silhouette maker, the Tournelle PM is a go-anywhere carryall for work and play. Thanks to the leather piping, its shape changes depending on whether you hold it by the handles or wear it over the shoulder with its long removable strap. For those who love the Popincourt, the Tournelle is another classic Monogram shoulder bag with a pop of color for your collection.

Sparkling, luminous Rose Cuivre Monogram-embossed patent calf leather makes this Zippy Wallet eye-catchingly fresh. The Zippy is one of our most practical and versatile wallets with numerous compartments and an all-round zip closure.

Slim and sober, the iPhone 7 Plus & 8 Plus Folio has two inside flat pockets for daily essentials like business or credit cards. It easily fits in a pocket or a briefcase. Animation of our LV INITIALES 40MM belt for the FW17 show in Taurillon leather with a serigraphy printing technique for an aye-catching effect and a strong logo statement.

Trendy and elegant, the Sorbonne perfectly incarnates Louis Vuitton’s tradition of “travelling with style”. Its urban yet feminine design, small size and flawless functionality will make it your go-to bag for everyday life.

Braiding and beads give this new Epi Twist bag a cool, creative edge. House craftsmanship shines in the intricate leather embroidery and finely wrought metal accents. On-trend and ultra-covetable, it can be carried over the shoulder or worn cross-body.

This colorful stole in soft wool plays with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern to create an intriguing blurred effect. It is a fashionable accessory whose generous size gives it a cozy, enveloping feel.
This trendy tie combines the Monogram Constellation pattern with a washed denim print for a subtle vintage look.

Comfortable to wear with their integrated flex hinges, this frame is fitted with Damier mirror lenses for a extra fashionable touch. Their iconic pilot design is a perfect match for oval and square face shapes.

The Mini Pochette Accessoires in iconic Monogram canvas decorated with a print evoking the golden age of Transatlantic cruises is a striking addition to any collection of luggage. It can be clipped to another bag or carried independently.

The new Vaneau combines richly iconic Epi leather with Cuir Ecume cowhide leather.  Sleek and modern yet refined, it is an ideal match for busy lifestyles: perfectly sized, incredibly light, with a well-organized interior, top handles and a shoulder strap for multiple carry options.

This silk square features an abstract Monogram flower created from a combination of classic and modern Louis Vuitton motifs, including stripes, chains and locks. Timeless and versatile, it can be worn in many different ways.

The peerless versatility of the Zippy. With its numerous card slots and compartments and all-round zip, the Zippy gets a refreshing upgrade thanks to the new colored lining and the addition of four more credit card slots.

en_US_description: A modern, ladylike bag with a sophisticated twist, the One Handle Flap combines smooth and grained Epi leather in a new folded shape. Accented with historic trunkmaker details Ð tuck lock, brackets, name tag Ð the PM is an ideal day-to-evening choice.
