Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17, transposing the well-known Brogue pattern to the Pochette Métis in a bold and modern fashion statement. Its trendy shape is perfect to fit different styles.

Combining fine-grained calf leather with iconic Monogram canvas, this stylish, trendy compact wallet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Double V bag. The original double flap conceals a secret pocket, which is ideal for tickets or coins.

model: SAC JEUNE FILLE MNG FASHION G.
en_US_description: The One Handle Flap Bag is the architectural piece of the show with its sleek folded shape & graphic mix of materials. Refined details are tribute to Louis Vuitton's DNA : brackets & lock inspired by historical trunks and nametag reminding of the travel spirit of the House. With its large capacity, MM size is the perfect daily companion.

The new Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear. For those who love the Manhattan, the Tuileries also offers a top handle & shoulder strap for the sophisticated urban lifestyle.

Completely reimagined to perfectly pair with the Retiro city bag, the envelope-style Sarah Wallet takes on striking modernity thanks to the colourful and architectural leather patches that bring a dashing contemporary feel to the classic Monogram canvas. The ingenious interior features a variety of pockets.

Easy chic silhouette maker, the Tournelle MM is a go-anywhere carryall for work and play. Thanks to the leather piping, its shape changes depending on whether you hold it with its comfortable handles or removable shoulder strap

These delicate necklaces play on Louis Vuitton's iconic codes in a tribute to the Maison's history and playful spirit. Available as single pendants or as a multi-charm necklace, they are the perfect gifts to mix-and-match and to play on accumulation.
This striking silk square transforms Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram into a vibrant, graphic pattern, while the rooster motif with its Monogram flower eye is a playful nod to the Chinese New Year.

With its refined buckle in golden-finished brass, this sleek new belt pays tribute to the House's trunk-making ("Malletier") heritage. A  LV Circle detail at the end of the strap adds the finishing touch to a timeless and elegant accessory.
Rich, contemporary Taurillon leather is adorned with the elegent iconic LV. A soft yet sturdy belt that that dresses to casual attire.

The most structured of the iconic Louis Vuitton handbags. The original was the creation of Gaston Vuitton, who named it for the Alma Bridge, a span that connects two fashionable Paris neighbourhoods. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Épi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colours.

The Twist was first presented in Cruise 2015 and quickly became a New Classic. Fashioned in pink Epi Jean leather, a unique printing and embossing technique that gives leather the visual effect of denim fabric, and paired with smooth black leather, this Twist PM brings a touch of fashionable femininity to any outfit.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 25 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Pleasingly classic lines and supple Taiga leather make the Anton Pochette an ideal option for every day. Compact and comfortable to carry, this new model features refined detailing: witness the discreet metal signature on the bag’s front pocket.

This iconic new design plays on the all-over multicolor revamped Monogram print from the FW17 range. Crafted from silk twill, it is a perfect gift that also well-suited to sophisticated looks and more casual attitudes.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with bright red leather for a highly colored silhouette.

This effortlessly elegant cashmere and silk stole literally envelops you in a blanket of delicate softness. The iconic leopard pattern by Stephen Sprouse has been revitalized with hints of pop colours that to liven things up.

Designed in 1932 to transport bottles of Champagne, the Noé returns for Spring 17 as the NéoNoé, an on-trend bucket bag in supple Monogram canvas with colorful calf-leather accents and an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry.
Compact form and supreme comfort come together in this easy-to-wear messenger-style bag. With its magnetic closure and zipped pocket on the back, it's as functional as it is tasteful.

A statement accessory coming from the Spring-Summer 2016 Show, the Tassel bag charm comes in both our iconic Monogram canvas or the new Blanc Gamma version, along with calf leather in this season’s pink color.

In creating the Fragrance Travel Cases, Louis Vuitton applies its savoir-faire and mastery in custom-designing the perfect case for transporting and protecting each item of one’s personal belongings. The 100ML travel case conserves and protects your perfume bottle, closing securely with a buckle. Slip it into your bag in every situation.The 100ml travel case can also be personalized in store to the initials of your choice.
A reversible scarf in wool and cashmere featuring the iconic Monogram logo in an all-over design.

For Cruise 2017, the City Steamer has been reinterpreted in an audacious & futuristic version. Each pocket is highly crafted with Louis Vuitton engraved studs on a smooth leather base. Flawless functionalitity & subtle sophistication make this City Steamer the perfect urban companion.

Louise EW is the ultimate elegant piece for evening outfit. This season, this pure clutch is animated in precious silver calfskin, making it the perfect gleaming accessory, enhanced by tone on tone Epi like resin lock for the jewel touch.
With its sober design, this elegant Folio in Monogram is the stylish way to protect your iPad Pro from dents and scratches. The innovative micro-suction pads hold it securely in place.
Elegant and practical, Louis Vuitton's classic Clemence Wallet is given a delicate, feminine feel by pink leather trim and a cute Monogram flower charm.

Here’s a cool new object of fashion desire: the Lockme Backpack in a fresh Mini size. Crafted from soft calfskin, it is surprisingly roomy and goes everywhere, from daytime to after dark. With adjustable straps, it can go from shoulder to cross-body wear.

Here’s a cool new object of fashion desire: the Lockme Backpack in a fresh Mini size. Crafted from soft calfskin, it is surprisingly roomy and goes everywhere, from daytime to after dark. With adjustable straps, it can go from shoulder to cross-body wear.

For Fall 2017, the House continues to reveal new facets of Vernis leather with an unexpected reinterpretation of one of Louis Vuitton’s most iconic shapes: the Alma BB. The audacious color and Monogram canvas trim gives it a stunningly disruptive feel.
A playful piece that will create a playful wintry vibe to any silhouette. The design offers a new twist on the Monogram Flower motif, inspired by traditional winter jacquard pattern.

This distinctive piece reinterprets the Monogram Flower in feminine cabochons for a subtle play on colors and contrasts. Iconic Louis Vuitton signatures combined in an association of different metal finishes and shiny stones.

This eye-catching accessory features Kabuki-themed stickers, a highlight of the Cruise SS 18 collection. Wrapped around neck, head – or knotted on the handles of a bag – it brings an on-trend touch of color and fun.
The Indian Flower silk square is printed with an intricately detailed floral pattern. It is a versatile accessory which will add elegance and femininity to any look.

Yarns of different colours are weaved together to reproduce multicolour Monogram on this signature shawl. Joyful, generous and enveloping, the Monogram Rainbow shawl is perfect to pep-up any winter look.
This practical ID Card Holder in Damier Graphite canvas is the easy way to wear your business badge around your neck.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather, the Capucines Compact Wallet has many functionalities and a large capacity to fit every day essentials. The ingenious and original structure of this elegant pocket-sized wallet made of 2 fold-over flaps gives you ample space for credit cards, coins and bills.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Normandy makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

The City Steamer is the perfect mix of Louis Vuitton heritage with the codes introduced by Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquière. This City Steamer MM features a graphic tailored vibe with hypnotic crafted patchwork that incorporates different stitching and a mix of smooth and shiny cracked leathers.
Makes the most of winter with Logomania Scarf. Adorned with giant versions of the iconic Monogram pattern and the house initials, it features warm wool and soft silk

With its easy-to-wear acetate design, this classic style will suit all wardrobes. Iconic studs evoke the Maison's historic trunks, while metallic Essential V inserts pay homage to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton.

Fashioned in understated Taurillon leather, the ultra-functional Zippy XL has never looked more elegant. With the capacity of a small bag in a wallet, it is large enough to hold a smartphone, keys and a passport, in addition to credit cards and cash.

This season, the Cluny BB steps out in Epi Platine, a new metallic shade of the signature House leather. Its structured lines and subtle sheen make this eye-catching bag an edgy, modern choice to accompany both daytime looks and evening silhouettes.

Introducing the Twist MM in Epi Platine, a seductive new metallic shade of the House’s signature grained leather. The understated shine lends an edge to daytime outfits, transitioning effortlessly to evening, adding a touch of subtle sparkle to party looks.

The charming Alma PM traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This contemporary version is crafted of Monogram canvas, featuring creative director Nicolas Ghesquière's playful take on classic hotel stickers, which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colorful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

Discreetly woven with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, the Monogramissime tie is a timelessly elegant choice in an array of classic or seasonal colors. A matching pocket square is also available.

Make any trip an effortlessly stylish affair with the Passport Cover. A sumptuous grained calf leather lining and several interior compartments complete this classic travel accessory. The giraffes on a shopping spree with their Louis Vuitton fancy bags, transform this elegant Passport Cover into the epitome of adorable.

A result of the collaboration between Louis Vuitton and Japanese streetwear designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, creator of the Fragment label, this trendy beret was traditionally handmade in France. In felted merino wool with leather edging and a silk lining, it can be personalized with Louis Vuitton and Fragment patches.

Featuring the new Monogram Savane canvas with unique Chapman's Animal, this versatile piece offers two belts in one. The iconic Reverso buckle completes this collector model for fashion and relax look.

One of our most iconic and versatile models, this Zippy Wallet in soft, subtly grained Mahina leather and delicate Monogram perforations with new extra credit card slots has never been more functional and stylish. Slip it into your bag or carry it by hand as a mini clutch!

This season, the Twist has been reinterpreted in elegant smooth patent calfskin mixed with graphic & hypnotic Monogram colors lock, for a fashion-forward take on this leather. Perfect for a day-to-evening use, this Twist PM is a bold & cool addition to any silhouette.

Featuring the new Monogram Savane canvas with unique Chapman's Animal, this versatile piece offers two belts in one. The iconic Reverso buckle completes this collector model for fashion and relax look.

This reversible belt offers two very different, and stylish looks in one: Monogram canvas with contrasting leather trimmings on one side and Louis Vuitton's emblematic Epi grained leather on the other side.

The name says it all: beautiful and desirable, the Venus, inspired from the Steamer, a House icon (1901), for today's urban lifestyles. In Monogram canvas with colored cowhide leather trim, its generous capacity makes this bag ideal for day-to-office use.

One of our most iconic and versatile models, this Zippy Wallet in soft, subtly grained Mahina leather and delicate Monogram perforations with new extra credit card slots has never been more functional and stylish. Slip it into your bag or carry it by hand as a mini clutch!

The iconic Monogram Shawl becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a new, soft and airy monogram jacquard material embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

The new Vaneau combines richly iconic Epi leather with Cuir Ecume cowhide leather.  Sleek and modern yet refined, it is an ideal match for busy lifestyles: perfectly sized, incredibly light, with a well-organized interior, top handles and a shoulder strap for multiple carry options.

With its pure lines and sophisticated details, the Louis Vuitton Very Chain Bag in supple Cuir Plume and Cuir Ecume leathers is your new must-have bag. The delicate chain and crafted V signature provide glamour while the flap and lock closure keep your essentials safe inside. Perfect for luxury car lovers, this case in coated canvas has a press-stud to easily remove the key when you have the valet park your car.

This season, the pure design of City Steamer has been mixed with punchy colorblocks, matching the sporty & joyful spirit of the show. Graphic tricolor combinations on trendy & versatile PM size will add a bold touch of color to any outfit.

This compact Pocket Organizer is for men looking for sophistication. The Monogram Savane canvas printed with a Chapman Brothers rhinoceros illustration brings a touch of whimsy to a classic all-in-one card holder that holds credit cards, bills and papers.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. Brazza Wallet generous size makes it ideal to carry all your cards and receipts while slipping easily in your jacket's pocket.

The successful Charlotte model is modernized with a bold mix of materials, including mirror lenses. They’re also supremely practical thanks to an innovative hinge system that means they can be easily folded flat and carried in a bag or clutch.
The Porte-Documents Voyage PM looks effortlessly stylish in masculine Taiga leather. With smooth leather trimmings and a spacious interior, it combines luxury and practicality.

Featuring a graphic bi-color design inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton motifs Damier and Monogram, mixed with timeless dots pattern, this long and generous winter scarf is a perfect cocoon against the cold.

The new Hudson sunglasses feature a fashionable round shape in a mix of laminated acetate and metal. The rim is delicatly engraved with the Damier design, with the Louis Vuitton signature on the temples.

Designed in 1932 to transport bottles of Champagne, the Noé returns for Spring 17 as the NéoNoé, an on-trend bucket bag in supple Monogram canvas with colorful calf-leather accents and an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine wallet is an exceptionnel compact wallet. Trendy in iconic Monogram canvas with a colourful leather lining, it offers quick and secure access to credit cards and personal belongings.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.

Perfect for every day, the Lockmeto in soft calfskin combines a spacious, functional design with sophisticated, feminine details, including swinging tassels and the LV twist-lock, a signature of the Lockme line.

This stylish backpack belongs to the new Canyon suite of bags, crafted of supple Utah calfskin and accented with aged-silver metal fittings. The relaxed shape, generous size and clever design make this city pack an ideal carry-all companion.

This elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials. The leather braid woven into a simple chevron pattern brings modern style to this classic wallet in Taurillon leather.

The Multiple Wallet holds your credit cards, bills and receipts in a very compact format. This version in Damier Ebène coated canvas adorned with an exclusive Chapman Brothers zebra illustration brings a touch of whimsy to a classic wallet.

Inspired by iconic steamer luggage from Louis Vuitton archives, the City Steamer is renowned for its functional and nomad spirit. Reinterpreted in easy-to-carry and elegant gray Epi Jean leather and paired with timeless silver metallic pieces, this City Steamer MM is pure elegance.
This iconic wallet just got an upgrade! Now with four additional credit card slots and a playful new coloured lining, the Zippy Wallet in Monogram Empreinte leather is more versatile than ever.

Slightly oversized for a trendy twist, this fashion forward model highlights our transversal Essential V signature. With its lightweight mix of materials, and thin metal temples, the cat-eye shape has a modern retro touch.
The Rock N’ Roses stole comes in a rich rainbow of colors. Adorned with Stephen Sprouse-designed flowers reworked in a camouflage effect. This fashion stole promises an effortless, casual-chic look.

Featuring the iconic LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt comes in two contrasting shades of supple and grained Taurillon leather, effectively offering two looks in one.

This silk and wool shawl combines the graphic patterns from Louis Vuitton's Spring/Summer 2017 fashion show to create an optical illusion of a Monogram flower. It is both a collector's item and a versatile accessory for every day.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art.  One of our most iconic and versatile models, the Zippy wallet is adorned with this exclusive collaboration: gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

Compact and ingeniously designed, the Ariane Wallet has multiple credit card slots and pockets hidden seemingly everywhere. The touch of color from the filetto detailing around the flap brings feminine sophistication to the Monogram canvas.

Monogram flower pins bloom on this new city backpack, an unexpected and oh-so-stylish piece made of supple Monogram Empreinte cowhide. The dark-blue leather’s metallic sheen sets off the aged-silver finish of the pins, for a modern, edgy look.
This envelope-style Sarah Wallet combines an elegant exterior in Epi leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

This fashionable Lockme Bucket evokes the elegant yet solid bag custom-made by Louis Vuitton in 1932 for a wealthy vineyard owner to transport bottles of champagne. Its sleek design and signature LV Twist lock make it eternally modern.

Our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Its extra features will accompany our most demanding and sophisticated customers.

The unique design of Monogram canvas matched with supple grained leather makes this a versatile day-to-night bag with style. It boasts a golden chain for short-shoulder, long-shoulder and cross-body carry!

The charming Alma BB traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This miniature version easily holds keys, wallet, smartphone and lipstick. With a strap that adjusts the bag to waist or hip height, the Alma BB can be worn across the body for hands-free ease. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Epi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colors.

This modern mask shape features an Essential V insert in the middle of the lens, a tribute to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton. The cylinder-shape temples, engraved with the Monogram design, complete the iconic style. Statement sunglasses for a wow effect, their mask shape is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

The Canyon briefcase in Utah calfskin features a mix of smooth and grained finishes, accented with double-stitching and aged-silver hardware. A light, compact business bag, it’s designed for convenience, with comfortable Toron handles and a removable strap.

Shimmery lurex yarn is woven into a cozy blend of wool and cashmere to form the iconic Malletage pattern, set off by a delicate LV Circle emblem in gold-finished metal. Its generous size and delicate mix of materials create a feeling of enveloping softness and warmth.

The successful Charlotte Fold model is now enriched with a bold mix of materials, including an eye-catching 3D LV Circle logo. Strasses on the metal temples add a touch of sophistication to this model, perfect for oval and triangular faces.

Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried like a clutch or over the shoulder thanks to its gorgeous silver chain. Accessorized with delicate flowery leather patches perforated with eyelets and decorated with silver studs, this exceptional version brings a fashionable touch to any outfit. As always, it is accessorized with the playful Twist turn-lock, featuring an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

This silk square reinterprets the famous universal bandana pattern to incorporate Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers. Overprinted with the LV initials in an arty, paintbrush style, it is a versatile accessory to accompany timeless and fashion-forward looks.
This Sarah Multicartes in brightly colored Epi leather is inspired by the House’s iconic envelop-style Sarah wallet. Its accordion interior has plenty of space for cards, coins and bank notes.

Inspired by the Leather Bracelet Over the strap from the show FW16, this double-strap bracelet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with shiny gold and silver metal hardware in a trendy, rock 'n' roll spirit.

Echoing the stylish, casual design of the Lockme II handbag, this wallet in soft calf leather is embellished with a feminine braided detail that subtly references Louis Vuitton's tradition of craftsmanship. Secured with a distinctive LV initials clasp, its spacious interior boasts a variety of pockets and compartments.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The trendy and bold shape of the Palmsprings backpack are the perfect base for the gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings distinctive of this collaboration. This graphic ring bag charm reinterprets the Maison's iconic LV Circle signature in a summery pink. Simple and Easy to fit in your pocket it is the perfect accessory for your keys or your bag.
In line with the Fall/Winter 2017 bags collection, this key holder and bag charm features leather with brogue-style perforations on a background of iconic Monogram canvas.

Providing stylish protection, this Eye-Trunk for iPhone 7 in Monogram Rouge canvas is a stunning tribute to our legacy as trunk makers. Designed in collaboration with iconic NYC skate brand Supreme, it’s sure to become the new must-have iPhone accessory.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.
This Enveloppe Carte de Visite in Taiga leather features two credit card slots and one compartment for business cards.

From the Louis Vuitton x Fragment Design collection comes this cool, sporty messenger in Monogram Eclipse, bisected by a black band with reflective trim. The fine detailing – lozine edging, pocket stitching, colored Rainbow hardware – befits a man of style.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the District messenger, created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the oversized  new Damier Latitude pattern, for a modern, masculine look.

The charming Alma BB traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This miniature version easily holds keys, wallet, smartphone and lipstick. With a strap that adjusts the bag to waist or hip height, the Alma BB can be worn across the body for hands-free ease. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Epi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colors.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. The ultra-functional Zippy XL offers the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It is large enough to hold a smartphone (in a specific pocket), keys and passport, in addition to credit cards and cash. Elegant in Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather, it can be hand carried  for a sophisticated look.
Glossy, cute and girly, the smallest Chain Louise blends iconic elegance with ultra-feminine charm. Additional functionality and versatility thanks to a delicate removable chain.

Inspired by the Leather Bracelet Over the strap from the show FW16, this double-strap bracelet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with shiny gold and silver metal hardware in a trendy, rock 'n' roll spirit.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17 with this architectural Cour Marly Bag in supple calfskin. Adorned with a golden lock and chain as well as small studs along the bottom, it is evocative of the historical trunks.
Compact yet ample, in smart and elegant Epi leather, the new version of  the Clémence Wallet is offered in playful and high-fashion shades.

The fashionable mini size of Capucines PM lends an intense pop of contrasting colors to wardrobe styles from classic to daring. Finished with shiny color accents, the Capucines PM comes with a removable shoulder strap for casual shoulder or cross-body wear.

The Idol V collection reinterprets the striking V signature introduced by Nicolas Ghesquière at his first fashion show for Louis Vuitton. Contrasting gold and palladium finishes bring a graphic touch to these feminine pendant earrings, which feature links of different shapes.

This stylish silk bandeau features a graphic reinterpretation of the Monogram flowers on one side and the Monogram pattern on the other. Its slim shape makes it ideal for tying around the handles of a bag, and it can also be worn as a scarf, headband or bracelet.
The Monaco Square comes in delicate silk. Decorated with Monogram flowers, it complements the timeless, chic style of the classic woman.

“Louis Vuitton Paris” spells out a unique, signature pattern on this stylish new tie, offered in three subtle shades. The silk jacquard weave creates an interesting textural effect that looks smart with a tailored suit, for business or formal occasions.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The iconic Neverfull is twisted within this collaboration with refinement and femininity through exclusive know-how: gold Monogram serti, flower shapes, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration. Ultimate luxury, the internal zipped clutch is animated and can be worn by itself as a clutch.

Feminine and playful, the Victorine is also a very practical wallet. Every detail, such as the zipped coin pocket on the edge, has been carefully designed to create an optimal small wallet able to contain as much as a long wallet.

This reversible model offers two belts in one, via a combination of Damier canvas and Calf leather, with subtle pop Orange edge-dyeing. The iconic Damier motif provides a discrete yet recognizable touch of branding to casual looks.

The unique LV Twist lock now adorns this brand-new tote, a bag with modern lines, luxurious signature details, and ample room for organizing a (business) day’s essentials. The exclusive model in Epi Denim sports 13 LV pins, for a playful, on-trend look.

Louis Vuitton’s exceptional craftsmanship goes Pop in this Twist MM. Its vibrant colors and crafted leather patches create a post-modern – but very feminine – interpretation of the emblematic Monogram flower.

Available in three colors that match the FW17 color range, this modern reinterpretation of the Monogram shawl will light up any winter outfit. Its eye-catching blurry design is inspired by set of lights.
A sophisticated accessory for formal looks, this elegant scarf in a soft, luxurious blend of cashmere and wool is woven with a graduated Monogram pattern.

A statement accessory coming from the Spring-Summer 2016 Show, the Tassel bag charm comes in both our iconic Monogram canvas or the new Blanc Gamma version, along with calf leather in this season’s pink color.
Rich, contemporary Taurillon leather is adorned with the elegent iconic LV. A soft yet sturdy belt that that dresses to casual attire.

Chic and refined, the Pochette Envelope GM in supple Taurillon leather boasts a luxurious microfiber lining and a highly practical zipped back pocket, making it a great clutch for distinctive men on the go.
The Brazza Wallet is part of the Taïga leather range, Louis Vuitton's very first collection for men. It is a practical companion with several different pockets, slots and compartments.
True statement on Louis Vuitton's Spring/Summer 2017 Men's fashion show, this punk-inspired collar necklace is crafted from iconic Monogram canvas with masculine palladium-finish hardware.
This thin silk tie features motifs of African animals created for Louis Vuitton by British artists Jake and Dinos Chapman. Its bold design will give any look a sophisticated, fashion-forward edge.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colorful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

The Japanese-inspired Bento Box is the statement shape from Cruise 18. Crafted of classic Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas with leather trim and gleaming golden hardware, it features both a handle and a strap for hand, shoulder or cross-body wear.
Get ready to turn heads with this totally on-trend Twist Tote and its perfect combination of modern lines and luxurious details like the iconic LV Twist-lock and très chic side-body straps.

This elegant watchcase in masculine Eclipse Monogram canvas has a removable microfiber cushion and can be used to safely transport up to three watches. The case closes securely thanks to its leather strap and buckle.

This Petite Malle fashioned in stunning silver Epi leather was inspired by custom trunks created for wealthy banker Albert Kahn in the early 20th century, with his signature 3 white crosses. Timelessly elegant, it’s an exceptional small bag for evenings out.
This envelope style Sarah wallet combines an exterior in discreetly embossed Monogram Empreinte leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.
This elegant silk square is printed with a romantic pattern inspired by the beauty of coral and featuring a stylized Monogram flower in the center.

A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the new Damier Coastline pattern, for a modern and fashion piece. You can slip the Pochette Voyage MM  into your bag as a travel pouch or hand carry it for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.
This envelope-style Sarah wallet combines an exterior in discreetly embossed Monogram Empreinte leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

The Japanese-inspired Bento Box is the statement shape from Cruise 18. Crafted of classic Monogram and Monogram Reverse canvas with leather trim and gleaming golden hardware, it features both a handle and a strap for hand, shoulder or cross-body wear.

In black leather with contrasting hot pink edge dyeing, this iconic wallet’s pure design gets a daring twist. Its well-organized functionalities make it the optimal answer for the vagaries of urban living.

Ideal to brighten up any look, this soft shawl in silk and wool is a study in versatility: highlight the plain part of the pattern for a more classic feel or feature the flower motif for a fancier occasion.

A must-have office accessory, this playful pencil pouch combines iconic Louis Vuitton signatures with an elegant look. Monogram canvas, VVN leather and the LV Circle motif add branded touches, while the color will brighten up your desk.

In time to bring a touch of delicate color to winter wardrobes, here is the Pochette Metis in new Rose Bruyère, a perfect shade of pink. Crafted of embossed Monogram Empreinte leather, it’s both practical and stylish: an ideal “go-to” bag for daily wear.

The Canyon briefcase in Utah calfskin features a mix of smooth and grained finishes, accented with double-stitching and aged-silver hardware. A light, compact business bag, it’s designed for convenience, with comfortable Toron handles and a removable strap.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. As practical as it is sophisticated, it fits comfortably into your pocket or handbag and holds credit cards, bills and papers.
An ideal gift, this adorable bag charm and key holder comes in luxurious mink, playfully adorned with tiny wings.

Make your Louis Vuitton bag your own with a peppy pop of colour thanks to this shoulder strap in Epi leather. Fun and versatile: it’s super easy to put on and remove thanks to the practical snap hook.

Available in a slimmer version, the Historic bracelet in Monogram Canvas is declined in two new hues of pink  as well as in the classic  Monogram canvas. Made to mix, match and stack, these signed pieces are perfect for gifting.

Smart and practical, the Jeanne Wallet in Monogram canvas offers endless possibilities. This envelop wallet in Monogram canvas is both ultra feminine and highly adaptable thanks to its three-in-one construction with removable card holder and coin pocket.

Fashioned in our new iconic black and grey Monogram Eclipse canvas, this resolutely masculine iPhone 7 Plus & 8 Plus Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface holds the phone perfectly in place to protect it.

Slim and sober, the iPhone 7 & 8 Folio has two inside flat pockets for daily essentials like business or credit cards. It easily fits in a pocket or a briefcase. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.
Matching our Leather Goods, this new belt suits both business silhouettes and more modern looks. The buckle features a sleek tone-on-tone plaque, with an LV logo adding a subtle signature.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with bright red leather for a highly colored silhouette.

The Palm Springs PM backpack gets a sophisticated new look thanks to Louis Vuitton’s feminine Matelasse Flower pattern: this delicate embroidery subtly reproduces the iconic Monogram flower on the bag’s ultra-soft black lambskin for a lightly quilted effect.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17 with this fresh take of the now-classic City Steamer, adorned with small studs on edges that highlight its architectural shape. This bag brings a fashionably edgy feel to any look.

Decorated with a print evoking the glamour of Louis Vuitton during the golden age of Transatlantic travel, this Zippy Wallet in coated canvas combines versatility, generous space and an all-round zip. It's perfect for carrying and organizing your daily essentials.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.
A playful piece that will create a playful wintry vibe to any silhouette. The design offers a new twist on the Monogram Flower motif, inspired by traditional winter jacquard pattern.
Ideal for jeans, this stylish belt in Monogram canvas features a new buckle finely engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature.

Easy chic silhouette maker, the Tournelle PM is a go-anywhere carryall for work and play. Thanks to the leather piping, its shape changes depending on whether you hold it by the handles or wear it over the shoulder with its long removable strap.

This fashionable Capucines BB is softened by a delicate and feminine cut inspired by the lace croquets technique. The chiseled edges, with a precious stud at their center, are inspired by the iconic Monogram Flower and by the nails on historic House Trunks.

The famous Louis Vuitton silk square becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a silk twill base embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

Woven of wool, silk and cashmere, the Storm stole wraps the wearer in softness and warmth. The design, linked to the Cruise show, is an artful take on camouflage motifs, in neutral black and white for ultimate wearability, with a contrasted “Louis Vuitton” signature on the bottom edge.

With its refined buckle in golden-finished brass, this sleek new belt pays tribute to the House's trunk-making ("Malletier") heritage. A  LV Circle detail at the end of the strap adds the finishing touch to a timeless and elegant accessory.

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 25 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

This statement ring extends our iconic alphabet motif to spell love, with a subtle nod to our emblematic LV initials. A perfect gift, this playful piece is embellished with trunk studs on the letters for an extra twist.
The stylish Ecu tie combines Petit Damier checks with a contrasting narrow stripe in shiny silk. It is finished with the LV initials in a discreet escutcheon.

Inspired by an imagined trip to Tahiti, this Neverfull MM in Monogram canvas brings new energy to classic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. The quintessence of the summer spirit, the bag’s design is completed by a manuscript ‘Knokke’ on the side.
This silk square captures the spirit of summer with its pattern of pink Monogram flowers as if hand-painted on a Damier Azur background. It is perfect to wear around the neck or in the hair.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian authenticity for Fall-Winter 17 with this futuristic version of the Speedy 25. Ideal for every day, this updated iconic bag offers an audacious style.

A contemporary take on the classic schoolbag, the updated Mylockme is a sleek, ultra-fashionable model crafted of soft, supple calf. Versatile and functional, with a well-organized interior, it can be carried by hand, on the shoulder or cross-body.

This modern mask shape features an Essential V insert in the middle of the lens, a tribute to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton. The cylinder-shape temples, engraved with the Monogram design, complete the iconic style. Statement sunglasses for a wow effect, their mask shape is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. New shape specifically designed for this collection, the chain bag mixes iconic elements from the House (lock, envelop shape, leather patch) and specific signatures of the collaboration: a new chain, gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected/surprising collaboration.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature, this elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials.

With its distinctive shape and refined details, the Avenue Backpack in supple Damier Infini leather brings casual sophistication to any look. It's practical and keeps your belongings secure thanks to its zipped compartments.

Featuring an archive drawing that evokes Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this feminine key holder is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods. A perfect gift, it can be personalized with hot-stamped initials on its rear side.

The Multiple Wallet is ideal to hold credit cards, bills and receipts in a very compact format. The smart mix between Damier Graphite canvas and colored leather lining adds an extra veneer of sophistication.

This Zippy Organizer in Damier Ebène coated canvas, featuring a whimsical illustration of a zebra, is a study in playful elegance. Ideal for those who like everything in one place: it easily holds a checkbook, plane tickets, papers and pen.

Fashioned in Monogram coated canvas customized with Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquiere’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, this large toiletry pouch boasts a spacious interior and gusset sides for easy storage.

With their bubble shape and neon colors, these adorable bag charms are playful must-haves. Two feminine color options in luxurious mink fur will add a pop touch to any bag. Versatile, these "BB" size bag charms offer new usage and can be hooked to the zip-puller of a small Leather Good item.

Crafted in Monogram Savane canvas with a whimsy illustration of a zebra, this compact Multiple Wallet holds credit cards, bills and receipts and slips easily into your pocket.  As stylish as it is functional.

With its easy-to-wear acetate design, this classic style will suit all wardrobes. Iconic studs evoke the Maison's historic trunks, while metallic Essential V inserts pay homage to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton.

Incomparably thin, this sophisticated Compact Wallet is fashioned from a mix of grained and smooth leather with double stitching. It’s compact enough to easily slip in the back pocket of a pair of jeans.The LV signature ton on ton makes it very refined and discreet.
The finishing touch for ultra-chic sophistication: this pure silk square with its modern take on our heritage, a trunks and luggage pattern, signed Louis Vuitton.

Incomparably thin, this Pocket Organizer with its mix of grained and smooth Utah leather, and double stitching, marries sophisticated style with easy functionality:  the perfect way to carry your credit cards and bills.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life. For those who love the Popincourt, the Pallas is another classic Monogram shoulder bag with a pop of color for your collection.

A bag to fit any mood or silhouette, the new Cléry Pochette in Epi leather can be worn on the shoulder, cross-body (merci, adjustable strap) or carried by the finely detailed top handle. Surprisingly roomy, it is offered in a bouquet of fashionable shades.

Must-have pieces for the Monogram lover, these statement accessories are engraved with our iconic pattern. The seasonal range includes an edgy thin cuff as well as a tie clip and cufflinks to complement business attires and our permanent  locket on charm necklace and signet ring.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. The Multiple wallet in Taiga leather is ideal for holding credit cards, bills and receipts.

A fashionable piece that will not go unnoticed, the arty Paint Splash stole is generous in size, to wear stylishly around the neck. The cotton-silk blend is soft and light, in an easy-going Navy or in a summery Light Grey.

The glamorous Pallas BB combines iconic Monogram canvas with colourful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colourful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.
The sporty Zack Backpack in coated canvas has a roomy interior and a classic Louis Vuitton look. The flap, drawstring closing, and metal buckle evoke so many the House classics.

The Malle Fleurs silk square was inspired by the Louis Vuitton tradition of sending flower-filled trunks to its best clients. Its feminine design features two open trunks amid a scattering of Monogram flowers and LV Circle logos.
The simple yet fine craftsmanship of this classic cardholder is highlighted by the vibrant pop art Monogram flower remix that adorns it.

This chic city bag marries exceptional style with flawless functionality. The V stitching signature on the strap and the contrast between sleek and grained leather bring refined elegance. But the large capacity– and quick access to personal belongings thanks to the back pocket– is what makes it a must-have daily companion.

The new St Germain belt features a slimmer version of the LV Initiales buckle. Embedded in the waxed calf leather, the signature adds a sleek  touch to the belt for a sophisticated look. Designed for the connoisseur, it enhances business suiting and off-duty outfits.

Featuring the light frame and flex hinges that make the Attraction model so comfortable to wear, these sunglasses boast a pilot frame meticulously covered with TAIGA leather, along with mirrored Monogram lenses for a moden, seasonal style.

A true collector's item, this Damier-pattern stole is printed with a motif of African animals created for Louis Vuitton by the renowned British artists Jake and Dinos Chapman. The luxurious blend of cashmere, wool and silk adds to the desirability of this striking design.

The whimsical Chapman Brothers giraffe illustration that adorns the Damier Ebène coated canvas brings a visually playful feel to this elegant wallet. The Brazza Wallet’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine is an optimal compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquière’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, it offers quick access to credit cards and personal belongings.

Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried like a clutch or over the shoulder thanks to its gorgeous silver chain. Accessorized with delicate flowery leather patches perforated with eyelets and decorated with silver studs, this exceptional version brings a fashionable touch to any outfit. As always, it is accessorized with the playful Twist turn-lock, featuring an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. A new chain has been created to enable to wear the pouch outside as inside a bag. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected/surprising collaboration.

This blooming Alma Flower tells a romantic story of the House’s savoir-faire. Individually cut and coloured leather blossoms are set with metal rivets on glamorous Monogram Vernis patent calf, for a very exclusive edition of the iconic Alma.

Featuring our iconic Damier Ebene pattern, this colorful belt is adorned with a serigraphy of a savannah animal exclusively designed by the Chapman Brothers. Available in two color options and two animals, it is the ideal complement for a relaxed silhouette.

The 2017 LV League collection reveals a tribute to Louis Vuitton history both past and present. It associates iconic labels inspired from Gaston-Louis Vuitton collection and college style ones. The Multiple Wallet is compact yet highly functional, fitting into any pocket.

Inspired by an imagined trip to Tahiti, this Neverfull MM in Monogram canvas brings new energy to classic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. The quintessence of the summer spirit, the bag’s design is completed by a manuscript ‘Mykonos’ on the side.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Pouch combines both House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity - with the shape - for a result both sporty and fashion. Practical to carry by hand thanks to the removable chain or directly in the bag, this pouch will carry your Ipad with style.

The Petite Malle Epi beautifully mixes Louis Vuitton craftsmanship with a bold, stylish statement. Reflecting the Maison’s heritage in trunkmaking, it is adorned with the crosses signature of world traveler Albert Khan. Ageless and perfect for day to night chic.

Fashioned in Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquieres playful take on classic hotel stickers which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels, the Palm Springs Mini is the essential accessory for sporty urban nomads. This stylish backpack also can be carried cross-body thanks to multi-positional shoulder strap.

With details inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship, this handy accessory will accompany every nomadic lifestyle. Available in a range of colors, its playful design is perfect for a bag or pocket.

The Avenue Sling Bag in Damier Graphite canvas fits urban lifestyles perfectly: compact and sporty, with a cool and casual attitude. Its “smart” strap adjusts for left- or right-side carry. The body-friendly shape and double zip keep valuables close and secure.

2015 brings a fresh new reading of the Lockme. With its fashionable round shape and double contrasting coloured lenses, this trendy design features an engraved Monogram flower motif on the bridge for a playful look. With small studs inspired by the Maisonês trunks on the end pieces, it is perfect for square and oval faces.

Proving that functionality and style can go together, the versatile Emilie Wallet in exquisite Monogram Empreinte leather is elegance itself.Numerous pockets and an attractive shape make it irresistible.

Functional, very body friendly, and soft to the touch, this is the perfect companion for everyday life. The supple Damier Infini leather makes it ultra-wearable and a myriad of compartments keep things organized.

This striking silk square combines bold color-blocking with a graphic pattern of Louis Vuitton chains, straps and handles in the shape of a Monogram flower.

Our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Its practical layout will appeal to those seeking a strictly functional companion.

Smart and practical, the Jeanne Wallet in Monogram canvas offers endless possibilities. This envelop wallet in Monogram canvas is both ultra feminine and highly adaptable thanks to its three-in-one construction with removable card holder and coin pocket.

Eye-catching, isn’t it? The new Kimono tote combines Monogram canvas with fine calf leather for a riveting graphic effect. Why “Kimono”? The name alludes to the V-cross motif, inspired by the Japanese robe. In the purest tradition of House craftsmanship the bag features long Toron leather handles, a distinctive metallic V signature inspired by an historical advertising of the brand and impeccable edge-dyeing. Both roomy and remarkably light, the Kimono is a pleasure to carry.

Artistic and colorful, our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. This functional version contains only essential diary elements.

Our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Its extra features will accompany our most demanding and sophisticated customers.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The pure lines of the historical Speedy allows an expression of refinement and femininity through exclusive know-how: gold Monogram serti, flower shapes, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.
This elegant bag charm and key holder combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram flowers with graphic stripes inspired by those used to personalize the historic trunks.

Reflecting the playful universe of Louis Vuitton, this ring is adorned with a pair of dice as lucky charms. With numbers made of feminine strass and an engraved Monogram pattern adding an iconic touch, it is a perfect gift.

The Porte-Documents Voyage explores and reinvents Louis Vuitton’s history, making the old new again with vintage LV travel stickers taking on college feel thanks to the imagination of Kim Jones.

A perfect gift, this playful necklace features a duet of dice as lucky charms. The numbers are crafted from feminine strass, while an engraved Monogram pattern adds an iconic touch complemented by the chain's graphic "V" signature.
