en_US_description: The meticulously crafted metal cage of this collectible bag charm opens at a touch to reveal a set of dice decorated with the LV initials and Monogram flowers.

This silk pocket square features motifs of African animals with negative photographic effect, created by the ChapmanÕs brothers. Its bold design will give any look a sophisticated, fashion-forward edge.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.

The Long Beach MM in high-shine Monogram Vernis offers sleek design and practical features: it’s the perfect modern tote. A pair of smooth leather tassels adds a playful touch; a removable zipped pouch keeps small necessities secure and accessible.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's Twist bag, the Twist Lock bracelet in iconic Monogram canvas or Epi leather is accessorized with a feminine tinkling charm, a perfect miniature replica of the emblematic bag.
Ideal for jeans, this stylish belt in Monogram canvas features a new buckle finely engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature.

The same twin Toucans who adorn this season’s Twist handbag appear on this playful bag charm and keyholder. Accented with a palladium “V” signature, the colorful pair will add a personal, summery touch to any bag.
Louis Vuitton's Essential V buckle adds a bold, graphic touch to this stylish and versatile belt in Monogram Reverse canvas. The strap is cut diagonally for a strong visual statement.

Reinterpreting Louis Vuitton's classic Obsession line, which is distinguished by sophisticated Monogram marquetry in the arms, these outsize square-framed sunglasses are a timelessly feminine, glamorous style.
With numerous carry options, the Montaigne BB is a compact alternative for businesswomen who don’t wish to carry too much. And of course it looks beautiful in Monogram Empreinte leather.

Bring even more glamour to your Louis Vuitton bag with this shoulder strap in Monogram coated canvas with an Epi grained cowhide leather lining. It’s super easy to attach and remove thanks to the practical snap hook.

The Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.
The Josh Backpack explores and reinvents Louis Vuitton’s history, making the old new again with vintage LV travel stickers taking on college feel thanks to the imagination of Kim Jones.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The new Mahina Asteria unites a chic, feminine look with the generous size that a woman wants in her favorite go-to bag. Made of remarkably supple perforated leather, its voluptuous lines and fine braided work give this model a timeless, elegant allure.

With a printed stripe that cuts across its Damier Graphite coated canvas, this Vasco Wallet is both sporty and sophisticated. The perfect size to fit in a small bag, it boasts all the essential functionalities you'll find in a Long Wallet: a zipped coin pocket, 10 credit card slots, an internal flat pocket and a large compartment for bills.

The season’s big “college spirit” story plays out on this light-hearted bag charm and key ring. Superbly crafted in varsity hues of red and blue calfskin, it makes a stylish gift: the Calf Leather back can be personalized with hot-stamped initials.

This new calf-leather bracelet reprises the LV buckle of the best-selling Neogram belt. With its stylish double-wrap strap, the Neogram is a timeless yet modern masculine accessory, available in three elegant colors.
This fashion-forward version of the Twist Wallet is crafted from shiny metallic Epi leather. As always the playful Twist turn-lock features an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

The fashionable mini size of Capucines PM lends an intense pop of contrasting colors to wardrobe styles from classic to daring. Finished with shiny color accents, the Capucines PM comes with a removable shoulder strap for casual shoulder or cross-body wear.

2015 brings a fresh new reading of the Lockme. Crafted in a natural soft calf leather with a supple hand, the bag’s on-trend silhouette lends a youthful cachet to any look – especially when carried cross-body or slung casually over the shoulder. The over-scale LV Twist closure in shiny Palladium brass adds an edgy touch.
Mascot is a modern, square shape model in a mix of acetate and metal. The bold, iconic "V" is the center piece of this frame and highlights the strong design of these fashion-forward sunglasses.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.

With details inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship, this handy accessory will accompany every nomadic lifestyle. Available in a range of colors, its playful design is perfect for a bag or pocket.

This season the House launches Freedom, an exclusive calfskin tote with an edgy, moto vibe. It can be styled with zippers open or closed, to change the bag’s shape and reveal side flaps that match contrast handles. The perfect piece for urban lifestyles, finished with a leather-and-metal LV signature.

Artistic and colorful, our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Designed for clients seeking a strictly functional approach.

Slim and chic, the reversible Slender 35mm belt in Taiga leather comes in two timeless and versatile color combinations. The ideal accessory for business suits, it features a finely crafted ardillon buckle in palladium-finished brass.

The successful Charlotte model is modernized with a bold mix of materials, including mirror lenses. They’re also supremely practical thanks to an innovative hinge system that means they can be easily folded flat and carried in a bag or clutch.

Combining the Nemeth rope design on our iconic Damier canvas with black calf leather, this reversible belt can accompany fashion forward statements and more formal silhouettes. A perfect match for our new product lines.

New this season, the Capucines BB in Noir tells an elegant color story: the soft burgundy-gray of the signature flap is a subtle counterpoint to the black Taurillon leather, for an effect as versatile as a neutral, but with a fashion-forward twist.

The printed stripe that cuts across the Damier Graphite coated canvas brings a fun and strong twist to one of our most classical wallets. Large enough to fit your daily essentials, the Brazza slips easily into almost any pocket.

This reversible belt in two complementary shades of Taurillon leather features a leather-covered LV Initiales buckle for a contrasted or tone on tone look. The discreet signature and timeless colors make this belt ideal for both formal and casual wear.

Matching the emblematic Capucines bag, this feminine wallet is ornamented with a delicately crafted iris flower, inspired by the stained glass windows in the historic Vuitton family home in Asnières. Its sleek design is large enough to hold all everyday essentials.

This colorful stole reinterprets the famous universal bandana pattern to incorporate Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers. In soft, airy cotton, it is perfect for hot days in the city and can also be worn as a pareo at the beach.

A stylish and easy-to-wear messenger bag, the new District PM is the ideal companion for everyday life. With its elegant details, lightweight and surprisingly spacious interior, it's the perfect combination of functionality and elegance

These casual-sport style sunglasses feature a playful design mixing gold color with translucent details. The lightweight injected frame is confortable and easy-to-wear, while the aviator shape especially suits square and oval faces.
This reversible scarf in soft, warm wool transforms Louis Vuitton's V motif into a graphic diamond pattern, which is knitted in bold colors for a vibrant, modern look.

Compact, versatile and totally on-trend, this Pochette Voyage MM in Taiga leather can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.
Modern, playful and practical, the Lockme backpack in soft calf leather is given a fresh, summery twist with gradated perforations in the shape of Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers.

With pure lines, a fresh shape, and exquisite details like its leather corners, the Flandrin in Monogram canvas and colorful leather is for those looking for an iconic yet casual bag. It can be carried by hand, on the elbow, or over the shoulder for a more easy-going look.

Available in a range of color options, these fashionable notebooks offer a playful way of taking Louis Vuitton wherever you go. Featuring high quality watermarked paper and Epi leather covers, they are adorned with a metallic LV Circle signature.

With their bubble shape and neon colors, these adorable bag charms are playful must-haves. Two feminine color options in luxurious mink fur will add a pop touch to any bag. Versatile, these "BB" size bag charms offer new usage and can be hooked to the zip-puller of a small Leather Good item.

The season’s stylish colorway features satiny, silvery leather set off with bi-metal eyelets and the signature LV Twist Lock. Bold and modern, the bag is practical too, with a well-organized interior and removable shoulder strap.
As an elegant, modern bag for city living, the Roman PM in cross grained Taïga leather has no parallel. With its specially designed iPad pocket, it also makes an excellent choice for short trips.

Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 collection. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros.    A graphic zebra paired with bicolor stripes give a cool and nomadic look to the vintage Amazone, a compact, functional city bag.

Available in a slimmer version, the Historic bracelet in Monogram Canvas is declined in two new hues of pink  as well as in the classic  Monogram canvas. Made to mix, match and stack, these signed pieces are perfect for gifting.

Louis Vuitton's classic Clémence wallet is an elegant and compact design offering multiple practical features. In iconic Monogram canvas, it is given a playful, feminine feel by its brightly colored leather zipper and lining.

On the season’s accessory A-list is this collectible Bandoulière, finely crafted in multi-hued patent and smooth Epi leather. Designed to customize almost any Louis Vuitton bag, the hook-on strap adds a playful pop of tropical color to neutral outfits.

Must-have pieces for the Monogram lover, these statement accessories are engraved with our iconic pattern. The seasonal range includes an edgy thin cuff as well as a tie clip and cufflinks to complement business attires and our permanent  locket on charm necklace and signet ring.
Thin yet very functional, this Brazza Wallet in Taiga Leather is large enough for all your essentials and still fits easily into a jacket pocket. The two-tone interior adds a touch of fun.

Feminine and playful, the Victorine is also a very practical wallet. Every detail, such as the zipped coin pocket on the edge, has been carefully designed to create an optimal small wallet able to contain as much as a long wallet.
Woven from a blend of cashmere and wool, this fashionable piece features a paisley pattern reinterpreted with lucky charms, sprinkled into a Monogram Flower bouquet.

Featuring an archive drawing that evokes Louis Vuitton's travel DNA, this feminine key holder is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods. A perfect gift, it can be personalized with hot-stamped initials on its rear side.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature, this elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials.

Designed in collaboration with iconic NYC skate brand Supreme, this version of the iPhone 7 Folio brings downtown style to a highly functional case. The adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, securely holds the phone to protect it.
The iconic Speedy bag is given a fresh, feminine feel for summer in Damier Azur canvas overlaid with a  surprising Monogram print adapted from the Louis Vuitton archives.

Product available in select stores only Meticulously crafted, this leather tab key holder references Louis Vuitton's leather goods heritage. A perfect gift, it may be personalized with the owner's initials on the back.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine is a optimal compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Monogram canvas featuring an adorable bird motif composed of classic House details, it offers quick access to credit cards and personal belongings.

This chic little bag has a secret: it's roomier than it looks. The cleverly designed "wave" base provides extra space for storing necessities. The new Twist features an updated version of the signature turn-lock. Rendered with a 3D bombé effect, the metal closure has a modern, architectural feel. To open the bag, a single smooth twist fits the letter "L" into the "V", with a satisfying click. The convertible chain handle can be worn cross-body or hung gracefully from the shoulder.

A must-have office accessory, this playful pencil pouch combines iconic Louis Vuitton signatures with an elegant look. Monogram canvas, VVN leather and the LV Circle motif add branded touches, while the color will brighten up your desk.
Ideal for everyday use, this luxuriously soft Monogram Neo Denim shawl is subtle and very feminine. Entirely weaven in jacquard, it features the Louis Vuitton signature and the Monogram pattern.

This Smart Wallet in Damier Graphite is as functional as it is sophisticated. Compact, it offers a quick access to the bills and cards inside while an external zipped gusset pocket makes it easy to get to your coins.
This Alma BB has a metallic finish that makes it perfect for evening wear. Femininity and elegance combine beautifully in one of the House's most iconic shapes.
Made from supple Utah calf leather fitted with aged-silver hardware, the Canyon Messenger unites a relaxed, urban vibe with craftsmanship, comfort and functionality. The PM holds a day’s essentials;
This elegant silk square is printed with a romantic pattern inspired by the beauty of coral and featuring a stylized Monogram flower in the center.

Kabuki-style graphics were the breakout story of Cruise SS 18. This new charm features a mask detail from the show; it slides to reveal a second disc with the reverse Monogram motif. The silver-finished metal is finely engraved with House signatures.
This elegant bag charm and key holder combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram flowers with graphic stripes inspired by those used to personalize the historic trunks.

These striking sunglasses feature luxurious Taiga leather details, including a removable part on the top bar. The large aviator shape is ideal for square and oval faces. Available with plain colour or monogram lenses.

This modern mask shape features an Essential V insert in the middle of the lens, a tribute to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton. The cylinder-shape temples, engraved with the Monogram design, complete the iconic style. Statement sunglasses for a wow effect, their mask shape is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

A genuine fashion accessory, this bandoulière strap will turn any bag into an object of desire. True to the codes of the House, the craftsmanship pays tribute to Louis Vuitton’s heritage of fine leatherwork.

Perfect for every day, the Lockmeto in soft calfskin combines a spacious, functional design with sophisticated, feminine details, including swinging tassels and the LV twist-lock, a signature of the Lockme line.

Trendy and elegant, the Sorbonne perfectly incarnates Louis Vuitton’s tradition of “travelling with style”. Its urban yet feminine design, small size and flawless functionality will make it your go-to bag for everyday life.

This finely detailed bag charm and key holder comes in the shape of a cute bird designed with Louis Vuitton historic rivets and iconic V signature on Monogram canvas. It can be personalized on the back with the owner's initials, making it an ideal gift.

Celebrating the Chinese New Year, this beautifully crafted chain bracelet features a rooster whose design plays with iconic Louis Vuitton details, including corners and studs referencing the historic trunks.

Braiding and beads give this new Epi Twist bag a cool, creative edge. House craftsmanship shines in the intricate leather embroidery and finely wrought metal accents. On-trend and ultra-covetable, it can be carried over the shoulder or worn cross-body.

Easy chic silhouette maker, the Tournelle PM is a go-anywhere carryall for work and play. Thanks to the leather piping, its shape changes depending on whether you hold it by the handles or wear it over the shoulder with its long removable strap. For those who love the Popincourt, the Tournelle is another classic Monogram shoulder bag with a pop of color for your collection.

Sparkling, luminous Rose Cuivre Monogram-embossed patent calf leather makes this Zippy Wallet eye-catchingly fresh. The Zippy is one of our most practical and versatile wallets with numerous compartments and an all-round zip closure.

Slim and sober, the iPhone 7 Plus & 8 Plus Folio has two inside flat pockets for daily essentials like business or credit cards. It easily fits in a pocket or a briefcase. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.
Designed around the iconic "V" signature, the new District sunglasses are made of metal and contrasting materials.  The Damier-pattern accentuates the style of this fashionable square-framed model.
This elegant tie is woven with a tone-on-tone Monogram pattern, creating a subtle textured effect that makes it ideal for business wear.

Nicolas Ghesquière keeps on twisting the backpack shape, with this cute Mini cross-body version. This season, it is given an even more fashionable twist with this hypnotic Monogram Infrarouge version.

Artistic and colorful, our 2017 Agenda Refill brings a touch of poetry to each day of the year with a selection of poems linked to the letters that make up Louis Vuitton. This complete version offers a host of extra features.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art.  One of our most iconic and versatile models, the Zippy wallet is adorned with this exclusive collaboration: gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

This chic silk bandeau is printed with an abstract design created from a combination of classic and modern Louis Vuitton motifs, including stripes, chains and locks, while its reverse side features the iconic Monogram pattern.

The LV Initiales line of masculine accessories adds sleek sophistication to business or evening looks. The tie clip is impeccably crafted of polished palladium, while the coordinated cufflinks mix metal with natural horn or mother-of-pearl.
A collectible key holder and bag charm with a functional pocket knife. Meticulously crafted, the pocket knife, which also has scissor and nail file functions, is sheathed in Monogram canvas.

This edgy, rigid cuff bracelet reinterprets the Maison's iconic Damier pattern with a masculine and graphic touch. An accessible piece, it offers a masculine association of black enamel and palladium finishing.

Inspired by the iconic rabbit, often played by Jeff Koons in his work, this bag charm will spice up any Louis Vuitton bag thanks to its original shape and bright colours. Louis Vuitton’s refinement is expressed through the work of the metallic structure and the choice of the leather.
This classic business tie subtly references Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern with discreet Monogram motifs printed in lines within the stripes.

Louis Vuitton paired with Fragment Design to create this exclusive pack in new Monogram Eclipse Flash, with a black band and reflective trim. Cool and sporty with a modern hiking spirit, it’s a stylish choice for city streets or paths less traveled.

The House’s iconic jeune fille bag gets a timely twist with this Saint Cloud in Epi leather enhanced with modern details such as a playful leather tassel and trendy studs. The daring color combination and contrasting edge-dyeing gives it a joyously youthful feel.
Perfect for travel or everyday, the Cosmetic Pouch is as sophisticated as ever in refined Epi leather. A rainbow of vibrant colours to choose from adds a vivacious twist to this iconic accessory.
The Kasai is the ideal accessory for today's man. Suitably compact yet practical with many sophisticated details, its Taiga leather sports a matte finish for a refined, masculine look.

One of our most iconic and versatile models, this Zippy Wallet in soft Epi leather with its bold fashion print delivers a sporty resort punch. Slip it into your bag or carry it by hand as a mini clutch!

Compact and slim, this Slender Wallet in Damier Graphite canvas carries all your essentials and still fits into a front or back pocket with ease. The printed stripe that highlights the canvas's geometric pattern makes this classic new again.

Inspired by the golden embroidery seen in the Spring Summer 17 show, this Petite Malle gets a delicate jewel-like ornamental that underline its shape with a precious frame: hundreds of shiny sequins and facetted glass beads embroidered with a thin golden thread, that harmoniously hem the edges of the satiny smooth calfskin.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the Slender Wallet, created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the new Damier Latitude pattern, for a modern,  masculine and yet practical piece. Compact and slim, the Slender Wallet carries all your essentials and still fits into a front or back pocket with ease.

Colorful Kabuki motifs – a big story from the Cruise SS 18 show – are screen-printed against a background of iconic Monogram jacquard to create this supremely stylish shawl. Generous and enveloping, it is woven of a warm blend of silk and wool.

This colorful silk square reinterprets Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers in a graphic, Japan-inspired spirit: "kamon" means coat-of-arms in Japanese. This elegant accessory will add a sophisticated, feminine touch to any outfit.
Soft and cozy pure-wool accessories in punchy fuchsia perfect to pop up winter outfits.

Oversized Kabuki stickers in brilliant hues give this new iteration of the Speedy a high-fashion twist. The mix of printed Monogram canvas and colorful Epi leather creates a pleasing play of textures on this flawlessly crafted, collectible piece.
Mascot is a modern, square shape model in a mix of acetate and metal. The bold, iconic "V" is the center piece of this frame and highlights the strong design of these fashion-forward sunglasses.

This graphic necklace reinterprets our iconic Damier pattern in a masculine association of black enamel and palladium finishing. Versatile, it can be worn with either the Damier pattern or Louis Vuitton signature on top thanks to bi-faced plates.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The iconic Neverfull is twisted within this collaboration with refinement and femininity through exclusive know-how: gold Monogram serti, flower shapes, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration. Ultimate luxury, the internal zipped clutch is animated and can be worn by itself as a clutch.

Precious miniatures of the iconic padlock and key from our trunks tell the story of Louis Vuitton and the art of travel. The exquisite craftsmanship on a variety of materials -- metal, enamel and sparkly strass -- is a testament to the House's know-how.

The iconic Louis Vuitton pilot model has an even more luxurious touch this season with tiny rhinestones inserted across the metal bridge and around each lens. The pilot shape particularly flatters square and oval faces.
With a knitted pattern inspired by Louis Vuitton's historic Damier canvas, this warm winter scarf combines the luxurious feel of cashmere with a casual, elegant style.

This signature belt does double duty: classic Monogram canvas, perfect for casual looks, reverses to grained-calf leather in Rose Bruyère (Wild Rose) for more sophisticated silhouettes. The piece is finished with a shiny golden LV Initiales buckle.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the District messenger, created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the oversized  new Damier Latitude pattern, for a modern, masculine look.

Inspired by the romantic vibe of Louis Vuitton's Spring/Summer 2017 fashion show, the Flower Lace theme transposes the collection's key lace story into an intricately crafted print incorporating the Monogram flowers. Sophisticated and feminine, this silk and wool shawl is ideal for day-to-evening wear.

Matching the emblematic Capucines bag, this elegant wallet is given a refined, feminine touch by Monogram flower ornaments, which are fixed by hand to its flap, creating a crown-like effect. Its compact design is large enough to hold all everyday essentials.

This elegant Brazza in Epi leather & Monogram Canvas is a modern tribute to Louis Vuitton’s classic signatures, mixing colors and materials for a look as playful as iconic. It’s a highly functional wallet that slips easily into a jacket pocket.

The new Saint Placide chain bag combine Monogram canvas with supple, colored leather, accented by a gleaming golden clasp borrowed from historic House trunks. The perfect size for day-to-night wear, it easily fits a long wallet and other essentials.

Perfect for business or casual wear, this stylish scarf in wool and cashmere is woven with trunk stamp motifs taken from the Louis Vuitton archives. This heritage pattern was one of the key statements of the Fall/Winter 2016 fashion show.

The 2017 LV League collection reveals a tribute to Louis Vuitton history both past and present. It associates iconic labels inspired from Gaston-Louis Vuitton collection and college style ones .This ultra-functional Zippy Vertical Wallet offers the capacity of a small bag in a wallet.

Supremely practical with numerous pockets and compartments, the Zippy Wallet Vertical in Damier Graphite canvas is the stylish way to carry your money, cards and coins. The interior is a unique construction of canvas and colored soft Damier Infini leather that brings a subtle twist.

A new take on the trendy Dynamo belt, this casual model's signed and bicolor webbing strap embodies the spirit of effortless cool. The Maison's iconic V Gaston logo adds a nautical touch to a model that coordinates perfectly with this season's shoes.

Product available in select stores only Designed in collaboration with iconic NYC skate brand Supreme, this Bumbag is inspired from the downtown spirit. Worn cross-body as seen on the Show, it will bring a cool and trendy touch to any look.

These distinctive cuff bracelets feature the Maison's iconic Monogram canvas for a genuine must-have piece. The range reinterprets the Monogram in three complementary colors, in a refined tribute to Louis Vuitton's unique know-how.

The famous Louis Vuitton silk square becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a silk twill base embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

The Dandy Briefcase is for the modern businessman looking for an elegant and distinctive business bag. As functional as it is stylish, it will follow you everywhere: as much at work as during your business trips thanks to its removable strap adjusted for Horizon luggage.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. The ultra-functional Zippy XL offers the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It is large enough to hold a smartphone (in a specific pocket), keys and passport, in addition to credit cards and cash. Elegant in Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather, it can be hand carried  for a sophisticated look.
Mascot is a modern, square shape model in a mix of acetate and metal. The bold, iconic "V" is the center piece of this frame and highlights the strong design of these fashion-forward sunglasses.

A bag to fit any mood or silhouette, the new Cléry Pochette in Epi leather can be worn on the shoulder, cross-body (merci, adjustable strap) or carried by the finely detailed top handle. Surprisingly roomy, it is offered in a bouquet of fashionable shades.

The fashionable mini size of Capucines BB lends an intense pop of contrasting colors to wardrobe styles from classic to daring. Finished with shiny silver color accents, the Capucines BB comes with a removable long shoulder strap for casual shoulder or cross-body wear.

With feminine cabochons providing a subtle play on colors, these versatile long necklaces can also be used as sunglasses chains. Featuring a mix of iconic Louis Vuitton signatures, they are available in two complementary color options.

A must-have feminine style with a wow effect thanks to the striking cat eye shape and intricate facet work on the front. The large temples display an oversize Essential V motif - a tribute to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton. Iconic studs evoke the Maisonês historic trunks.

Available in a range of color options, these fashionable notebooks offer a playful way of taking Louis Vuitton wherever you go. Featuring high quality watermarked paper and Epi leather covers, they are adorned with a metallic LV Circle signature.

Combining fine-grained calf leather with iconic Monogram canvas, this stylish, trendy compact wallet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Double V bag. The original double flap conceals a secret pocket, which is ideal for tickets or coins.
Featuring the iconic LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt comes in two contrasting shades of supple and grained Taurillon leather, effectively offering two looks in one.
Colorful and trendy, the Emilie case in Monogram canvas and VVN leather protects precious sunnies from scratches. The LV Circle charm on the zip pull adds a chic signature touch.
Luxurious Epi leather makes the Neverfull MM suitable for every occasion. Effortlessly practical, it is an ideal tote or the laces can be tightened to create a more compact, chic city bag.

Proving that functionality and beautiful design can go together, the Emilie Wallet is elegance itself in supple Monogram Canvas with a fresh lining color. Numerous pockets and an attractive shape make it irresistible.

This feminine bag charm reinterprets the Maison's Monogram Flowers and the LV Initials signature in a light and summery spirit. It is the perfect accessory to your BB size bag or your Small Leather Good item.

Slightly oversized for a trendy twist, this fashion forward model highlights our transversal Essential V signature. With its lightweight mix of materials, and thin metal temples, the cat-eye shape has a modern retro touch.
A perfect gift, this stylish silk twill square is printed with emblematic Louis Vuitton details - leather straps, metal chains and padlocks - on a background of the iconic Monogram pattern.

An exclusive gradient color effect gives this version of the beloved Capucines extra fashion currency. The MM model can be carried by hand or over the elbow, with the flap in (to display the LV initials) or out (to show the Monogram flower ornament).

The perfect summer companion, this effortlessly chic Girolata in Mahina calfskin is versatility incarnate. Its distinctive flap can be worn two ways: outside to reveal the outline of a Monogram flower, or inside to show the LV initials.

The pattern on this silk bandeau playfully references all Louis Vuitton's emblematic locks and clasps. It can be worn as a scarf or headband, while its narrow shape makes it easy to tie around the handles of a bag.

Inspired by the Amazon rainforest, this Twist Exotic Birds limited edition is adorned with a hummingbird motif, intricately embroidered in multi-colored sequins. Épi inspires Nicolas Ghesquière. His fresh interpretation of the Cluny bag will thrill aficionados of the signature House leather. The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour palette totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

Our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Its basic diary content is designed for clients seeking a strictly functional approach.

This colorful stole in soft wool plays with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern to create an intriguing blurred effect. It is a fashionable accessory whose generous size gives it a cozy, enveloping feel.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the Pocket Organizer  created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. Pocket Organizer slips easily into any pocket or handbag.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's association with the America's Cup,  this bag charm and key holder made of a reflective cord features a functional whistle on a nautical knot, making it the perfect gift both playful and useful for sailing enthousiasts.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. Crafted of grained Taurillon leather, this city bag that takes care of business, with ample room for papers and files.
Luxurious Epi leather makes the Neverfull MM suitable for every occasion. Effortlessly practical, it is an ideal tote or the laces can be tightened to create a more compact, chic city bag.

Remarkably thin and structured, the Dandy Briefcase Slim is for modern businessmen looking for a stylish workbag. The nice craftsmanship details will appeal to connoisseurs clients. This new model is proposed in Epi leather for business clients who want a discreet Louis Vuitton Signature.

This stylish over-sized bag in supple Monogram Eclipse coated canvas exterior is the perfect hold-all bag to carry all your daily belongings: keys, wallet, books, and even your iPad. Ideal for those looking to marry form and function.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Cabas light combines both  House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity thanks to the shape. Extra-light and comfortable, it allows a hand or shoulder carry for a stylish touch.

The lovely Zippy coin purse is given a fresh and feminine feel for summer in Damier Azur canvas overlaid with a splashy Monogram print adapted from the Louis Vuitton archives. Compact yet functional, it can be either carried in a bag or even in a pocket.

In iconic Monogram canvas with a brightly colored lining inspired by the covers of Louis Vuitton City Guides, the iPhone 7 Plus Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life
Glossy, cute and girly, the smallest Chain Louise blends iconic elegance with ultra-feminine charm. Additional functionality and versatility thanks to a delicate removable chain.

With its pure lines and sophisticated details, the Louis Vuitton Very Chain Bag in supple Cuir Plume and Cuir Ecume leathers is your new must-have bag. The delicate chain and crafted V signature provide glamour while the flap and lock closure keep your essentials safe inside. Very body friendly, thanks to its soft feel and very light weight. The silky & very transparent leather played in contrasted with a small grained version lets discretly appear the Monogram pattern

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art.  The timeless envelop shape of the Sarah wallet lay emphasis on the femininity and refinement through exclusive know how : gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

The ideal evening companion, the Soft clutch in sensual calf leather combines style and convenience. Its supple, body-friendly shape is enhanced by emblematic Louis Vuitton details: an LV turn-lock closure and removable nautical-inspired chain.

Supple and easy to wear, this playful bracelet extends the Maison's iconic alphabet motif to spell love. A perfect gift, the graphic composition offers a subtle reference to our LV initials signature.

The elegant Anton backpack makes a polished impression in any professional setting. Fashioned of durable Taiga leather, it features impeccably crafted heritage details: note the top handle, subtle tone-on-tone signature tab, and metal zip pulls.

This warm wool hat is knitted using an innovative technique to create a 3D effect. Its bold pattern was inspired by Louis Vuitton's Fall/Winter 2016 fashion show, which played with trunk stamp motifs taken from the House archives.

Slightly oversized for a trendy twist, this fashion forward model highlights our transversal Essential V signature. With its lightweight mix of materials, and thin metal temples, the cat-eye shape has a modern retro touch.

The charming Alma BB traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This miniature version easily holds keys, wallet, smartphone and lipstick. With a strap that adjusts the bag to waist or hip height, the Alma BB can be worn across the body for hands-free ease. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Épi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colours.

Accented with sporty blue lacquer, this refined LV Initiales piece is crafted of polished palladium-finished brass. The key ring and snap hook are both meticulously engraved with the “Louis Vuitton” signature. A timelessly stylish item for gifting.

Get the statutory & desirable attitude with the Very Tote Bag. Supple slender handles provide a modern look and carrying comfort while the V signature and the beautiful nods give it a rich, bright feel. The cleverly organized interior has 2 large compartments as well as a zipped pocket?for your valuables.

This stylish scarf interprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern in a subtle, modern way through texture, pattern and colour. Its light, airy cotton knit makes it ideal for mid-season, while its discreet design complements both casual and business looks.

The elegant, envelope-style Pallas wallet in Monogram canvas is given a fresh, feminine feel by brightly colored leather trim. Louis Vuitton's emblematic S-lock guarantees security, while inside there is ample space for all everyday essentials.

An incredible jewel, this Capucines BB evening bag is the sublime result of painstaking House craftsmanship. Each of the 1200 tone-on-tone beads is cut and painted by hand, then embroidered one by one onto black calf leather, to recreate the Paris skyline.

This edgy Pochette Plate in shiny metallic Epi leather comes with a fashionnable slot handclasp. When carried, this avant-garde Pochette Plate will adorn your hand with the essential V signature jewel.

With its eye-catching design in gold and plexiglass, this subtly branded photo frame incorporates lozines and corner pieces from Louis Vuitton's historic trunks. A fun piece, it can also be used as a paperweight on your desk.

In iconic Monogram canvas with a brightly colored lining inspired by the covers of Louis Vuitton City Guides, the iPhone 7 & 8 Folio is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.
This iconic Zippy Wallet in dark blue comes  with Monogram Flower metallic pins. This  rock'n'roll and edgy companion will keep  your belongings held and organized.

Aficionados of the iconic Damier pattern will appreciate this masculine bracelet, accented with a medal in shiny palladium-finished brass, engraved on one side with LV Initiales and on the other with the Damier “rice grain” motif.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. Your iconic travel companion Keepall is twisted with exclusive details: the gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

The House’s iconic jeune fille bag gets a timely twist with this Saint Cloud in Epi leather enhanced with modern details such as a playful leather tassel and trendy studs. The daring color combination and contrasting edge-dyeing gives it a joyously youthful feel.

Incomparably thin, this sophisticated Compact Wallet is fashioned from a mix of grained and smooth leather with double stitching. It’s compact enough to easily slip in the back pocket of a pair of jeans.

This colorful stole in soft wool plays with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern to create an intriguing blurred effect. It is a fashionable accessory whose generous size gives it a cozy, enveloping feel.

The Dandy Wallet’s ultra-functional design gives you the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It can be carried under the arm, inside a bag, or by hand for a more sophisticated look thanks to its removable wrist strap.

This silk square features an abstract Monogram flower created from a combination of classic and modern Louis Vuitton motifs, including stripes, chains and locks. Timeless and versatile, it can be worn in many different ways.

Fashioned in Damier Ebène coated canvas decorated with an exclusive Chapman Brothers illustration of a lion, this clutch is for the modern man looking for a fashionable portfolio with which to transport documents and other daily essentials.

With its pure lines and the subtle petal-like curve of its flap, the Florine embodies feminine elegance. This everyday bag, has the perfect size to carry and organise your daily essentials, thanks to its two interior compartments. Very versatile, the Florine can be carried by hand or over the shoulder, with the flap inside or out… As you wish.

A miniature version of the LV Initials Belt, the LV Initials 14MM Taurillon Reversible Bracelet is timeless and contemporary. Crafted with soft Taurillon leather and the iconic LV Initials buckle, it is reversible to reveal another color.
This striking silk bandeau transforms Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram into a vibrant, graphic pattern, while the rooster motif with its Monogram flower eye is a playful nod to the Chinese New Year.

A new take on the trendy Dynamo belt, this casual model's signed and bicolor webbing strap embodies the spirit of effortless cool. The Maison's iconic V Gaston logo adds a nautical touch to a model that coordinates perfectly with this season's shoes.
With numerous carry options, the Montaigne BB is a compact alternative for businesswomen who don’t wish to carry too much. And of course it looks beautiful in Monogram Empreinte leather.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.
A revamped version of our iconic Check It model combining Damier canvas on one side and Damier Infini on the other, this new urban and easy-to-wear bracelet will provide a modern twist to any outfit.

Inspired by the architectural spirit of the show, the Chain-it bag features sleek lines and flawless design. Statement chain embellishment, with characteristic nautical inspired design, reminds of Louis Vuitton’s travel DNA, while its bold and smart closing system unveils a central button with LV circle signature. Seen on the runway, this exclusive shape is set to become one of the most exciting pieces of the season. A fashionable take on iconic Monogram canvas.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

This envelope style Sarah wallet combines an exterior in Monogram canvas with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots. The adorable polar bears, playing with iconic Louis Vuitton trunks and luggage, transform this classic Sarah Wallet into a stylish object of whimsy.

Fashioned from Taurillon leather with precious python leather pads on its four corners as well as its handle, this already emblematic bag takes on added allure. The Capucines PM comes with a removable shoulder strap for casual shoulder or cross-body wear.

This elegant bag charm combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram flowers with graphic stripes inspired by those used to personalize the historic trunks. Its BB size makes it the perfect complement to BB bags and small leather goods.
Ideal for mid-season, this versatile wool and silk stole combines the iconic Monogram pattern with stripes in muted colors for a fashionable vintage look.

For Cruise 2017, Iconic Speedy 30 has been refreshed with "Louis Vuitton Race" colors & mix of emblematic signatures : Epi grain, iconic Damier & Louis Vuitton statement logo. A bold & fashion print on versatile Speedy 30 with strap shape, for a flashy & sporty resort look.
The Happy Monogram silk square is printed with a modern, multi-colored interpretation of the iconic Monogram pattern. Ideal as a gift, it can be worn in different ways to express your personal style.
Woven with the Monogram pattern in a subtly contrasting shade to create an intriguing "shadow" effect, this giant silk square will bring a modern, feminine touch to any look.
The Happy Monogram silk square is printed with a modern, multi-colored interpretation of the iconic Monogram pattern. Ideal as a gift, it can be worn in different ways to express your personal style.
This feminine model is adorned with a delicate enameled charm in the shape of our iconic Petite Malle on a sophisticated bi-color double strap. It is also available in Monogram canvas strap.

The ideal evening companion, the Soft clutch in sensual calf leather combines style and convenience. Its supple, body-friendly shape is enhanced by emblematic Louis Vuitton details: an LV turn-lock closure and removable nautical-inspired chain.

Designed in 1932 to transport bottles of Champagne, the Noé returns for Spring 17 as the Néonoé, an on-trend bucket bag in supple Monogram canvas with colorful calf-leather accents and an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Ideal for the business traveler, the Icare in Damier Graphite canvas with the classic leather nametag and iconic stripes gives you that timeless briefcase style. It’s ultra-functional with numerous compartments for a laptop, files and even some clothes. The removable Horizon strap means it fits perfectly on the Horizon luggage for hands-free travel.

The essential accessory for the modern traveller, this passport cover in coated canvas combines style with practicality. It boasts four credit card slots and two flying pockets for easier access to your passport.
Crafted from masculine Damier Graphite canvas, the extra-flat Pince Wallet easily slips into a jacket or trouser pocket. Its functional design features an articulated clip to hold tickets and notes.

A genuine fashion accessory, this bandoulière strap will turn any bag into an object of desire. True to the codes of the House, the craftsmanship pays tribute to Louis Vuitton’s heritage of fine leatherwork.

Trendy and elegant, the Sorbonne perfectly incarnates Louis Vuitton’s tradition of “travelling with style”. Its urban yet feminine design, small size and flawless functionality will make it your go-to bag for everyday life.

With 120 silver LV studs in two different sizes, this hypnotic Love Note is a stylish tribute to the House’s trunk making heritage. Its supple, body-friendly shape is complemented by emblematic details: the LV turn-lock closure and a removable nautical chain.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. For the collaboration, the House developed a stylish solution to organize daily essentials. The flat pouch perfectly wears gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. A new chain has been created to enable to wear the pouch outside as inside a bag. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected/surprising collaboration.

The LV Circle that adorns this Pochette Jour GM evokes Louis Vuitton’s first travel trunks, decorated at the time with this distinctive mark. Big enough to fit A4 documents, it can be used as a bag inside a bigger bag or hand-carried for a modern, and trendier look.
This silk pocket square combines Louis Vuitton's graphic V signature with dynamic lines and bold colors evoking the America's Cup universe.

The new V Square line offers a fresh, graphic take on a House signature. The contrast of brushed and polished palladium adds a sophisticated touch. These statement pieces are finely crafted, with precision cutting and flawless engraving

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 25 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

As feminine as it is functional, the Victorine is our first compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Damier Ebene canvas with a colorful leather lining, its ingeniously designed interior holds almost as much as a long wallet.

Available in two natural colors, this jewel-like bracelet in calf leather features a locking system inspired by the handles of the Maison's legendary trunk. Casual and chic, its metallic piece is engraved with a discrete Louis Vuitton signature.

With an elegant Nano Monogram design engraved on its cylinder-shape temples and iconic LV studs on the front, this easy-to-wear model will accompany any outfit. The feminine pilot shape is a perfect match for oval and square face shapes.
This glamorous design features a black and gold engraved Monogram design on the front and temples, with classic black lenses. A strong iconic style.

Perfect mix of Louis Vuitton’s heritage and new codes established by Nicolas Ghesquière, City Steamer features a pure design with flawless functionality.  This elegant New Classic is reinterpreted this season in cool and trendy Epi, an effortless take on this “Essentiel de Jour”.

The essential accessory for the modern traveller, this passport cover in coated canvas combines style with practicality. It boasts four credit card slots and two flying pockets for easier access to your passport.
The Kasai is the ideal accessory for today's man. Suitably compact yet practical with many sophisticated details, its Damier Graphite canvas sports a matte finish for a refined, masculine look.
Graphic and modern, the Sarah Tuileries Wallet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with a distinctive rounded flap and sides in contrasting colors of soft leather.

This Multiple Wallet in Epi leather & Monogram Canvas is a modern tribute to Louis Vuitton’s classic signatures, mixing colors and materials for a look as playful as iconic. Compact yet highly functional, it fits into any pocket.

The iris is a talisman for the Vuitton family, present in the garden and ancestral home at Asnières. For Fall, the House adorns the Capucines BB bag in Marengo Taurillon with a delicate iris charm: suspended from a leather string, it adds a fun, feminine accent.
Ideal for casual and urban wear, this belt in Monogram canvas features a new, Western-inspired version of the iconic LV Initiales buckle.

The Logomania Shine scarf is a perfect way to brighten cold days. Its blend of wool, silk and lurex yarns creates a lustrous effect, while a jacquard technique is used to reproduce Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern for a bold signature look.

Reflecting the playful universe of Louis Vuitton, this ring is adorned with a pair of dice as lucky charms. With numbers made of feminine strass and an engraved Monogram pattern adding an iconic touch, it is a perfect gift.

Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 collection. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros.  With its leather wrap handle, the versatile Pochette Volga in Damier Ebene is a bag clutch that is always ready to get up and go.

This statement frameês double lens design features a pilot shape inserted into a mask for an edgy and striking look. Inspired by the Maisonês iconic Petite Malle, this model is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

Available in a rainbow of different lens colors, these stylish sunglasses are decorated with iconic studs that evoke the Maison's trunks: lining the edges of each sunlens, they highlight the design's perfect pilot shape.
For the dynamic businesswoman, the Montaigne GM is ideal. Its smartly designed interior is structured to carry all the essentials, while Monogram Empreinte leather adds a touch of sophistication.
This smart yet chic cardholder in Taiga leather slips easily into a pocket. It can hold credit cards, transport tickets and business cards in its four slots and central pocket.

Airy V embossed finishing, reminding the V of Vuitton, brings a graphic touch to essential Louise GM. This animation offers a trendy take on timeless Black & Nude colours and glamorous Red. To create this design, smooth leather has been embossed with a thin foam backing, ensuring a light padded result. Louise GM offers a great capacity of storage to please active women & its delicate chain allows an elegant shoulder carry.

The reversible Pull It bracelet delivers double style points with its combination of Damier canvas and colored calf leather. The clasp is fashioned of palladium-finished brass, engraved with Damier checks and the “Louis Vuitton Paris” signature.
This Twist MM in raw Epi denim decorated with LV metal pin buttons has an Americana Rock and Roll vibe that makes this the ultimate casual chic bag.

Compact, versatile and totally on-trend, this Pochette Voyage MM in Damier Graphite coated canvas can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The iconic Neverfull is twisted within this collaboration with refinement and femininity through exclusive know-how: gold Monogram serti, flower shapes, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration. Ultimate luxury, the internal zipped clutch is animated and can be worn by itself as a clutch.

A must-have office accessory, this playful pencil pouch combines iconic Louis Vuitton signatures with an elegant look. Monogram canvas, VVN leather and the LV Circle motif add branded touches, while the color will brighten up your desk.

The Dandy Wallet’s ultra-functional design gives you the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It can be carried under the arm, inside a bag, or by hand for a more sophisticated look thanks to its removable wrist strap.
Featuring the iconic LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt comes in two contrasting shades of supple and grained Taurillon leather, effectively offering two looks in one.

The Vivienne NM is the perfect desirable tiny bag for every  youthful silhouette. The leather handle, the grained leather, the sensual round shape and the delicate Louis Vuitton Monogram signature add softness to the bag for a refined allure. The bold Kaki brings a modern touch to the Vivienne NM.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17, transposing the well-known Brogue pattern to the Pochette Métis in a bold and modern fashion statement. Its trendy shape is perfect to fit different styles.

Combining fine-grained calf leather with iconic Monogram canvas, this stylish, trendy compact wallet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Double V bag. The original double flap conceals a secret pocket, which is ideal for tickets or coins.

model: SAC JEUNE FILLE MNG FASHION G.
en_US_description: The One Handle Flap Bag is the architectural piece of the show with its sleek folded shape & graphic mix of materials. Refined details are tribute to Louis Vuitton's DNA : brackets & lock inspired by historical trunks and nametag reminding of the travel spirit of the House. With its large capacity, MM size is the perfect daily companion.

The new Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear. For those who love the Manhattan, the Tuileries also offers a top handle & shoulder strap for the sophisticated urban lifestyle.

Completely reimagined to perfectly pair with the Retiro city bag, the envelope-style Sarah Wallet takes on striking modernity thanks to the colourful and architectural leather patches that bring a dashing contemporary feel to the classic Monogram canvas. The ingenious interior features a variety of pockets.

Easy chic silhouette maker, the Tournelle MM is a go-anywhere carryall for work and play. Thanks to the leather piping, its shape changes depending on whether you hold it with its comfortable handles or removable shoulder strap

These delicate necklaces play on Louis Vuitton's iconic codes in a tribute to the Maison's history and playful spirit. Available as single pendants or as a multi-charm necklace, they are the perfect gifts to mix-and-match and to play on accumulation.
This striking silk square transforms Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram into a vibrant, graphic pattern, while the rooster motif with its Monogram flower eye is a playful nod to the Chinese New Year.

With its refined buckle in golden-finished brass, this sleek new belt pays tribute to the House's trunk-making ("Malletier") heritage. A  LV Circle detail at the end of the strap adds the finishing touch to a timeless and elegant accessory.
Rich, contemporary Taurillon leather is adorned with the elegent iconic LV. A soft yet sturdy belt that that dresses to casual attire.

The most structured of the iconic Louis Vuitton handbags. The original was the creation of Gaston Vuitton, who named it for the Alma Bridge, a span that connects two fashionable Paris neighbourhoods. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Épi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colours.

The Twist was first presented in Cruise 2015 and quickly became a New Classic. Fashioned in pink Epi Jean leather, a unique printing and embossing technique that gives leather the visual effect of denim fabric, and paired with smooth black leather, this Twist PM brings a touch of fashionable femininity to any outfit.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 25 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Pleasingly classic lines and supple Taiga leather make the Anton Pochette an ideal option for every day. Compact and comfortable to carry, this new model features refined detailing: witness the discreet metal signature on the bag’s front pocket.

This iconic new design plays on the all-over multicolor revamped Monogram print from the FW17 range. Crafted from silk twill, it is a perfect gift that also well-suited to sophisticated looks and more casual attitudes.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with bright red leather for a highly colored silhouette.

This effortlessly elegant cashmere and silk stole literally envelops you in a blanket of delicate softness. The iconic leopard pattern by Stephen Sprouse has been revitalized with hints of pop colours that to liven things up.

Designed in 1932 to transport bottles of Champagne, the Noé returns for Spring 17 as the NéoNoé, an on-trend bucket bag in supple Monogram canvas with colorful calf-leather accents and an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry.
Compact form and supreme comfort come together in this easy-to-wear messenger-style bag. With its magnetic closure and zipped pocket on the back, it's as functional as it is tasteful.

A statement accessory coming from the Spring-Summer 2016 Show, the Tassel bag charm comes in both our iconic Monogram canvas or the new Blanc Gamma version, along with calf leather in this season’s pink color.

In creating the Fragrance Travel Cases, Louis Vuitton applies its savoir-faire and mastery in custom-designing the perfect case for transporting and protecting each item of one’s personal belongings. The 100ML travel case conserves and protects your perfume bottle, closing securely with a buckle. Slip it into your bag in every situation.The 100ml travel case can also be personalized in store to the initials of your choice.
A reversible scarf in wool and cashmere featuring the iconic Monogram logo in an all-over design.

For Cruise 2017, the City Steamer has been reinterpreted in an audacious & futuristic version. Each pocket is highly crafted with Louis Vuitton engraved studs on a smooth leather base. Flawless functionalitity & subtle sophistication make this City Steamer the perfect urban companion.

Louise EW is the ultimate elegant piece for evening outfit. This season, this pure clutch is animated in precious silver calfskin, making it the perfect gleaming accessory, enhanced by tone on tone Epi like resin lock for the jewel touch.
With its sober design, this elegant Folio in Monogram is the stylish way to protect your iPad Pro from dents and scratches. The innovative micro-suction pads hold it securely in place.
Elegant and practical, Louis Vuitton's classic Clemence Wallet is given a delicate, feminine feel by pink leather trim and a cute Monogram flower charm.

Here’s a cool new object of fashion desire: the Lockme Backpack in a fresh Mini size. Crafted from soft calfskin, it is surprisingly roomy and goes everywhere, from daytime to after dark. With adjustable straps, it can go from shoulder to cross-body wear.

Here’s a cool new object of fashion desire: the Lockme Backpack in a fresh Mini size. Crafted from soft calfskin, it is surprisingly roomy and goes everywhere, from daytime to after dark. With adjustable straps, it can go from shoulder to cross-body wear.

For Fall 2017, the House continues to reveal new facets of Vernis leather with an unexpected reinterpretation of one of Louis Vuitton’s most iconic shapes: the Alma BB. The audacious color and Monogram canvas trim gives it a stunningly disruptive feel.
A playful piece that will create a playful wintry vibe to any silhouette. The design offers a new twist on the Monogram Flower motif, inspired by traditional winter jacquard pattern.

This distinctive piece reinterprets the Monogram Flower in feminine cabochons for a subtle play on colors and contrasts. Iconic Louis Vuitton signatures combined in an association of different metal finishes and shiny stones.

This eye-catching accessory features Kabuki-themed stickers, a highlight of the Cruise SS 18 collection. Wrapped around neck, head – or knotted on the handles of a bag – it brings an on-trend touch of color and fun.
The Indian Flower silk square is printed with an intricately detailed floral pattern. It is a versatile accessory which will add elegance and femininity to any look.

Yarns of different colours are weaved together to reproduce multicolour Monogram on this signature shawl. Joyful, generous and enveloping, the Monogram Rainbow shawl is perfect to pep-up any winter look.
This practical ID Card Holder in Damier Graphite canvas is the easy way to wear your business badge around your neck.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather, the Capucines Compact Wallet has many functionalities and a large capacity to fit every day essentials. The ingenious and original structure of this elegant pocket-sized wallet made of 2 fold-over flaps gives you ample space for credit cards, coins and bills.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Normandy makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

The City Steamer is the perfect mix of Louis Vuitton heritage with the codes introduced by Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquière. This City Steamer MM features a graphic tailored vibe with hypnotic crafted patchwork that incorporates different stitching and a mix of smooth and shiny cracked leathers.
Makes the most of winter with Logomania Scarf. Adorned with giant versions of the iconic Monogram pattern and the house initials, it features warm wool and soft silk

With its easy-to-wear acetate design, this classic style will suit all wardrobes. Iconic studs evoke the Maison's historic trunks, while metallic Essential V inserts pay homage to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton.

Fashioned in understated Taurillon leather, the ultra-functional Zippy XL has never looked more elegant. With the capacity of a small bag in a wallet, it is large enough to hold a smartphone, keys and a passport, in addition to credit cards and cash.

This season, the Cluny BB steps out in Epi Platine, a new metallic shade of the signature House leather. Its structured lines and subtle sheen make this eye-catching bag an edgy, modern choice to accompany both daytime looks and evening silhouettes.

Introducing the Twist MM in Epi Platine, a seductive new metallic shade of the House’s signature grained leather. The understated shine lends an edge to daytime outfits, transitioning effortlessly to evening, adding a touch of subtle sparkle to party looks.

The charming Alma PM traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This contemporary version is crafted of Monogram canvas, featuring creative director Nicolas Ghesquière's playful take on classic hotel stickers, which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colorful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

Discreetly woven with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, the Monogramissime tie is a timelessly elegant choice in an array of classic or seasonal colors. A matching pocket square is also available.

Make any trip an effortlessly stylish affair with the Passport Cover. A sumptuous grained calf leather lining and several interior compartments complete this classic travel accessory. The giraffes on a shopping spree with their Louis Vuitton fancy bags, transform this elegant Passport Cover into the epitome of adorable.

A result of the collaboration between Louis Vuitton and Japanese streetwear designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, creator of the Fragment label, this trendy beret was traditionally handmade in France. In felted merino wool with leather edging and a silk lining, it can be personalized with Louis Vuitton and Fragment patches.

Featuring the new Monogram Savane canvas with unique Chapman's Animal, this versatile piece offers two belts in one. The iconic Reverso buckle completes this collector model for fashion and relax look.

One of our most iconic and versatile models, this Zippy Wallet in soft, subtly grained Mahina leather and delicate Monogram perforations with new extra credit card slots has never been more functional and stylish. Slip it into your bag or carry it by hand as a mini clutch!

This season, the Twist has been reinterpreted in elegant smooth patent calfskin mixed with graphic & hypnotic Monogram colors lock, for a fashion-forward take on this leather. Perfect for a day-to-evening use, this Twist PM is a bold & cool addition to any silhouette.

Featuring the new Monogram Savane canvas with unique Chapman's Animal, this versatile piece offers two belts in one. The iconic Reverso buckle completes this collector model for fashion and relax look.

This reversible belt offers two very different, and stylish looks in one: Monogram canvas with contrasting leather trimmings on one side and Louis Vuitton's emblematic Epi grained leather on the other side.

The name says it all: beautiful and desirable, the Venus, inspired from the Steamer, a House icon (1901), for today's urban lifestyles. In Monogram canvas with colored cowhide leather trim, its generous capacity makes this bag ideal for day-to-office use.

One of our most iconic and versatile models, this Zippy Wallet in soft, subtly grained Mahina leather and delicate Monogram perforations with new extra credit card slots has never been more functional and stylish. Slip it into your bag or carry it by hand as a mini clutch!
