This practical Zippy Coin Purse in Monogram canvas – decorated with a print evoking the golden age of Transatlantic cruises – is ideal for everyday use. Its compact size can hold small change, credit cards and folded bills, and easily slips into a small pocket.

The Vosges bag presents a supple yet structured shape. Its refined design will enhance every elegant silhouette. The Rose Fizzy Braided detail is a playful hint to the Couture spirit of the House and the contrast of colors adds a luminous touch to the bold Kaki bag.

Matching the emblematic Capucines bag, this elegant wallet is given a refined, feminine touch by Monogram flower ornaments, which are fixed by hand to its flap, creating a crown-like effect. Its sleek design is large enough to hold all everyday essentials.

Cute and practical, the Porte-Monnaie Anaé enriches the Mahina line with a brand new little purse shape. Fashioned in Mahina leather, this slim and practical coin purse slips easily into a pocket, coat or small bag. The understated perforated pattern gives it a marvelously delicate and elegant feel.
Ideal as a gift, this silk jacquard tie transforms Louis Vuitton's V motif into a graphic diamond pattern for a vibrant, modern look.

The discovery of a splendid 50s-era kimono in the House archives led to the design of this exceptional bag. Graphic patterns embossed on calf leather play off Monogram canvas to create a kimono shape, echoed by the metal V signature. An exceptional piece!
A new classic, this luxurious Louis Vuitton scarf, with its motif mixing many of the House’s iconic signatures, is easy to match with any casual or business look.

Printed on the Maison's iconic Damier Ebene canvas, these playful pieces feature the “Big 5” animal designs from this season's Leather Goods collection. A perfect gift, they can be personalized with hot-stamped initials.
Real New Classic of the House, the Twist MM chain bag is the ideal size for a day-to-evening companion, worn either over the shoulder or cross-body on its long, sliding chain.

This hard-working briefcase in full-grain Taurillon leather is the perfect association of practicality and utmost elegance. It boasts multiple compartments, including a large zipped compartment in which you can put your laptop or important business documents and two open lateral pockets, providing easy access to personal belongings such as newspapers.

These striking sunglasses feature luxurious Taiga leather details, including a removable part on the top bar. The large aviator shape is ideal for square and oval faces. Available with plain colour or monogram lenses.

Flaunt your fashion sense with this daring take on the Twist Compact Wallet. Crafted in shiny metallic Epi leather, it is accessorized with the line's signature turn-lock, featuring the iconic L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.
The perfect choice for a bold day-to-evening look, Louis Vuitton's New Classic Twist bag is given a rock touch with sequin-embroidered flames motifs on  pearly Epi leather.

Today’s traveller longs for an immaculately made, functional toilet bag for his short journeys, ideally if it matches his luggage. The Toilet Pouch GM is such a bag, in sturdy Monogram Eclipse canvas leather.
Graphic and modern, the Sarah Tuileries Wallet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with a distinctive rounded flap and sides in contrasting colors of soft leather.
Sophisticated and supple Epi leather is the perfect material for the Multiple Wallet. Very compact but still functional with numerous pockets and slots, it fits easily into any pocket.

Part of the America's Cup collection, this new animation of the Cosmic bracelet is evoking a marine inspiration. The enameled V Gaston  logo makes a strong graphic statement on this navy calf wrist band. The bright blue contrasting edge-dyeing adds a casual sporty twist.

Glamorous and glossy, this Victorine Wallet in Monogram embossed patent leather is the ultimate compact companion. Feminine yet practical, every detail has been carefully considered to create a small wallet able to contain as much as a long one.

Designed for travelers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era's rapid transit), with a strap for casual cross-body wear, todays Speedy 30 is a perfect city bag supple, lightweight and forever in style. This version in Monogram coated canvas features Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquieres playful take on classic hotel stickers, which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels.
This eye-catching silk tie features a playful design of trunks and vintage cars inspired by the Louis Vuitton archives.

Multi-compartment and sophisticated in Monogram canvas with calf leather flap, this compact version of the stylish Pallas wallet combines an array of convenient features into a lightweight and space-saving design, making it the perfect choice for every day use.

Color brings a fresh twist to the LV Initiales reversible belt in Damier canvas and black calf leather. The handsomely crafted buckle features a lacquered LV Initiales frame inlayed with a palladium piece; the same hue is echoed in the strap’s dyed edge.

A classic compact fur scarf in softest beaver, embellished with inlays of signature Monogram Flower and LV Circle motifs. Warm, fashionable and easy to wear, it’s the ideal piece to dress up a winter wardrobe.

The smart twist between Damier Graphite canvas and blue neon leather lining adds a touch of sophistication to this classic Louis Vuitton wallet. The Brazza’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials.

The new Manhattan bag brings a fresh, on-trend spirit to iconic Monogram. Rich leather trim and golden hardware enhance its sporty-chic allure. Named for the city that never sleeps, this roomy tote is an ideal partner for on-the-go urban lifestyles.
Crafted in soft and supple Damier Infini leather, the Avenue Soft Briefcase is very practical thanks to its multiple carry option. Its internal oganization also allows 15'' laptop transportation

Timeless design and chic, sporty style are the hallmarks of the new Hyde Park bag in Damier Ebene canvas with Cuir Taurillon trim. This contemporary carryall is roomy, functional and versatile, with twin leather handles and a removable shoulder strap. For those who love the Bond Street, the Hyde Park is another beautiful Damier Ebene style with top handle and shoulder strap.

Inspired by the iconic rabbit, often played by Jeff Koons in his work, this bag charm will spice up any Louis Vuitton bag thanks to its original shape and bright colours. Louis Vuitton’s refinement is expressed through the work of the metallic structure and the choice of the leather.

A modern twist is given to these vintage-inspired sunglasses by distinctive details: a Monogram-engraved metal bridge and feminine 2 layer acetate colours, laminated togehter for an inside-out look. The square shape particularly suits round and oval faces.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The iconic Neverfull is twisted within this collaboration with refinement and femininity through exclusive know-how: gold Monogram serti, flower shapes, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration. Ultimate luxury, the internal zipped clutch is animated and can be worn by itself as a clutch.

A new belt for devotees of the House, crafted of heritage Monogram canvas. The LV Iconic buckle in shiny gold-finished brass features a fresh twist this season: the rounded angles lend the piece an even more feminine on-trend look.
A collectible key holder and bag charm with a functional pocket knife. Meticulously crafted, the pocket knife, which also has scissor and nail file functions, is sheathed in Monogram canvas.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colorful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

Compact and slim, this Slender Wallet in Damier Graphite canvas carries all your essentials and still fits into a front or back pocket with ease. The printed stripe that highlights the canvas?s geometric pattern makes this classic new again.

Designed in collaboration with iconic NYC skate brand Supreme, this version of the Pocket Organizer is steeped in cutting edge street style. As practical as it is fashionable, it fits comfortably into your pocket or handbag and holds credit cards, bills and papers.

Artistic and colorful, our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Ideal for those seeking a strictly functional companion.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. For the collaboration, the House developed a stylish solution to organize daily essentials. The flat pouch perfectly wears gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. A new chain has been created to enable to wear the pouch outside as inside a bag. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.
Inspired by the Lockme II bag and its trendy yet casual shape, Lockme II wallet in soft calf leather offers a modern style combined with optimal functionalities.

The clean masculine lines of the Pocket Organiser are beautifully enhanced in Damier Graphite canvas. Such stylishness is not at the expense of practicality though as it fits easily into most pockets. The smart mix between Damier Graphite canvas and colored leather lining adds an extra veneer of sophistication.
Louis Vuitton's Essential V buckle adds a bold, graphic touch to this slim belt in black calf leather. Elegantly defining the waist, it is ideal for day-to-evening wear.

The Patchwork Waves pattern, a big story from Cruise 18, plays together with classic Damier Azur checks on this trendy new edition of the Palm Springs backpack. With its leather top handle and padded straps, it can be carried by hand or on the shoulder.

Available in two rich tortoise-shell acetate colors, this fashionable design is in tune with this season’s safari theme. Featuring a laser wood effect on the front, the square frame is a perfect match for oval and round faces.

Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 collection. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros.  The season’s exclusive wildlife motif and bicolor stripes elevate this edition of the Atlas Tote with a unique artistic signature. Light and supple in Damier Ebene canvas with leather trim, its well-organized interior keep belongings secured.
This edgy update of the traditional French beret was one of the standout accessories of the Louis Vuitton's Fall/Winter 2017 men's fashion show. It is finished with a band in iconic Monogram canvas.

The understated elegance of this Pocket Organizer is indisputable. The mix of canvas and leather and the printed stripe that cuts across the Damier Graphite canvas bring a fun and strong twist to one of our most classical pieces. As practical as it is sophisticated, it fits comfortably into your pocket or handbag and holds credit cards, bills and papers.

In Damier Graphite canvas with a colored leather lining, this Multiple Wallet is the epitome of urban chic. The smart twist between Damier Graphite canvas and blue neon  lining adds a touch of sophistication to this wallet. The Multiple lives up to its name, with numerous slots for cards, receipts and banknotes. Comfortably fits in most pockets.

Available in three colors that match the FW17 color range, this modern reinterpretation of the Monogram shawl will light up any winter outfit. Its eye-catching blurry design is inspired by set of lights.

Golden Light, a key theme for evening from the Cruise 18 runway, is transposed to this new Twist bag. The smooth black calfskin base is printed and embossed to achieve a unique, luminous glow; the LV lock in black metal adds a sophisticated signature.

For the 2017 America’s Cup Collection, the House introduces Damier Latitude, an oversized version of the damier, embelished by a modern reinterpretation of the vertical V Gaston. Generously sized and detailed with sporty nautical touches, this pack is set to travel the world and its seven seas.
This stylish shawl in a soft, lightweight blend of silk and wool is printed with a playful design of Louis Vuitton locks on a woven Monogram background.

The new Manhattan bag brings a fresh, on-trend spirit to iconic Monogram. Rich leather trim and golden hardware enhance its sporty-chic allure. Named for the city that never sleeps, this roomy tote is an ideal partner for on-the-go urban lifestyles.

The new Saint Placide chain bag combine Monogram canvas with supple, colored leather, accented by a gleaming golden clasp borrowed from historic House trunks. The perfect size for day-to-night wear, it easily fits a long wallet and other essentials.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

A great day-to-evening bag, the Wight mixes emblematic Damier Ebène canvas with a generous stripe of colorful Cuir Taurillon leather for easy elegance. The thin golden chain and signed eyelets and delicate lock further embolden this study in casual chic. For those who love the Saint Placide, the Wight is a classic Damier Ebene evening bag for your collection.

This exclusive Petite Malle makes a bold fashion statement. The colorful, oversized Kabuki stickers – a big story from the Cruise 18 show – are expertly printed on a background of signature Monogram canvas. A collectible model for day-to-evening wear.
Combining playful dots with a paisley pattern, this bold design is perfect to brighten up a formal look. A perfect gift, it is a universal piece with a traditional inspiration.

2015 brings a fresh new reading of the Lockme. Crafted in a natural soft calf leather with a supple hand, the bag’s on-trend silhouette lends a youthful cachet to any look – especially when carried cross-body or slung casually over the shoulder. The over-scale LV Twist closure in shiny Palladium brass adds an edgy touch.

The understated elegance of this Pocket Organizer is indisputable. The mix of canvas and leather and the printed stripe that cuts across the Damier Graphite canvas bring a fun and strong twist to one of our most classical pieces. As practical as it is sophisticated, it fits comfortably into your pocket or handbag and holds credit cards, bills and papers.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.

Decorated with a print evoking the glamour of Louis Vuitton during the golden age of Transatlantic travel, this Zippy Wallet in coated canvas combines versatility, generous space and an all-round zip. It's perfect for carrying and organizing your daily essentials.

The House collaboration with Hiroshi Fujiwara of Fragment Design produced this exclusive Apollo Backpack. Cool and sporty in body-friendly Monogram Eclipse canvas, it features the line’s signature black band, reflective trim and new Rainbow hardware.

This exclusive Petite Malle makes a bold fashion statement. The colorful, oversized Kabuki stickers – a big story from the Cruise 18 show – are expertly printed on a background of Reverse Monogram canvas. A collectible model for day-to-evening wear.

Meet the Clemence Wallet, compact yet with high capacity. This zipped wallet with its lovable penguins strutting on the catwalk, fancy Louis Vuitton bags in their hands, is a joyful vision of elegance.
This Alma BB has a metallic finish that makes it perfect for evening wear. Femininity and elegance combine beautifully in one of the House's most iconic shapes.

This wallet in smooth Taiga leather is surprisingly compact and slim. It can carry all your essentials and still fit into a front or back pocket with ease. This model features a transparent window for your ID.

This colorful stole in soft wool plays with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern to create an intriguing blurred effect. It is a fashionable accessory whose generous size gives it a cozy, enveloping feel.

This season, the Twist has been reinterpreted in elegant smooth patent calfskin mixed with graphic & hypnotic Monogram colors lock, for a fashion-forward take on this leather. Perfect for a day-to-evening use, this Twist PM is a bold & cool addition to any silhouette.

The new District range highlights House craftsmanship, with such signature details as saddle-stitched Monogram canvas, a distinctive snap hook, and fine engraving. Stylish and collectible pieces to layer, mix or match.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.
This sophisticated shawl, woven with a tone-on-tone Monogram pattern, is given a subtle shimmer by the use of a soft shine yarn.

This signature belt does double duty: classic Monogram canvas, perfect for casual looks, reverses to grained-calf leather in Rose Bruyère (Wild Rose) for more sophisticated silhouettes. The piece is finished with a shiny golden LV Initiales buckle.

Refined and understated, this timeless model will satisfy clients looking for a classic business belt. Combining our new buckle with a 35mm calf leather strap, it offers a choice of elegant colors to match any business suit.

This iconic Zippy Wallet in Monogram canvas overlaid with a print evoking the golden age of Transatlantic cruises brings vintage LV glamour to an ultra-functional piece. The wallet’s compact design and generous interior make it a true essential.
The Multiple wallet in Taiga leather is ideal for holding credit cards, bills and receipts.

As feminine as it is functional, the Victorine is our first compact wallet. Crafted in glamorous Epi Tropical leather for a refreshing exotic feel, its ingeniously designed interior holds almost as much as a long wallet.

The Junot bag, with its trendy pompom and its young and fresh shape, perfectly suits the code of the Monogram Empreinte line. The bright Crème braided detail underlines Louis Vuitton's Couture spirit and brings a trendy twist to the timeless Noir bag.

Featuring contrasting stitching, a microfiber lining to protect contents and our iconic Monogram Flower as a graphic leather intarsia, these versatile boxes are a must-have for both home and office.  Available 3 sizes that can be stored in the Matriochka way.

The Dandy Wallet’s ultra-functional design gives you the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It can be carried under the arm, inside a bag, or by hand for a more sophisticated look thanks to its removable wrist strap.
With its radiant gold motif printed on intense black calf leather, this Twist Chain Wallet is a visually stunning illustration of the House’s leatherworking process.

Inspired by Kansaï Yamamoto, Nicolas Ghesquière brings Kabuki stickers to this Twist Chain Wallet in Monogram canvas. As versatile as it is stylish, it can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain.

Modern and ultra feminine, the Pont-Neuf long wallet is exceptionally well thought-out: a flat zipped front pocket that maximizes interior space and gives it a slimmer feel. Slender but optimized, it can even hold a smartphone.

The stylish and ultra-secure Zippy wallet looks sophisticated in supple Monogram Empreinte leather. Combining well-organized functionalities with a pure design, it is the perfect choice for an urban lifestyle.

The Dandy Briefcase is for the modern businessman looking for an elegant and distinctive business bag. As functional as it is stylish, it will follow you everywhere: as much at work as during your business trips thanks to its removable strap adjusted for Horizon luggage.
Louis Vuitton’s iconic hatbox is reimagined as an adorable day-to-evening bag. Small yet practical, this exclusive piece comes in classic Monogram canvas with cowhide trim.

The new season brings an adorable BB version of the Twist Lock bag charm and key ring. Bi-color metal is bejeweled with sparkling strass and embellished with a delicate Monogram flower charm: just the thing to decorate a BB bag, wallet or clutch.

The new Long Beach PM goes everywhere in style, from city to beach. Made of Monogram Vernis in exclusive metallic shades, the tote is accented with smooth leather trim and charming tassels. A removable pouch holds keys, cards and other small items.
This Zippy Wallet crafts vibrant-colored leather patches into a fresh, and very feminine, reworking of our emblematic Monogram flower.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with a colored grained calf leather for a more sophisticated silhouette.

Creative director Nicolas Ghesquière pays tribute to emblematic Japanese designer and artist Kansai Yamamoto with this envelope style Sarah wallet in Monogram canvas and leather, decorated with a traditional Kabuki mask motif.

These distinctive cuff bracelets feature the Maison's iconic Monogram canvas for a genuine must-have piece. The range reinterprets the Monogram in three complementary colors, in a refined tribute to Louis Vuitton's unique know-how.

This reversible belt offers two very different, and stylish looks in one: Monogram canvas with contrasting leather trimmings on one side and Louis Vuitton's emblematic Epi grained leather on the other side.
Rich, contemporary Taurillon leather is adorned with the elegent iconic LV. A soft yet sturdy belt that that dresses to casual attire.

With its colorful, artistic design and daily poetry inspired by the different letters that spell Louis Vuitton, this Agenda Refill will accompany you throughout the year. This complete version includes a directory, traveler's guide and world map.

For this season, emblematic Alma  comes in an exclusive & exotic Epi leather reminding of beautiful Brazilian landscapes with their intense & vibrant colors. Refreshing Green Pink version on cute & versatile Alma BB shape is the perfect match for this collector version.

Expressing Louis Vuitton tradition of « traveling with style », this shoulder tote is practical with a touch of sophistication. Ultra-secure thanks to its zipped main compartment and comfortable to carry thanks to its light weight and supple flat handles. The ideal companion for today’s modern woman.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.
This refined business tie incorporates Louis Vuitton's graphic V motif into a silk jacquard weave to create an elegantly understated look.

With its single loop in our iconic Monogram canvas , this bracelet is signed with a delicately engraved Monogram pattern on its locking system. A perfect match for any outfit, it can be worn on its own or with other bracelets for a strong fashion statement.

With its trendy, large pilot shape this lightweight, metal design is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes. The cutout V design on the bridge offers a distinctive branded signature with a contrasting matt/shiny effect. Mirror or more classic lenses available.

Inspired by an imagined trip to Tahiti, this Neverfull MM in Monogram canvas brings new energy to classic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. The quintessence of the summer spirit, the bag’s design is completed by a manuscript ‘Hawaii’ on the side.

These casual-sport style sunglasses feature a playful design mixing gold color with translucent details. The lightweight injected frame is confortable and easy-to-wear, while the aviator shape especially suits square and oval faces.

Versatile and right on trend, the Double V is made from noble fine-grained leather and iconic Monogram canvas. The round and voluptuous shape of the bag is perfectly contrasted by the bold V-shape flap, making the Double V a unique bag. It can be carried by hand or over the shoulder thanks to the removable strap.

Very worked, the Saint Cloud is an ideal everyday bag for easy-chic young ladies on the go; cross-body in Monogram canvas it features a playful tassel, trendy studs and leather patches. The central patch can be hot-stamped with the owner’s initials, for a personalized touch.  For those who love the Lorette, the Saint Cloud is another new Monogram cross-body bag to add to your collection.

Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 collection. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros.  A rhinoceros stands guard on this collectible edition of the Nil shoulder bag of signature Damier Ebene coated canvas. A stylish city companion, the Nil features multiple pockets inside and out, to keep items secured and accessible.

The iconic Monogram Shawl becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a new, soft and airy monogram jacquard material embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

model: SET DE BROCHES CITY BADGE SP
en_US_description: This set of two collectible brooches can mixed and matched to create a unique, personalized look.

The Lockme backpack, with its modern and practical shape is reinterpreted in a Mechanical Flowers version. The exclusive soft natural leather with its fine grain and sensual hand is embellished by golden and silver metallic studs giving a rock touch to the iconic Monogram Flowers. The Black and White colors offer a timeless option for a young, chic and stylish attitude.

This surprisingly refined shoulder tote with its delicate braided leather piping and handles, soft rose-colored lining, and playful leather tassel is all about summer elegance. As versatile as it is chic, it’s perfect for the city and the beach.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Slim and practical, this zipped cardholder is the apex of discreet charm. Its secure zip compartment can hold safely coins, bills or keys while the delicately stitched pockets reflect Louis Vuitton’s exceptional craftsmanship.

Crafted of new, extra-supple Utah leather, a skin with a visible flat grain, this belt features double stitching, rich edge-dyeing and the LV Initiales buckle with an aged-gold or palladium finish. In Navy or Chocolat, reversing to smooth black calf.
The lambskin leather braiding woven into the Taurillon leather of this Capucines PM brings a modern feel to an emblematic handbag, accentuated by the subtle color contrast of the leathers.
The Porte-Documents Voyage PM looks effortlessly stylish in masculine Taiga leather. With smooth leather trimmings and a spacious interior, it combines luxury and practicality.
This envelope style Sarah wallet combines an exterior in discreetly embossed Monogram Empreinte leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

This chic city bag marries exceptional style with flawless functionality. The V stitching signature on the strap and the contrast between sleek and grained leather bring refined elegance. But the large capacity?– and quick access to personal belongings thanks to the back pocket?– is what makes it a must-have daily companion.

This innovative design features a nylon frame made entirely of sun lenses, adorned with the Monogram logo on the front and the temples. Perfect for oval and square face shapes, its trendy mask shape makes a strong fashion statement.

The Party goes on, now in a sleek new cat-eye model – a shape especially flattering for oval and square faces. The iconic studs around the lenses hark back to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage underscored by the LV Circle signature on the end tips.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the KEEPALL 45 BANDOULIERE combines both House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity with fine details -  two reflective bands and a black one, lozine edging, pocket stitching and colored Rainbow hardware - for a result both sporty and fashion. Cabin size but with a generous volume, it is the perfect companion for two days trips.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Cabas light combines both  House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity thanks to the shape. Extra-light and comfortable, it allows a hand or shoulder carry for a stylish touch.
Mascot is a modern, square shape model in a mix of acetate and metal. The bold, iconic "V" is the center piece of this frame and highlights the strong design of these fashion-forward sunglasses.
The Pearlygram collection revisits the must-have feminine white pearl with iconic Louis Vuitton signatures, from the Monogram flower petals, to the LV Circle and Monogram pattern engraved.

A study in minimalist chic, the All-In PM is a totally foldable travel bag. Inspired by iconic House pieces like the Steamer Bag and the Sac Plat, its ultra-supple shape goes easily from flat to full while remaining effortlessly stylish.

This decidedly masculine version of the iPhone 7 & 8 Folio – crafted in our new iconic black and grey Monogram Eclipse canvas – is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely in place to protect it from the accidents of modern life.

Featuring the iconic Louis Vuitton padlock as an elegant charm, this statement piece is embellished with the Maison's timeless Monogram canvas. Elegant and discrete Monogram engraving on the central plate adds an extra touch of refinement.

The Graphic V theme combines fresh, feminine colors with a striking, sophisticated design that pays tribute to Louis Vuitton's Monogram Canvas and Epi leather. Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Spotted several times at the Cruise 18 show, the Kabuki Masks Pochette is richly crafted of colorful Epi leather paired with iconic Monogram canvas. It is fitted with a heavy chain handle and adjustable strap, for a host of fashionable carry options.

With its sleek, sophisticated lines, the Pont Neuf is a distinguished descendant of Louis Vuitton’s classic Steamer. Smooth and embossed Empreinte leather combines to create a modern, feminine bag that adapts with ladylike elegance to any setting.

The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour strap totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

For the second time, Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 Fashion Show. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros and Elephant.
The LV Twist bracelet is inspired by the bi-galva locking system and the epi colors of the emblematic Louis Vuitton Twist bag.

Created for the 35th America’s Cup regatta, this limited edition of the iconic travel bag sports a modern, nautical look. The dynamic “V Gaston” logo lends extra graphic punch to the piece, expertly crafted of oversized  new Damier Latitude canvas.

The new Manhattan bag brings a fresh, on-trend spirit to iconic Monogram. Rich leather trim and golden hardware enhance its sporty-chic allure. Named for the city that never sleeps, this roomy tote is an ideal partner for on-the-go urban lifestyles.

Feminine and playful, the Victorine is also a very practical wallet. Every detail, such as the zipped coin pocket on the edge, has been carefully designed to create an optimal small wallet able to contain as much as a long wallet.

Expressing Louis Vuitton tradition of « traveling with style », this shoulder tote is practical with a touch of sophistication.  Ultra-secure thanks to its zipped main compartment and comfortable to carry thanks to its light weight and supple flat handles. The ideal companion for today’s modern woman.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The fruit of a remarkable collaboration between Louis Vuitton and Marc Newson, the most influential industrial designer of his generation, this rolling luggage for the 21st century traveller is fashioned in iconic canvas with an aluminium wide trolley system. Travel with peace of mind, tracing your luggage in the main worldwide airports with the Louis Vuitton Echo connected device (sold separately).

Meet the future of luxurious rolling luggage. Imagined by Marc Newson, widely acknowledged as the most influential industrial designer of his generation, this lightweight 4-wheeled carry-on has a completely flat interior thanks to its large external cane. Every detail exudes innovation and lightness: from the discreet new TSA lock to the most comfortable wheels ever designed by Louis Vuitton. Travel in style with your Horizon 50, ideal for shorter trips. Travel with peace of mind, tracing your luggage in the main worldwide airports with the Louis Vuitton Echo connected device (sold separately).

The smart twist between Damier Graphite canvas and fjord leather lining adds a touch of sophistication to this classic Louis Vuitton wallet. The Brazza’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket.

The Graphic V theme combines fresh, feminine colors with a striking, sophisticated design that pays tribute to Louis Vuitton's Monogram Canvas and Epi leather. Elegant and practical, the Twist wallet features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Its slim design and pure lines make the Anton Briefcase’s elegant silhouette as appropriate for work as the weekend. Whether you carry it by hand or wear it over the shoulder with the removable strap, you’ll be right on-trend.
This elegant Monogram-pattern shawl is woven from yarns of three different colors to produce a subtly shimmering, two-tone effect. Soft and warm, it is ideal for day-to-evening wear.
This smart yet chic cardholder in Taiga leather slips easily into a pocket. It can hold credit cards, transport tickets and business cards in its four slots and central pocket.
This striking silk bandeau transforms Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram into a vibrant, graphic pattern, while the rooster motif with its Monogram flower eye is a playful nod to the Chinese New Year.

Meet the future of luxurious rolling luggage. Every detail exudes innovation and lightness: from the discreet new TSA lock to the most comfortable wheels ever designed by Louis Vuitton. Travel in style with your Horizon 50, ideal for shorter trips. Travel with peace of mind, tracing your luggage in the main worldwide airports with the Louis Vuitton Echo connected device (sold separately).

Fashioned in Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquiere’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, this Keepall Bandoulière 50 embodies modern stylish travel: light, supple and always ready for immediate departure. With their graceful shape, sparkling colours and delicate flower details, these sunglasses are a pretty, timelessly feminine accessory.

The epitome of casual chic, this Jersey shoulder tote in Damier Ebene canvas and supple Taurillon leather is the perfect daily companion for on-the-go women. Flawlessly functional and distinctively elegant, it is sure to become your new best friend.

An exceptional piece, it is designed to be carried as a clutch or worn cross-body with its adjustable leather strap.

A fashionable piece that will not go unnoticed, the arty Paint Splash stole is generous in size, to wear stylishly around the neck. The cotton-silk blend is soft and light, in an easy-going Navy or in a summery Light Grey.

The glamorous Pallas BB combines iconic Monogram canvas with colourful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colourful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.
The sporty Zack Backpack in coated canvas has a roomy interior and a classic Louis Vuitton look. The flap, drawstring closing, and metal buckle evoke so many the House classics.

The Malle Fleurs silk square was inspired by the Louis Vuitton tradition of sending flower-filled trunks to its best clients. Its feminine design features two open trunks amid a scattering of Monogram flowers and LV Circle logos.
The simple yet fine craftsmanship of this classic cardholder is highlighted by the vibrant pop art Monogram flower remix that adorns it.

This chic city bag marries exceptional style with flawless functionality. The V stitching signature on the strap and the contrast between sleek and grained leather bring refined elegance. But the large capacity– and quick access to personal belongings thanks to the back pocket– is what makes it a must-have daily companion.

The new St Germain belt features a slimmer version of the LV Initiales buckle. Embedded in the waxed calf leather, the signature adds a sleek  touch to the belt for a sophisticated look. Designed for the connoisseur, it enhances business suiting and off-duty outfits.

Featuring the light frame and flex hinges that make the Attraction model so comfortable to wear, these sunglasses boast a pilot frame meticulously covered with TAIGA leather, along with mirrored Monogram lenses for a moden, seasonal style.

A true collector's item, this Damier-pattern stole is printed with a motif of African animals created for Louis Vuitton by the renowned British artists Jake and Dinos Chapman. The luxurious blend of cashmere, wool and silk adds to the desirability of this striking design.

The whimsical Chapman Brothers giraffe illustration that adorns the Damier Ebène coated canvas brings a visually playful feel to this elegant wallet. The Brazza Wallet’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine is an optimal compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquière’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, it offers quick access to credit cards and personal belongings.

Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried like a clutch or over the shoulder thanks to its gorgeous silver chain. Accessorized with delicate flowery leather patches perforated with eyelets and decorated with silver studs, this exceptional version brings a fashionable touch to any outfit. As always, it is accessorized with the playful Twist turn-lock, featuring an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. For the collaboration, the House developed a stylish solution to organize daily essentials. The flat pouch perfectly wears gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. A new chain has been created to enable to wear the pouch outside as inside a bag. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected/surprising collaboration.

This blooming Alma Flower tells a romantic story of the House’s savoir-faire. Individually cut and coloured leather blossoms are set with metal rivets on glamorous Monogram Vernis patent calf, for a very exclusive edition of the iconic Alma.

Featuring our iconic Damier Ebene pattern, this colorful belt is adorned with a serigraphy of a savannah animal exclusively designed by the Chapman Brothers. Available in two color options and two animals, it is the ideal complement for a relaxed silhouette.

The 2017 LV League collection reveals a tribute to Louis Vuitton history both past and present. It associates iconic labels inspired from Gaston-Louis Vuitton collection and college style ones. The Multiple Wallet is compact yet highly functional, fitting into any pocket.

Inspired by an imagined trip to Tahiti, this Neverfull MM in Monogram canvas brings new energy to classic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. The quintessence of the summer spirit, the bag’s design is completed by a manuscript ‘Mykonos’ on the side.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Pouch combines both House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity - with the shape - for a result both sporty and fashion. Practical to carry by hand thanks to the removable chain or directly in the bag, this pouch will carry your Ipad with style.

The Petite Malle Epi beautifully mixes Louis Vuitton craftsmanship with a bold, stylish statement. Reflecting the Maison’s heritage in trunkmaking, it is adorned with the crosses signature of world traveler Albert Khan. Ageless and perfect for day to night chic.

Fashioned in Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquieres playful take on classic hotel stickers which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels, the Palm Springs Mini is the essential accessory for sporty urban nomads. This stylish backpack also can be carried cross-body thanks to multi-positional shoulder strap.

With details inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship, this handy accessory will accompany every nomadic lifestyle. Available in a range of colors, its playful design is perfect for a bag or pocket.

The Avenue Sling Bag in Damier Graphite canvas fits urban lifestyles perfectly: compact and sporty, with a cool and casual attitude. Its “smart” strap adjusts for left- or right-side carry. The body-friendly shape and double zip keep valuables close and secure.

model: PTE CLES NEO LV CLUB TAIGA ST.

2015 brings a fresh new reading of the Lockme. The over-scale LV Twist closure in shiny Palladium brass adds an edgy touch.

With its fashionable round shape and double contrasting coloured lenses, this trendy design features an engraved Monogram flower motif on the bridge for a playful look. With small studs inspired by the Maisonês trunks on the end pieces, it is perfect for square and oval faces.

An ideal tote when its laces are open, tighten them and it becomes a more compact, chic city bag.

This silk jacquard tie reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern in a modern, miniaturised version. Discreetly signed with the LV initials, it is a timelessly stylish accessory that makes an ideal gift.

Proving that functionality and style can go together, the versatile Emilie Wallet in exquisite Monogram Empreinte leather is elegance itself.Numerous pockets and an attractive shape make it irresistible.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's association with the America's Cup, this bag charm and key holder in the iconic Damier Cobalt canvas with a graphic V matches perfectly the leather goods line. The ideal gift for sailing enthusiasts, it can be personalized on the back with the owner's initials.

A stylish and easy-to-wear messenger bag, the new District PM is the ideal companion for everyday life. With its elegant details, lightweight and surprisingly spacious interior, it's the perfect combination of functionality and elegance

Animation of our LV INITIALES 40MM belt for the FW17 show in Taurillon leather with a serigraphy printing technique for an aye-catching effect and a strong logo statement.

en_US_description: A modern, ladylike bag with a sophisticated twist, the One Handle Flap combines smooth and grained Epi leather in a new folded shape. Accented with historic trunkmaker details Ð tuck lock, brackets, name tag Ð the PM is an ideal day-to-evening choice.

Small enough to fit into any Twist bag, it is accessorized with the line's signature turn-lock, with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

The LV Circle that adorns this Pochette Jour GM evokes Louis Vuitton’s first travel trunks, decorated at the time with this distinctive mark. Big enough to fit A4 documents, it can be used as a bag inside a bigger bag or hand-carried for a modern, and trendier look.
This silk pocket square combines Louis Vuitton's graphic V signature with dynamic lines and bold colors evoking the America's Cup universe.

The new V Square line offers a fresh, graphic take on a House signature. The contrast of brushed and polished palladium adds a sophisticated touch. These statement pieces are finely crafted, with precision cutting and flawless engraving

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 25 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

As feminine as it is functional, the Victorine is our first compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Damier Ebene canvas with a colorful leather lining, its ingeniously designed interior holds almost as much as a long wallet.

Available in two natural colors, this jewel-like bracelet in calf leather features a locking system inspired by the handles of the Maison's legendary trunk. Casual and chic, its metallic piece is engraved with a discrete Louis Vuitton signature.

With an elegant Nano Monogram design engraved on its cylinder-shape temples and iconic LV studs on the front, this easy-to-wear model will accompany any outfit. The feminine pilot shape is a perfect match for oval and square face shapes.
This glamorous design features a black and gold engraved Monogram design on the front and temples, with classic black lenses. A strong iconic style.

Perfect mix of Louis Vuitton’s heritage and new codes established by Nicolas Ghesquière, City Steamer features a pure design with flawless functionality.  This elegant New Classic is reinterpreted this season in cool and trendy Epi, an effortless take on this “Essentiel de Jour”.

The essential accessory for the modern traveller, this passport cover in coated canvas combines style with practicality. It boasts four credit card slots and two flying pockets for easier access to your passport.
The Kasai is the ideal accessory for today's man. Suitably compact yet practical with many sophisticated details, its Damier Graphite canvas sports a matte finish for a refined, masculine look.
Graphic and modern, the Sarah Tuileries Wallet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with a distinctive rounded flap and sides in contrasting colors of soft leather.

This Multiple Wallet in Epi leather & Monogram Canvas is a modern tribute to Louis Vuitton’s classic signatures, mixing colors and materials for a look as playful as iconic. Compact yet highly functional, it fits into any pocket.

The iris is a talisman for the Vuitton family, present in the garden and ancestral home at Asnières. For Fall, the House adorns the Capucines BB bag in Marengo Taurillon with a delicate iris charm: suspended from a leather string, it adds a fun, feminine accent.
Ideal for casual and urban wear, this belt in Monogram canvas features a new, Western-inspired version of the iconic LV Initiales buckle.

The Logomania Shine scarf is a perfect way to brighten cold days. Its blend of wool, silk and lurex yarns creates a lustrous effect, while a jacquard technique is used to reproduce Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern for a bold signature look.

Reflecting the playful universe of Louis Vuitton, this ring is adorned with a pair of dice as lucky charms. With numbers made of feminine strass and an engraved Monogram pattern adding an iconic touch, it is a perfect gift.

Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 collection. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros.  With its leather wrap handle, the versatile Pochette Volga in Damier Ebene is a bag clutch that is always ready to get up and go.

This statement frameês double lens design features a pilot shape inserted into a mask for an edgy and striking look. Inspired by the Maisonês iconic Petite Malle, this model is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

Available in a rainbow of different lens colors, these stylish sunglasses are decorated with iconic studs that evoke the Maison's trunks: lining the edges of each sunlens, they highlight the design's perfect pilot shape.
For the dynamic businesswoman, the Montaigne GM is ideal. Its smartly designed interior is structured to carry all the essentials, while Monogram Empreinte leather adds a touch of sophistication.
This smart yet chic cardholder in Taiga leather slips easily into a pocket. It can hold credit cards, transport tickets and business cards in its four slots and central pocket.

Airy V embossed finishing, reminding the V of Vuitton, brings a graphic touch to essential Louise GM. This animation offers a trendy take on timeless Black & Nude colours and glamorous Red. To create this design, smooth leather has been embossed with a thin foam backing, ensuring a light padded result. Louise GM offers a great capacity of storage to please active women & its delicate chain allows an elegant shoulder carry.

The reversible Pull It bracelet delivers double style points with its combination of Damier canvas and colored calf leather. The clasp is fashioned of palladium-finished brass, engraved with Damier checks and the “Louis Vuitton Paris” signature.
This Twist MM in raw Epi denim decorated with LV metal pin buttons has an Americana Rock and Roll vibe that makes this the ultimate casual chic bag.

Compact, versatile and totally on-trend, this Pochette Voyage MM in Damier Graphite coated canvas can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The iconic Neverfull is twisted within this collaboration with refinement and femininity through exclusive know-how: gold Monogram serti, flower shapes, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration. Ultimate luxury, the internal zipped clutch is animated and can be worn by itself as a clutch.

A must-have office accessory, this playful pencil pouch combines iconic Louis Vuitton signatures with an elegant look. Monogram canvas, VVN leather and the LV Circle motif add branded touches, while the color will brighten up your desk.

The Dandy Wallet’s ultra-functional design gives you the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It can be carried under the arm, inside a bag, or by hand for a more sophisticated look thanks to its removable wrist strap.
Featuring the iconic LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt comes in two contrasting shades of supple and grained Taurillon leather, effectively offering two looks in one.

The Vivienne NM is the perfect desirable tiny bag for every  youthful silhouette. The leather handle, the grained leather, the sensual round shape and the delicate Louis Vuitton Monogram signature add softness to the bag for a refined allure. The bold Kaki brings a modern touch to the Vivienne NM.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17, transposing the well-known Brogue pattern to the Pochette Métis in a bold and modern fashion statement. Its trendy shape is perfect to fit different styles.

Combining fine-grained calf leather with iconic Monogram canvas, this stylish, trendy compact wallet coordinates with Louis Vuitton's Double V bag. The original double flap conceals a secret pocket, which is ideal for tickets or coins.

model: SAC JEUNE FILLE MNG FASHION G.
en_US_description: The One Handle Flap Bag is the architectural piece of the show with its sleek folded shape & graphic mix of materials. Refined details are tribute to Louis Vuitton's DNA : brackets & lock inspired by historical trunks and nametag reminding of the travel spirit of the House. With its large capacity, MM size is the perfect daily companion.

The new Tuileries Handbag tells a bold fashion story with its eye-catching mix of Monogram canvas and tricolor cowhide leather. It allows multiple ways of carry, with twin Toron handles for a chic elbow carry and a strap for practical over-the-shoulder wear. For those who love the Manhattan, the Tuileries also offers a top handle & shoulder strap for the sophisticated urban lifestyle.

Completely reimagined to perfectly pair with the Retiro city bag, the envelope-style Sarah Wallet takes on striking modernity thanks to the colourful and architectural leather patches that bring a dashing contemporary feel to the classic Monogram canvas. The ingenious interior features a variety of pockets.

Easy chic silhouette maker, the Tournelle MM is a go-anywhere carryall for work and play. Thanks to the leather piping, its shape changes depending on whether you hold it with its comfortable handles or removable shoulder strap

These delicate necklaces play on Louis Vuitton's iconic codes in a tribute to the Maison's history and playful spirit. Available as single pendants or as a multi-charm necklace, they are the perfect gifts to mix-and-match and to play on accumulation.
This striking silk square transforms Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram into a vibrant, graphic pattern, while the rooster motif with its Monogram flower eye is a playful nod to the Chinese New Year.

With its refined buckle in golden-finished brass, this sleek new belt pays tribute to the House's trunk-making ("Malletier") heritage. A  LV Circle detail at the end of the strap adds the finishing touch to a timeless and elegant accessory.
Rich, contemporary Taurillon leather is adorned with the elegent iconic LV. A soft yet sturdy belt that that dresses to casual attire.

The most structured of the iconic Louis Vuitton handbags. The original was the creation of Gaston Vuitton, who named it for the Alma Bridge, a span that connects two fashionable Paris neighbourhoods. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Épi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colours.

The Twist was first presented in Cruise 2015 and quickly became a New Classic. Fashioned in pink Epi Jean leather, a unique printing and embossing technique that gives leather the visual effect of denim fabric, and paired with smooth black leather, this Twist PM brings a touch of fashionable femininity to any outfit.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 25 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Brittany makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Pleasingly classic lines and supple Taiga leather make the Anton Pochette an ideal option for every day. Compact and comfortable to carry, this new model features refined detailing: witness the discreet metal signature on the bag’s front pocket.

This iconic new design plays on the all-over multicolor revamped Monogram print from the FW17 range. Crafted from silk twill, it is a perfect gift that also well-suited to sophisticated looks and more casual attitudes.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with bright red leather for a highly colored silhouette.

This effortlessly elegant cashmere and silk stole literally envelops you in a blanket of delicate softness. The iconic leopard pattern by Stephen Sprouse has been revitalized with hints of pop colours that to liven things up.

Designed in 1932 to transport bottles of Champagne, the Noé returns for Spring 17 as the NéoNoé, an on-trend bucket bag in supple Monogram canvas with colorful calf-leather accents and an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry.
Compact form and supreme comfort come together in this easy-to-wear messenger-style bag. With its magnetic closure and zipped pocket on the back, it's as functional as it is tasteful.

A statement accessory coming from the Spring-Summer 2016 Show, the Tassel bag charm comes in both our iconic Monogram canvas or the new Blanc Gamma version, along with calf leather in this season’s pink color.

In creating the Fragrance Travel Cases, Louis Vuitton applies its savoir-faire and mastery in custom-designing the perfect case for transporting and protecting each item of one’s personal belongings. The 100ML travel case conserves and protects your perfume bottle, closing securely with a buckle. Slip it into your bag in every situation.The 100ml travel case can also be personalized in store to the initials of your choice.
A reversible scarf in wool and cashmere featuring the iconic Monogram logo in an all-over design.

For Cruise 2017, the City Steamer has been reinterpreted in an audacious & futuristic version. Each pocket is highly crafted with Louis Vuitton engraved studs on a smooth leather base. Flawless functionalitity & subtle sophistication make this City Steamer the perfect urban companion.

Louise EW is the ultimate elegant piece for evening outfit. This season, this pure clutch is animated in precious silver calfskin, making it the perfect gleaming accessory, enhanced by tone on tone Epi like resin lock for the jewel touch.
With its sober design, this elegant Folio in Monogram is the stylish way to protect your iPad Pro from dents and scratches. The innovative micro-suction pads hold it securely in place.
Elegant and practical, Louis Vuitton's classic Clemence Wallet is given a delicate, feminine feel by pink leather trim and a cute Monogram flower charm.

Here’s a cool new object of fashion desire: the Lockme Backpack in a fresh Mini size. Crafted from soft calfskin, it is surprisingly roomy and goes everywhere, from daytime to after dark. With adjustable straps, it can go from shoulder to cross-body wear.

Here’s a cool new object of fashion desire: the Lockme Backpack in a fresh Mini size. Crafted from soft calfskin, it is surprisingly roomy and goes everywhere, from daytime to after dark. With adjustable straps, it can go from shoulder to cross-body wear.

For Fall 2017, the House continues to reveal new facets of Vernis leather with an unexpected reinterpretation of one of Louis Vuitton’s most iconic shapes: the Alma BB. The audacious color and Monogram canvas trim gives it a stunningly disruptive feel.
A playful piece that will create a playful wintry vibe to any silhouette. The design offers a new twist on the Monogram Flower motif, inspired by traditional winter jacquard pattern.

This distinctive piece reinterprets the Monogram Flower in feminine cabochons for a subtle play on colors and contrasts. Iconic Louis Vuitton signatures combined in an association of different metal finishes and shiny stones.

This eye-catching accessory features Kabuki-themed stickers, a highlight of the Cruise SS 18 collection. Wrapped around neck, head – or knotted on the handles of a bag – it brings an on-trend touch of color and fun.
The Indian Flower silk square is printed with an intricately detailed floral pattern. It is a versatile accessory which will add elegance and femininity to any look.

Yarns of different colours are weaved together to reproduce multicolour Monogram on this signature shawl. Joyful, generous and enveloping, the Monogram Rainbow shawl is perfect to pep-up any winter look.
This practical ID Card Holder in Damier Graphite canvas is the easy way to wear your business badge around your neck.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather, the Capucines Compact Wallet has many functionalities and a large capacity to fit every day essentials. The ingenious and original structure of this elegant pocket-sized wallet made of 2 fold-over flaps gives you ample space for credit cards, coins and bills.

The new status bag from Louis Vuitton. Sophisticated and feminine, the Normandy makes an elegant statement with its contrast pairing of Damier canvas with Cuir Taurillon leather. House craftsmanship shines in the handle mounts, gussets and keybell.

The City Steamer is the perfect mix of Louis Vuitton heritage with the codes introduced by Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquière. This City Steamer MM features a graphic tailored vibe with hypnotic crafted patchwork that incorporates different stitching and a mix of smooth and shiny cracked leathers.
Makes the most of winter with Logomania Scarf. Adorned with giant versions of the iconic Monogram pattern and the house initials, it features warm wool and soft silk

With its easy-to-wear acetate design, this classic style will suit all wardrobes. Iconic studs evoke the Maison's historic trunks, while metallic Essential V inserts pay homage to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton.

Fashioned in understated Taurillon leather, the ultra-functional Zippy XL has never looked more elegant. With the capacity of a small bag in a wallet, it is large enough to hold a smartphone, keys and a passport, in addition to credit cards and cash.

This season, the Cluny BB steps out in Epi Platine, a new metallic shade of the signature House leather. Its structured lines and subtle sheen make this eye-catching bag an edgy, modern choice to accompany both daytime looks and evening silhouettes.

Introducing the Twist MM in Epi Platine, a seductive new metallic shade of the House’s signature grained leather. The understated shine lends an edge to daytime outfits, transitioning effortlessly to evening, adding a touch of subtle sparkle to party looks.

The charming Alma PM traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This contemporary version is crafted of Monogram canvas, featuring creative director Nicolas Ghesquière's playful take on classic hotel stickers, which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colorful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

Discreetly woven with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, the Monogramissime tie is a timelessly elegant choice in an array of classic or seasonal colors. A matching pocket square is also available.

Make any trip an effortlessly stylish affair with the Passport Cover. A sumptuous grained calf leather lining and several interior compartments complete this classic travel accessory. The giraffes on a shopping spree with their Louis Vuitton fancy bags, transform this elegant Passport Cover into the epitome of adorable.

A result of the collaboration between Louis Vuitton and Japanese streetwear designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, creator of the Fragment label, this trendy beret was traditionally handmade in France. In felted merino wool with leather edging and a silk lining, it can be personalized with Louis Vuitton and Fragment patches.

Featuring the new Monogram Savane canvas with unique Chapman's Animal, this versatile piece offers two belts in one. The iconic Reverso buckle completes this collector model for fashion and relax look.

One of our most iconic and versatile models, this Zippy Wallet in soft, subtly grained Mahina leather and delicate Monogram perforations with new extra credit card slots has never been more functional and stylish. Slip it into your bag or carry it by hand as a mini clutch!

This season, the Twist has been reinterpreted in elegant smooth patent calfskin mixed with graphic & hypnotic Monogram colors lock, for a fashion-forward take on this leather. Perfect for a day-to-evening use, this Twist PM is a bold & cool addition to any silhouette.

Featuring the new Monogram Savane canvas with unique Chapman's Animal, this versatile piece offers two belts in one. The iconic Reverso buckle completes this collector model for fashion and relax look.

This reversible belt offers two very different, and stylish looks in one: Monogram canvas with contrasting leather trimmings on one side and Louis Vuitton's emblematic Epi grained leather on the other side.

The name says it all: beautiful and desirable, the Venus, inspired from the Steamer, a House icon (1901), for today's urban lifestyles. In Monogram canvas with colored cowhide leather trim, its generous capacity makes this bag ideal for day-to-office use.

One of our most iconic and versatile models, this Zippy Wallet in soft, subtly grained Mahina leather and delicate Monogram perforations with new extra credit card slots has never been more functional and stylish. Slip it into your bag or carry it by hand as a mini clutch!

The iconic Monogram Shawl becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a new, soft and airy monogram jacquard material embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

The new Vaneau combines richly iconic Epi leather with Cuir Ecume cowhide leather.  Sleek and modern yet refined, it is an ideal match for busy lifestyles: perfectly sized, incredibly light, with a well-organized interior, top handles and a shoulder strap for multiple carry options.

With its pure lines and sophisticated details, the Louis Vuitton Very Chain Bag in supple Cuir Plume and Cuir Ecume leathers is your new must-have bag. The delicate chain and crafted V signature provide glamour while the flap and lock closure keep your essentials safe inside. Perfect for luxury car lovers, this case in coated canvas has a press-stud to easily remove the key when you have the valet park your car.

This season, the pure design of City Steamer has been mixed with punchy colorblocks, matching the sporty & joyful spirit of the show. Graphic tricolor combinations on trendy & versatile PM size will add a bold touch of color to any outfit.

This compact Pocket Organizer is for men looking for sophistication. The Monogram Savane canvas printed with a Chapman Brothers rhinoceros illustration brings a touch of whimsy to a classic all-in-one card holder that holds credit cards, bills and papers.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. Brazza Wallet generous size makes it ideal to carry all your cards and receipts while slipping easily in your jacket's pocket.

The successful Charlotte model is modernized with a bold mix of materials, including mirror lenses. They’re also supremely practical thanks to an innovative hinge system that means they can be easily folded flat and carried in a bag or clutch.
The Porte-Documents Voyage PM looks effortlessly stylish in masculine Taiga leather. With smooth leather trimmings and a spacious interior, it combines luxury and practicality.

Featuring a graphic bi-color design inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton motifs Damier and Monogram, mixed with timeless dots pattern, this long and generous winter scarf is a perfect cocoon against the cold.

The new Hudson sunglasses feature a fashionable round shape in a mix of laminated acetate and metal. The rim is delicatly engraved with the Damier design, with the Louis Vuitton signature on the temples.

Designed in 1932 to transport bottles of Champagne, the Noé returns for Spring 17 as the NéoNoé, an on-trend bucket bag in supple Monogram canvas with colorful calf-leather accents and an adjustable strap that lengthens for a modern, cross-body carry.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine wallet is an exceptionnel compact wallet. Trendy in iconic Monogram canvas with a colourful leather lining, it offers quick and secure access to credit cards and personal belongings.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.

Perfect for every day, the Lockmeto in soft calfskin combines a spacious, functional design with sophisticated, feminine details, including swinging tassels and the LV twist-lock, a signature of the Lockme line.

This stylish backpack belongs to the new Canyon suite of bags, crafted of supple Utah calfskin and accented with aged-silver metal fittings. The relaxed shape, generous size and clever design make this city pack an ideal carry-all companion.

This elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials. The leather braid woven into a simple chevron pattern brings modern style to this classic wallet in Taurillon leather.

The Multiple Wallet holds your credit cards, bills and receipts in a very compact format. This version in Damier Ebène coated canvas adorned with an exclusive Chapman Brothers zebra illustration brings a touch of whimsy to a classic wallet.

Inspired by iconic steamer luggage from Louis Vuitton archives, the City Steamer is renowned for its functional and nomad spirit. Reinterpreted in easy-to-carry and elegant gray Epi Jean leather and paired with timeless silver metallic pieces, this City Steamer MM is pure elegance.
This iconic wallet just got an upgrade! Now with four additional credit card slots and a playful new coloured lining, the Zippy Wallet in Monogram Empreinte leather is more versatile than ever.

Slightly oversized for a trendy twist, this fashion forward model highlights our transversal Essential V signature. With its lightweight mix of materials, and thin metal temples, the cat-eye shape has a modern retro touch.
The Rock N’ Roses stole comes in a rich rainbow of colors. Adorned with Stephen Sprouse-designed flowers reworked in a camouflage effect. This fashion stole promises an effortless, casual-chic look.

Featuring the iconic LV Initiales buckle, this reversible belt comes in two contrasting shades of supple and grained Taurillon leather, effectively offering two looks in one.

This silk and wool shawl combines the graphic patterns from Louis Vuitton's Spring/Summer 2017 fashion show to create an optical illusion of a Monogram flower. It is both a collector's item and a versatile accessory for every day.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art.  One of our most iconic and versatile models, the Zippy wallet is adorned with this exclusive collaboration: gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

Compact and ingeniously designed, the Ariane Wallet has multiple credit card slots and pockets hidden seemingly everywhere. The touch of color from the filetto detailing around the flap brings feminine sophistication to the Monogram canvas.

Monogram flower pins bloom on this new city backpack, an unexpected and oh-so-stylish piece made of supple Monogram Empreinte cowhide. The dark-blue leather’s metallic sheen sets off the aged-silver finish of the pins, for a modern, edgy look.
This envelope-style Sarah Wallet combines an elegant exterior in Epi leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

This fashionable Lockme Bucket evokes the elegant yet solid bag custom-made by Louis Vuitton in 1932 for a wealthy vineyard owner to transport bottles of champagne. Its sleek design and signature LV Twist lock make it eternally modern.

Our 2018 Agenda Refill celebrates our House Métiers dedicating every month to a travel destination through watercolour clothing sketches. Its extra features will accompany our most demanding and sophisticated customers.

The unique design of Monogram canvas matched with supple grained leather makes this a versatile day-to-night bag with style. It boasts a golden chain for short-shoulder, long-shoulder and cross-body carry!

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The charming Alma BB traces its pedigree to the original Art Deco icon, introduced in 1934. This miniature version easily holds keys, wallet, smartphone and lipstick. With a strap that adjusts the bag to waist or hip height, the Alma BB can be worn across the body for hands-free ease. This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Epi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colors.

With its pure lines and sophisticated details, the Louis Vuitton Very Chain Bag in supple Cuir Plume and Cuir Ecume leathers is your new must-have bag.
