This modern mask shape features an Essential V insert in the middle of the lens, a tribute to Nicolas Ghesquière's first show for Louis Vuitton. The cylinder-shape temples, engraved with the Monogram design, complete the iconic style. Statement sunglasses for a wow effect, their mask shape is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes.

The Canyon briefcase in Utah calfskin features a mix of smooth and grained finishes, accented with double-stitching and aged-silver hardware. A light, compact business bag, it’s designed for convenience, with comfortable Toron handles and a removable strap.

Shimmery lurex yarn is woven into a cozy blend of wool and cashmere to form the iconic Malletage pattern, set off by a delicate LV Circle emblem in gold-finished metal. Its generous size and delicate mix of materials create a feeling of enveloping softness and warmth.

The successful Charlotte Fold model is now enriched with a bold mix of materials, including an eye-catching 3D LV Circle logo. Strasses on the metal temples add a touch of sophistication to this model, perfect for oval and triangular faces.

Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried like a clutch or over the shoulder thanks to its gorgeous silver chain. Accessorized with delicate flowery leather patches perforated with eyelets and decorated with silver studs, this exceptional version brings a fashionable touch to any outfit. As always, it is accessorized with the playful Twist turn-lock, featuring an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

This silk square reinterprets the famous universal bandana pattern to incorporate Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers. Overprinted with the LV initials in an arty, paintbrush style, it is a versatile accessory to accompany timeless and fashion-forward looks.
This Sarah Multicartes in brightly colored Epi leather is inspired by the House’s iconic envelop-style Sarah wallet. Its accordion interior has plenty of space for cards, coins and bank notes.

Inspired by the Leather Bracelet Over the strap from the show FW16, this double-strap bracelet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with shiny gold and silver metal hardware in a trendy, rock 'n' roll spirit.

Echoing the stylish, casual design of the Lockme II handbag, this wallet in soft calf leather is embellished with a feminine braided detail that subtly references Louis Vuitton's tradition of craftsmanship. Secured with a distinctive LV initials clasp, its spacious interior boasts a variety of pockets and compartments.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The trendy and bold shape of the Palmsprings backpack are the perfect base for the gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings distinctive of this collaboration. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this surprising collaboration.
This graphic ring bag charm reinterprets the Maison's iconic LV Circle signature in a summery pink. Simple and Easy to fit in your pocket it is the perfect accessory for your keys or your bag.
In line with the Fall/Winter 2017 bags collection, this key holder and bag charm features leather with brogue-style perforations on a background of iconic Monogram canvas.

Providing stylish protection, this Eye-Trunk for iPhone 7 in Monogram Rouge canvas is a stunning tribute to our legacy as trunk makers. Designed in collaboration with iconic NYC skate brand Supreme, it’s sure to become the new must-have iPhone accessory.

Louis Vuitton's best-selling The Party aviator sunglasses are updated for the new season with fresh lens colors. Small metal studs echo the House’s iconic trunks, along with signatures at the temples and LV Circle logos on the lenses and at the tips. Metal temples with rubber tips and integrated flex hinges create a comfortable fit.
This Enveloppe Carte de Visite in Taiga leather features two credit card slots and one compartment for business cards.

From the Louis Vuitton x Fragment Design collection comes this cool, sporty messenger in Monogram Eclipse, bisected by a black band with reflective trim. The fine detailing – lozine edging, pocket stitching, colored Rainbow hardware – befits a man of style.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the District messenger, created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the oversized  new Damier Latitude pattern, for a modern, masculine look.

This contemporary version of the iconic silhouette, crafted of Epi leather, comes in an array of bright, bracing colors.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. The ultra-functional Zippy XL offers the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It is large enough to hold a smartphone (in a specific pocket), keys and passport, in addition to credit cards and cash. Elegant in Louis Vuitton's emblematic Taiga leather, it can be hand carried  for a sophisticated look.
Glossy, cute and girly, the smallest Chain Louise blends iconic elegance with ultra-feminine charm. Additional functionality and versatility thanks to a delicate removable chain.

Inspired by the Leather Bracelet Over the strap from the show FW16, this double-strap bracelet combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram canvas with shiny gold and silver metal hardware in a trendy, rock 'n' roll spirit.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17 with this architectural Cour Marly Bag in supple calfskin. Adorned with a golden lock and chain as well as small studs along the bottom, it is evocative of the historical trunks.
Compact yet ample, in smart and elegant Epi leather, the new version of  the Clémence Wallet is offered in playful and high-fashion shades.

“Louis Vuitton Paris” spells out a unique, signature pattern on this stylish new tie, offered in three subtle shades. The silk jacquard weave creates an interesting textural effect that looks smart with a tailored suit, for business or formal occasions.

Louis Vuitton’s exceptional craftsmanship goes Pop in this Twist MM. Its vibrant colors and crafted leather patches create a post-modern – but very feminine – interpretation of the emblematic Monogram flower.

Crafted from our iconic Taiga leather, this casual and easy-to-wear belt features contrasted edge dying for a colorful twist. The perfect fashion forward accompaniment for our new leather goods designs.

The mettalic studs represent the hearts of the flowers and give a rock touch to the bag. They also remind the nails which were used to stretch the Monogram canvas on the historical Louis Vuitton's trunks. this delicate animation crosses different universes and codes of the House in a feminine way.

This elegant Capucines PM uses different types of threads, with different colors, thickness and compositions. They are weaved in together to create a unique volume and pattern, using an ancient craftsmanship.

Combining playful dots with a paisley pattern, this bold design is perfect to brighten up a formal look. A perfect gift, it is a universal piece with a traditional inspiration.

2015 brings a fresh new reading of the Lockme. Crafted in a natural soft calf leather with a supple hand, the bag’s on-trend silhouette lends a youthful cachet to any look – especially when carried cross-body or slung casually over the shoulder. The over-scale LV Twist closure in shiny Palladium brass adds an edgy touch.

The understated elegance of this Pocket Organizer is indisputable. The mix of canvas and leather and the printed stripe that cuts across the Damier Graphite canvas bring a fun and strong twist to one of our most classical pieces. As practical as it is sophisticated, it fits comfortably into your pocket or handbag and holds credit cards, bills and papers.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.

Decorated with a print evoking the glamour of Louis Vuitton during the golden age of Transatlantic travel, this Zippy Wallet in coated canvas combines versatility, generous space and an all-round zip. It's perfect for carrying and organizing your daily essentials.

The House collaboration with Hiroshi Fujiwara of Fragment Design produced this exclusive Apollo Backpack. Cool and sporty in body-friendly Monogram Eclipse canvas, it features the line’s signature black band, reflective trim and new Rainbow hardware.

This exclusive Petite Malle makes a bold fashion statement. The colorful, oversized Kabuki stickers – a big story from the Cruise 18 show – are expertly printed on a background of Reverse Monogram canvas. A collectible model for day-to-evening wear.

Meet the Clemence Wallet, compact yet with high capacity. This zipped wallet with its lovable penguins strutting on the catwalk, fancy Louis Vuitton bags in their hands, is a joyful vision of elegance.
This Alma BB has a metallic finish that makes it perfect for evening wear. Femininity and elegance combine beautifully in one of the House's most iconic shapes.

This wallet in smooth Taiga leather is surprisingly compact and slim. It can carry all your essentials and still fit into a front or back pocket with ease. This model features a transparent window for your ID.

This colorful stole in soft wool plays with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern to create an intriguing blurred effect. It is a fashionable accessory whose generous size gives it a cozy, enveloping feel.

This season, the Twist has been reinterpreted in elegant smooth patent calfskin mixed with graphic & hypnotic Monogram colors lock, for a fashion-forward take on this leather. Perfect for a day-to-evening use, this Twist PM is a bold & cool addition to any silhouette.

The new District range highlights House craftsmanship, with such signature details as saddle-stitched Monogram canvas, a distinctive snap hook, and fine engraving. Stylish and collectible pieces to layer, mix or match.
This reversible belt associates the iconic LV Initiales buckle in dark ruthenium with our new Monogram Eclipse canvas. Subtly branded, it is a perfect match for the Maison's leather goods and shoes.
This sophisticated shawl, woven with a tone-on-tone Monogram pattern, is given a subtle shimmer by the use of a soft shine yarn.

This signature belt does double duty: classic Monogram canvas, perfect for casual looks, reverses to grained-calf leather in Rose Bruyère (Wild Rose) for more sophisticated silhouettes. The piece is finished with a shiny golden LV Initiales buckle.

Refined and understated, this timeless model will satisfy clients looking for a classic business belt. Combining our new buckle with a 35mm calf leather strap, it offers a choice of elegant colors to match any business suit.

This iconic Zippy Wallet in Monogram canvas overlaid with a print evoking the golden age of Transatlantic cruises brings vintage LV glamour to an ultra-functional piece. The wallet’s compact design and generous interior make it a true essential.
The Multiple wallet in Taiga leather is ideal for holding credit cards, bills and receipts.

As feminine as it is functional, the Victorine is our first compact wallet. Crafted in glamorous Epi Tropical leather for a refreshing exotic feel, its ingeniously designed interior holds almost as much as a long wallet.

The Junot bag, with its trendy pompom and its young and fresh shape, perfectly suits the code of the Monogram Empreinte line. The bright Crème braided detail underlines Louis Vuitton's Couture spirit and brings a trendy twist to the timeless Noir bag.

Featuring contrasting stitching, a microfiber lining to protect contents and our iconic Monogram Flower as a graphic leather intarsia, these versatile boxes are a must-have for both home and office.  Available 3 sizes that can be stored in the Matriochka way.

The Dandy Wallet’s ultra-functional design gives you the capacity of a small bag in a wallet. It can be carried under the arm, inside a bag, or by hand for a more sophisticated look thanks to its removable wrist strap.
With its radiant gold motif printed on intense black calf leather, this Twist Chain Wallet is a visually stunning illustration of the House’s leatherworking process.

Inspired by Kansaï Yamamoto, Nicolas Ghesquière brings Kabuki stickers to this Twist Chain Wallet in Monogram canvas. As versatile as it is stylish, it can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain.

Modern and ultra feminine, the Pont-Neuf long wallet is exceptionally well thought-out: a flat zipped front pocket that maximizes interior space and gives it a slimmer feel. Slender but optimized, it can even hold a smartphone.

The stylish and ultra-secure Zippy wallet looks sophisticated in supple Monogram Empreinte leather. Combining well-organized functionalities with a pure design, it is the perfect choice for an urban lifestyle.

The Dandy Briefcase is for the modern businessman looking for an elegant and distinctive business bag. As functional as it is stylish, it will follow you everywhere: as much at work as during your business trips thanks to its removable strap adjusted for Horizon luggage.
Louis Vuitton’s iconic hatbox is reimagined as an adorable day-to-evening bag. Small yet practical, this exclusive piece comes in classic Monogram canvas with cowhide trim.

The new season brings an adorable BB version of the Twist Lock bag charm and key ring. Bi-color metal is bejeweled with sparkling strass and embellished with a delicate Monogram flower charm: just the thing to decorate a BB bag, wallet or clutch.

The new Long Beach PM goes everywhere in style, from city to beach. Made of Monogram Vernis in exclusive metallic shades, the tote is accented with smooth leather trim and charming tassels. A removable pouch holds keys, cards and other small items.
This Zippy Wallet crafts vibrant-colored leather patches into a fresh, and very feminine, reworking of our emblematic Monogram flower.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with a colored grained calf leather for a more sophisticated silhouette.

Creative director Nicolas Ghesquière pays tribute to emblematic Japanese designer and artist Kansai Yamamoto with this envelope style Sarah wallet in Monogram canvas and leather, decorated with a traditional Kabuki mask motif.

These distinctive cuff bracelets feature the Maison's iconic Monogram canvas for a genuine must-have piece. The range reinterprets the Monogram in three complementary colors, in a refined tribute to Louis Vuitton's unique know-how.

This reversible belt offers two very different, and stylish looks in one: Monogram canvas with contrasting leather trimmings on one side and Louis Vuitton's emblematic Epi grained leather on the other side.
Rich, contemporary Taurillon leather is adorned with the elegent iconic LV. A soft yet sturdy belt that that dresses to casual attire.

With its colorful, artistic design and daily poetry inspired by the different letters that spell Louis Vuitton, this Agenda Refill will accompany you throughout the year. This complete version includes a directory, traveler's guide and world map.

For this season, emblematic Alma  comes in an exclusive & exotic Epi leather reminding of beautiful Brazilian landscapes with their intense & vibrant colors. Refreshing Green Pink version on cute & versatile Alma BB shape is the perfect match for this collector version.

Expressing Louis Vuitton tradition of « traveling with style », this shoulder tote is practical with a touch of sophistication. Ultra-secure thanks to its zipped main compartment and comfortable to carry thanks to its light weight and supple flat handles. The ideal companion for today’s modern woman.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The Classic Monogram shawl is woven of a soft silk-and-wool blend. Inspired by House travel blankets, it features a jacquard LV pattern and “Louis Vuitton” signature. Generously sized, it envelops the wearer in lightweight warmth. The fabric is deep-dyed for luxurious color. A wardrobe essential, it can be styled in a host of ways and makes a welcome gift.
This refined business tie incorporates Louis Vuitton's graphic V motif into a silk jacquard weave to create an elegantly understated look.

With its single loop in our iconic Monogram canvas , this bracelet is signed with a delicately engraved Monogram pattern on its locking system. A perfect match for any outfit, it can be worn on its own or with other bracelets for a strong fashion statement.

With its trendy, large pilot shape this lightweight, metal design is a perfect fit for oval and square face shapes. The cutout V design on the bridge offers a distinctive branded signature with a contrasting matt/shiny effect. Mirror or more classic lenses available.

Inspired by an imagined trip to Tahiti, this Neverfull MM in Monogram canvas brings new energy to classic Louis Vuitton craftsmanship. The quintessence of the summer spirit, the bag’s design is completed by a manuscript ‘Hawaii’ on the side.

These casual-sport style sunglasses feature a playful design mixing gold color with translucent details. The lightweight injected frame is confortable and easy-to-wear, while the aviator shape especially suits square and oval faces.

Versatile and right on trend, the Double V is made from noble fine-grained leather and iconic Monogram canvas. The round and voluptuous shape of the bag is perfectly contrasted by the bold V-shape flap, making the Double V a unique bag. It can be carried by hand or over the shoulder thanks to the removable strap.

Very worked, the Saint Cloud is an ideal everyday bag for easy-chic young ladies on the go; cross-body in Monogram canvas it features a playful tassel, trendy studs and leather patches. The central patch can be hot-stamped with the owner’s initials, for a personalized touch.  For those who love the Lorette, the Saint Cloud is another new Monogram cross-body bag to add to your collection.

Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 collection. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros.  A rhinoceros stands guard on this collectible edition of the Nil shoulder bag of signature Damier Ebene coated canvas. A stylish city companion, the Nil features multiple pockets inside and out, to keep items secured and accessible.

The iconic Monogram Shawl becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a new, soft and airy monogram jacquard material embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

model: SET DE BROCHES CITY BADGE SP
en_US_description: This set of two collectible brooches can mixed and matched to create a unique, personalized look.

The Lockme backpack, with its modern and practical shape is reinterpreted in a Mechanical Flowers version. The exclusive soft natural leather with its fine grain and sensual hand is embellished by golden and silver metallic studs giving a rock touch to the iconic Monogram Flowers. The Black and White colors offer a timeless option for a young, chic and stylish attitude.

This surprisingly refined shoulder tote with its delicate braided leather piping and handles, soft rose-colored lining, and playful leather tassel is all about summer elegance. As versatile as it is chic, it’s perfect for the city and the beach.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

Slim and practical, this zipped cardholder is the apex of discreet charm. Its secure zip compartment can hold safely coins, bills or keys while the delicately stitched pockets reflect Louis Vuitton’s exceptional craftsmanship.

Crafted of new, extra-supple Utah leather, a skin with a visible flat grain, this belt features double stitching, rich edge-dyeing and the LV Initiales buckle with an aged-gold or palladium finish. In Navy or Chocolat, reversing to smooth black calf.
The lambskin leather braiding woven into the Taurillon leather of this Capucines PM brings a modern feel to an emblematic handbag, accentuated by the subtle color contrast of the leathers.
The Porte-Documents Voyage PM looks effortlessly stylish in masculine Taiga leather. With smooth leather trimmings and a spacious interior, it combines luxury and practicality.
This envelope style Sarah wallet combines an exterior in discreetly embossed Monogram Empreinte leather with an ingeniously designed interior featuring a variety of pockets and credit card slots.

This chic city bag marries exceptional style with flawless functionality. The V stitching signature on the strap and the contrast between sleek and grained leather bring refined elegance. But the large capacity?– and quick access to personal belongings thanks to the back pocket?– is what makes it a must-have daily companion.

This innovative design features a nylon frame made entirely of sun lenses, adorned with the Monogram logo on the front and the temples. Perfect for oval and square face shapes, its trendy mask shape makes a strong fashion statement.

The Party goes on, now in a sleek new cat-eye model – a shape especially flattering for oval and square faces. The iconic studs around the lenses hark back to historic Louis Vuitton trunks, a heritage underscored by the LV Circle signature on the end tips.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the KEEPALL 45 BANDOULIERE combines both House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity with fine details -  two reflective bands and a black one, lozine edging, pocket stitching and colored Rainbow hardware - for a result both sporty and fashion. Cabin size but with a generous volume, it is the perfect companion for two days trips.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Cabas light combines both  House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity thanks to the shape. Extra-light and comfortable, it allows a hand or shoulder carry for a stylish touch.
Mascot is a modern, square shape model in a mix of acetate and metal. The bold, iconic "V" is the center piece of this frame and highlights the strong design of these fashion-forward sunglasses.
The Pearlygram collection revisits the must-have feminine white pearl with iconic Louis Vuitton signatures, from the Monogram flower petals, to the LV Circle and Monogram pattern engraved.

A study in minimalist chic, the All-In PM is a totally foldable travel bag. Inspired by iconic House pieces like the Steamer Bag and the Sac Plat, its ultra-supple shape goes easily from flat to full while remaining effortlessly stylish.

This decidedly masculine version of the iPhone 7 & 8 Folio – crafted in our new iconic black and grey Monogram Eclipse canvas – is as innovative as it is elegant. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely in place to protect it from the accidents of modern life.

Featuring the iconic Louis Vuitton padlock as an elegant charm, this statement piece is embellished with the Maison's timeless Monogram canvas. Elegant and discrete Monogram engraving on the central plate adds an extra touch of refinement.

The Graphic V theme combines fresh, feminine colors with a striking, sophisticated design that pays tribute to Louis Vuitton's Monogram Canvas and Epi leather. Stylish and versatile, the Twist Chain Wallet can be carried as a clutch or over the shoulder on its long chain. It features the playful Twist turn-lock with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

Spotted several times at the Cruise 18 show, the Kabuki Masks Pochette is richly crafted of colorful Epi leather paired with iconic Monogram canvas. It is fitted with a heavy chain handle and adjustable strap, for a host of fashionable carry options.

With its sleek, sophisticated lines, the Pont Neuf is a distinguished descendant of Louis Vuitton’s classic Steamer. Smooth and embossed Empreinte leather combines to create a modern, feminine bag that adapts with ladylike elegance to any setting.

The bag’s pure, structured silhouette is timeless and the lively colour strap totally on-trend. The Cluny is practical as well, an ideal bag for business, with its top handle for hand or elbow carry and a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear. A magnetic closure keeps personal effects secure in the well-organized interior pockets.

For the second time, Louis Vuitton commissioned renowed British artists Jake & Dinos Chapman to work on an oneiric wildlife world for the men's Spring Summer 2017 Fashion Show. Their unique artistic signature is illustrated thanks to original designs of these animals : Lion, Giraffe, Zebra, Rhinoceros and Elephant.
The LV Twist bracelet is inspired by the bi-galva locking system and the epi colors of the emblematic Louis Vuitton Twist bag.

Created for the 35th America’s Cup regatta, this limited edition of the iconic travel bag sports a modern, nautical look. The dynamic “V Gaston” logo lends extra graphic punch to the piece, expertly crafted of oversized  new Damier Latitude canvas.

The new Manhattan bag brings a fresh, on-trend spirit to iconic Monogram. Rich leather trim and golden hardware enhance its sporty-chic allure. Named for the city that never sleeps, this roomy tote is an ideal partner for on-the-go urban lifestyles.

Feminine and playful, the Victorine is also a very practical wallet. Every detail, such as the zipped coin pocket on the edge, has been carefully designed to create an optimal small wallet able to contain as much as a long wallet.

Expressing Louis Vuitton tradition of « traveling with style », this shoulder tote is practical with a touch of sophistication.  Ultra-secure thanks to its zipped main compartment and comfortable to carry thanks to its light weight and supple flat handles. The ideal companion for today’s modern woman.

Availability is limited. Shop for the holidays now.

The fruit of a remarkable collaboration between Louis Vuitton and Marc Newson, the most influential industrial designer of his generation, this rolling luggage for the 21st century traveller is fashioned in iconic canvas with an aluminium wide trolley system. Travel with peace of mind, tracing your luggage in the main worldwide airports with the Louis Vuitton Echo connected device (sold separately).

Meet the future of luxurious rolling luggage. Imagined by Marc Newson, widely acknowledged as the most influential industrial designer of his generation, this lightweight 4-wheeled carry-on has a completely flat interior thanks to its large external cane. Every detail exudes innovation and lightness: from the discreet new TSA lock to the most comfortable wheels ever designed by Louis Vuitton. Travel in style with your Horizon 50, ideal for shorter trips. Travel with peace of mind, tracing your luggage in the main worldwide airports with the Louis Vuitton Echo connected device (sold separately).

The smart twist between Damier Graphite canvas and fjord leather lining adds a touch of sophistication to this classic Louis Vuitton wallet. The Brazza’s generous size makes it perfect for your daily essentials and yet fits into any pocket.

Its slim design and pure lines make the Anton Briefcase’s elegant silhouette as appropriate for work as the weekend. Whether you carry it by hand or wear it over the shoulder with the removable strap, you’ll be right on-trend.
This elegant Monogram-pattern shawl is woven from yarns of three different colors to produce a subtly shimmering, two-tone effect. Soft and warm, it is ideal for day-to-evening wear.
This smart yet chic cardholder in Taiga leather slips easily into a pocket. It can hold credit cards, transport tickets and business cards in its four slots and central pocket.

The exotic vibe of the last Cruise lives on with this new Alma Tropical handbag. Energizing hues of rose and turquoise give the iconic shape a surprising, youthful allure. It’s the perfect piece for a trendy boost of color to Spring and Summer silhouettes.
Understated but edgy, this graphic printed design has a modern and fashionable feel. Available in vibrant light blue and easy-going navy, it will match any look.

This eye-catching version of the Nano Alma in Monogram canvas decorated with an adorable bird composed of classic House details – such as rivets, Monogram Flowers and the golden V signature – is the ideal way to carry your daily essentials. Very light, it easily fits your smartphone, credit cards and keys.

Feminine yet functional, the Victorine is a optimal compact wallet. Fashioned in iconic Monogram canvas featuring an adorable bird motif composed of classic House details, it offers quick access to credit cards and personal belongings.

Imagined by Marc Newson, widely acknowledged as the most influential industrial designer of his generation, this lightweight 4-wheeled carry-on has a completely flat interior thanks to its large external cane. Every detail exudes innovation and lightness: from the discreet new TSA lock to the most comfortable wheels ever designed by Louis Vuitton. Travel in style with your Horizon 50, ideal for shorter trips. This season, the Saint-Germain BB in Monogram Empreinte steps out for evening arrayed in Gris Silver, an exciting new shade with a pearlescent sheen. Bi-color metal studs punctuate the bag’s luxurious embossed leather, for an edgy, rocker attitude.

Fashioned in Monogram canvas featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquiere’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, this Keepall Bandoulière 50 embodies modern stylish travel: light, supple and always ready for immediate departure. Those adept at the art of packing can easily fit a week's wardrobe into the generously sized (and cabin-friendly) Keepall 50.
With their graceful shape, sparkling colours and delicate flower details, these sunglasses are a pretty, timelessly feminine accessory.

The epitome of casual chic, this Jersey shoulder tote in Damier Ebene canvas and supple Taurillon leather is the perfect daily companion for on-the-go women. Flawlessly functional and distinctively elegant, it is sure to become your new best friend.

Available in a rainbow of different lens colors, these stylish sunglasses are decorated with iconic studs that evoke the Maison's trunks: lining the edges of each sunlens, they highlight the design's perfect pilot shape.

Color brings a fresh twist to the LV Initiales reversible belt in Damier canvas and black calf leather. The handsomely crafted buckle features a lacquered LV Initiales frame inlayed with a palladium piece; the same hue is echoed in the strap’s dyed edge.

The Essential V theme reinterprets the graphic V signature of Nicolas Ghesquière's first fashion show for Louis Vuitton. Paved with strass and featuring golden and palladium finishing, this pendant necklace makes the perfect feminine piece.
Exceptional Louis Vuitton craftsmanship marks the Iconic Damier Infini signature. Damier engraved metal highlights the rolling belt buckle of this reversible style.

Crafted in supple leather and bearing the discreet LV Twist Lock signature, the Lockme Backpack completes the Lockme Family with a fresh new shape. Lightweight and feminine, it is a youthful daily companion for active women: carry it on a single shoulder as a handbag or go for more functionality by wearing it as a backpack.

This smart yet chic cardholder in our new Monogram Eclipse coated canvas slips easily into a pocket. It can hold credit cards, transport tickets and business cards in its four slots and central pocket.
Elegant and businesslike, the Anton tote conceals an array of functional pockets and compartments within its sleek, timeless design. Handles and a removable shoulder strap offer two carrying options.

With its distinctive shape and refined details, the Avenue Backpack in supple Damier Infini leather brings casual sophistication to any look. It's practical and keeps your belongings secure thanks to its zipped compartments.

Ideal to brighten up any look, this soft shawl in silk and wool is a study in versatility: highlight the plain part of the pattern for a more classic feel or feature the flower motif for a fancier occasion.

Combining the Nemeth rope design on our iconic Damier canvas with black calf leather, this reversible belt can accompany fashion forward statements and more formal silhouettes. A perfect match for our new product lines.
A new design that remind traditional winter patterns. Knitted in a cozy wool-and-cashmere blend, with a modern touch of shimmery lurex, these pieces will shine on ski slopes or city streets.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. It is a city bag that takes care of business too with ample room for papers and files.

Refined and understated, this timeless model will satisfy clients looking for a classic business belt. Combining our new buckle with a 35mm calf leather strap, it offers a choice of elegant colors to match any business suit.
Ideal for casual and urban wear, this belt in Monogram canvas features a new, Western-inspired version of the iconic LV Initiales buckle.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.
The Multiple wallet in Taiga leather is ideal for holding credit cards, bills and receipts.
Bright colorblocks give this new version of the City Steamer a sporty spin. Crafted of smooth Veau Satin calfskin, the graphic PM model brings a bold touch to any look

An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

Slim and sober, the iPhone 7 & 8 Folio has two inside flat pockets for daily essentials like business or credit cards. It easily fits in a pocket or a briefcase. The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.
The Avenue Sling Bag explores and reinvents Louis Vuitton’s history, making the old new again with vintage LV travel stickers taking on college feel thanks to the imagination of Kim Jones.
Louis Vuitton's Essential V buckle adds a bold, graphic touch to this stylish and versatile belt in Monogram Reverse canvas. The strap is cut diagonally for a strong visual statement.

Personnalize your Louis Vuitton bag thanks to this shoulder leather strap. The studs in bright flower shapes match with the Capucines and the Twist wich interpret the same story on their bags. The craftsmanship of the strap brings an audacious touch of color to every look. Fun and versatile: the bandouliere is easy to put on and remove thanks to the practical snap hook.
This elegant tie is woven with a tone-on-tone Monogram pattern, creating a subtle textured effect that makes it ideal for business wear.

Crafted in supple Taurillon leather with a leather-covered LV signature, this elegant wallet is inspired by the emblematic Capucines line. Sensorial yet functional, it is still large enough to fit all your daily essentials.

The spacious Graceful hobo has a lightweight, body-friendly design that makes it perfect for every day. The flat handle sits easily on the shoulder, while emblematic details, such as the leather name tag, reference Louis Vuitton's travel heritage.

Crafted of new, extra-supple Utah leather, a skin with a visible flat grain, this belt features double stitching, rich edge-dyeing and the LV Initiales buckle with an aged-gold or palladium finish. In Navy or Chocolat, reversing to smooth black calf.

For those who like to have everything in one place, the Zippy organiser in Taïga leather is ideal. It easily holds a chequebook, plane tickets, papers and pen and still has this elegant look.

Combining the Nemeth rope design on our iconic Damier canvas with black calf leather, this reversible belt can accompany fashion forward statements and more formal silhouettes. A perfect match for our new product lines.
Your go-to necktie for sartorial panache: the signature Louis Vuitton Damier tie reworked in a more discreet tone-on-tone feel.
Matching our Leather Goods, this new belt suits both business silhouettes and more modern looks. The buckle features a sleek tone-on-tone plaque, with an LV logo adding a subtle signature.

Sporty and casual, the Avenue Sling Bag in Damier Infini leather is your ideal city companion. Extra compact, lightweight and very body-friendly, it's the perfect small bag for the moving man of today.

For the dynamic businesswoman, the Montaigne MM is ideal. Its smartly designed interior is structured to carry all the essentials, while Monogram Empreinte leather adds a touch of sophistication.
Inspired by Kansaï Yamamoto, Nicolas Ghesquière brings Kabuki stickers to this Zippy Wallet in Monogram canvas. A theatrical interpretation of one of our most iconic wallets.

This  beach towel features an eye-catching design combining dynamic lines, bold colors and race numbers to evoke the sailing universe. Its very rich and efficient thick cotton base allies softness, absorbability and qualitative look.

Every feature of this Speedy is iconic: the unique shape, the leather handles. No wonder it has achieved cult status the world over. Designed for travellers in 1930 (the name is a nod to the era’s rapid transit), with a strap for shoulder or cross-body wear, today’s Speedy 30 is a perfect city bag – supple, lightweight and forever in style. This new reading of a House icon, crafted of embossed Empreinte leather, is a timelessly elegant bag for the fashionable woman.

With its colorful, artistic design and daily poetry inspired by the letters that spell Louis Vuitton, this Agenda Refill will accompany you throughout the year. This basic version is designed for those seeking a strictly functional solution.

In Damier Graphite coated canvas, the slim and refined Enveloppe Carte de Visite slips effortlessly into any pocket or bag. Its press-stud closure ensures that your business or credit cards stay safe.

Twist Wallet in impeccable Epi leather brings together clever practical design with high sense of fashion to make it instantly distinctive. The architectural LV Twist turn-lock – with the L that transforms into a V by a twist of the fingers - and multiple pockets makes it a playful and functional wallet.

The City Steamer pays homage to House heritage while offering a host of new signature twists: note the engraved padlock, nametag, and hot-stamped LV Circle. It is a city bag that takes care of business too with ample room for papers and files.

Exotic & refreshing Twist Epi Tropical highlights Louis Vuitton’s leather expertise: 5 to 7 graved frames of color are applied successively on the smooth leather base that is then embossed with the iconic Epi grain, giving this exceptional finish.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the Slender Wallet, created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the new Damier Latitude pattern, for a modern,  masculine and yet practical piece. Compact and slim, the Slender Wallet carries all your essentials and still fits into a front or back pocket with ease.

Inspired by nautical codes, this playful and easy-to-wear bracelet features an enameled V Gaston logo as a graphic Louis Vuitton signature. With its elegant navy and white tones, it is a collectible piece that makes a perfect gift for sailing enthusiasts.

This new calf-leather bracelet reprises the LV buckle of the best-selling Neogram belt. With its stylish double-wrap strap, the Neogram is a timeless yet modern masculine accessory, available in three elegant colors.
This adorable tassel in a BB size is the perfect companion for your bags or Small Leather Goods. It can be personalized by hot-stamping your initials to make a delightful gift.
A playful "Toi&Moi" bag charm associating a padlock and a key inspired by the House historical trunks. Separate it in two parts and share it with your significant other.
This classic Monogram blanket in wool and cashmere is perfect for cocooning at home or throwing over your shoulder for an audacious and trendy look.

Compact and iconic in Monogram Empreinte leather, the Montaigne BB is notable for its chic versatility. This new model in bold Gris Silver goes further still: the bag’s pearlescent sheen and edgy metal studs make it a perfect choice for day to evening.

This romantic design offers a highly feminine reference to the Maison's heritage. Its trunk liberating Monogram Flower is a reference to the historic Louis Vuitton tradition of sending trunks full of flowers to special clients.

Echoing the City Bags design, the new Pochette Tuileries gives a casual and relaxed looks thanks to its different carrying options: as a clutch for an indisputably stylish look thanks to its original and colorful shape or slipped inside a bag for more functional use.
This original piece in silk crepe features a paisley bandana pattern reinterpreted with lucky charm motifs. Its playful, modern pattern is combined with edgy colors for a fashionable look.
Shimmery lurex yarn is woven into a cozy blend of wool and cashmere to form the iconic Malletage pattern, set off by a delicate LV Circle emblem in gold-finished metal.
This Christopher PM backpack explores and reinvents Louis Vuitton’s history, making the old new again with vintage LV travel stickers taking on college feel thanks to the imagination of Kim Jones.
Journey back to the 60’s with this pop art inspired Twist Wallet in Epi leather, styled with an unexpected mashup of emblematic Louis Vuitton signatures.
The perfect romantic gift, this heart-shaped bag charm and key holder comes in Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram Vernis leather with a beautiful dégradé effect inspired by the sky at sunset.

Crafted in supple leather and bearing the discreet LV Twist Lock signature, the Lockme Backpack completes the Lockme Family with a fresh new shape. Lightweight and feminine, it is a youthful daily companion for active women: carry it on a single shoulder as a handbag or go for more functionality by wearing it as a backpack.

Featuring the Maison's iconic Monogram flowers motives, this ruler is lined with leather for extra comfort. Inspired by chilhood memories, the three flowers can be used as stencils, offering a smart and playful signature touch.

Twist Mechanical Flowers reinterprets the Monogram Flowers through a mix of materials and high craftsmanship. Flowery leather patches are delicately applied on Epi leather base and embellished by 14 eyelets & 122 golden or silver color studs both engraved with "Louis Vuitton" signature. This creation brings a fashionable appeal to must-have Twist bag.

A new must-have in the collection: this sophisticated belt features the Maison's iconic LV Twist signature in a stylish bi-galva finishing. Available in Epi calf leather and in three different colors, it will brighten up timeless looks as well as colorful edgy silhouettes.

Available in a rainbow of different lens colors, these stylish sunglasses are decorated with iconic studs that evoke the Maison's trunks: lining the edges of each sunlens, they highlight the design's perfect pilot shape.

Made from supple Utah calf leather fitted with aged-silver hardware, the Canyon Messenger unites a relaxed, urban vibe with craftsmanship, comfort and functionality. The MM model is ideal for carrying papers and files.
Get ready to turn heads with this totally on-trend Twist Tote and its perfect combination of modern lines and luxurious details like the iconic LV Twist-lock and très chic side-body straps.
This edgy Zippy Wallet in shiny metallic Epi leather comes with a fashionnable slot handclasp. When carried, this avant-garde Zippy Wallet will adorn your hand with the essential V signature jewel.

The season’s big “LV League” sticker story brings a fun, youthful look to the Metropole belt. This new version, in calf leather-lined Damier canvas, features colorful edge-dyeing and a tonal covered buckle for a sleek, streamlined allure.

The Elizabeth pencil pouch is meticulously crafted of leather and Monogram Eclipse canvas, a dark, masculine version of the iconic pattern. Hot-stamped with the “Louis Vuitton Paris” signature, it keeps fine writing instruments organized and protected.

In line with Louis Vuitton's heritage, vintage travel stickers inspired the colorful charms and pins of the new LV League collection. Note the meticulously crafted finishes: enamel on metal and laser engraving. They add a playful, on-trend twist to any look.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17 with a modern reinterpretation of the Pochette Métis. The elegant yet feminine flower pattern and golden double key chain make this bag a true object of desire.

Adorned with feminine strass and engraved with the Maison's iconic Monogram pattern, these stud earrings feature small dice. Associating two different metal finishing, they are perfect to mix-&-match for a personnalized look.

Behold the Lockme II BB reimagined in soft, sensual Rose Gold calf leather, embellished with edgy bi-color metal eyelets. After a day in the city, off comes the shoulder strap to reveal a precious, feminine evening bag, ready for a night on the town.

Echoing the City Bags design, the new Pochette Tuileries gives a casual and relaxed looks thanks to its different carrying options: as a clutch for an indisputably stylish look thanks to its original and colorful shape or slipped inside a bag for more functional use.

A reversible, super-soft cushion in wool and cashmere featuring the iconic Monogram logo in an all-over design. The item is signed with a qualitative Epi leather patch.
This chic silk bandeau has an arty floral print inspired by Louis Vuitton's Fall/Winter 2017 fashion show. A modern, versatile accessory, that can be worn in many different ways.

Inspired by Louis Vuitton's association with the America's Cup, this leather bag charm and key holder features a brightly colored yacht. The perfect gift for sailing enthusiasts, it can be personalized on the back with the owner's initials.
Your go-to necktie for sartorial panache: the signature Louis Vuitton Damier tie reworked in a more discreet tone-on-tone feel.

This warm wool hat is knitted using an innovative technique to create a 3D effect. Its bold pattern was inspired by Louis Vuitton's Fall/Winter 2016 fashion show, which played with trunk stamp motifs taken from the House archives.

For the 2017 America’s Cup Collection, the House introduces Damier Latitude, an oversized version of the damier, embelished by a modern reinterpretation of the vertical V Gaston. Generously sized and detailed with sporty nautical touches, this pack is set to travel the world and its seven seas.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the Zippy Organizer created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the new Damier Latitude pattern, for a modern, masculine and yet practical piece. This limited-edition of Zippy Organizer, will please the traveler who prizes both style and utility.
In masculine Damier Graphite canvas with a touch of color thanks to its leather lining, this compact Pocket Organizer is the perfect all-in-one wallet. It holds credit cards, bills and papers.

This compact version of the emblematic Twist Wallet in Epi leather packs multiple practical features into an exceptionally space-efficient design. Small enough to fit into any Twist bag, it is accessorized with the line's signature turn-lock, with an L that transforms into a V with a twist of the fingers.

A modern twist is given to these vintage-inspired sunglasses by distinctive details: a Monogram-engraved metal bridge and feminine 2 layer acetate colours, laminated togehter for an inside-out look. The square shape particularly suits round and oval faces.

Containing poetry and artistic compositions to accompany you throughout the year, this colorful 2017 Agenda Refill is a perfect daily companion. Its basic diary content is designed for clients seeking a strictly functional approach.
This fun design features a gold metal front with an eye catching Nano Monogram pattern for an iconic touch. Their pilot shape is a perfect complement for oval and square face shapes.

This season the House launches Freedom, an exclusive calfskin tote with an edgy, moto vibe. It can be styled with zippers open or closed, to change the bag’s shape and reveal side flaps that match contrast handles. The perfect piece for urban lifestyles, finished with a leather-and-metal LV signature.

These striking sunglasses feature luxurious Taiga leather details, including a removable part on the top bar. The large aviator shape is ideal for square and oval faces. Available with plain colour or monogram lenses.

The new Saint Placide chain bag combine Monogram canvas with supple, colored leather, accented by a gleaming golden clasp borrowed from historic House trunks. The perfect size for day-to-night wear, it easily fits a long wallet and other essentials.

An elegant everyday bag, this smaller version of the Harington Messenger is the very epitome of city chic. The House’s savoir-faire is present in the rich detailing: imbedded leather handles, large edges with L construction, and hand-painted edge dyeing.

The perfect day-to-evening clutch, the Mira boasts a striking envelope design and a sophisticated metallic piece signed Louis Vuitton Paris. Versatile, it can be carried two ways: over the shoulder with the delicate chain or cross-body, thanks to the long leather strap.

Inspired by nautical codes, this playful and easy-to-wear bracelet features an enameled V Gaston logo as a graphic Louis Vuitton signature. With its elegant navy and white tones, it is a collectible piece that makes a perfect gift for sailing enthusiasts.
Referencing Louis Vuitton's leather goods heritage, this dragonne bag charm and key holder combines iconic Damier Graphite canvas with brightly coloured calf leather for a modern and masculine look.

The glamorous Pallas combines iconic Monogram canvas with colorful grained leather for a very feminine, modern feel. This Full version is enriched with colorful leather gussets, for even more elegance. A study in flawless functionality, it is lightweight yet roomy enough to fit all the essentials of daily life.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17 by transposing the classic brogue pattern to the City Steamer. All eyes will be on this stunning reinterpretation of a new House classic.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. The pure lines of our new modern bucket allow an expression of refinement and femininity through exclusive know how : gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

This Pochette Voyage MM in Epi leather & Monogram Canvas is a modern tribute to Louis Vuitton’s classic signatures, mixing colors and materials for a look that is as playful as it is iconic. It can be used as a bag in bag or hand-carried for a more modern, and trendier look.

model: PTE CLES MNG ALL OVER RUBBER
en_US_description: In the shape of our distinctive flower, this bag charm and key holder features the House's iconic Monogram as an all-over pattern on rubber. Graphic and playful, it makes a perfect signature gift.

Featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquieres playful take on classic hotel stickers, which Gaston-Louis Vuitton used to collect during all his travels, this sturdy and elegant Petite Malle in Monogram canvas reflects the rich history of the House. An exceptional piece, it is designed to be carried as a clutch or worn cross-body with its adjustable leather strap.

Perfect for business or casual wear, this stylish scarf in wool and cashmere is woven with trunk stamp motifs taken from the Louis Vuitton archives. This heritage pattern was one of the key statements of the Fall/Winter 2016 fashion show.

Upgrade your arm candy. The unique design of Monogram canvas matched with supple calf leather & elegant pleats makes this a versatile day-to-night bag with style. It boasts a golden chain for short-shoulder, long-shoulder and cross-body carry!

Our iconic LV Pyramide buckle is reinvented on this graphic belt, which pairs it with the Maison's Monogram Illusion signature in timeless black or a pop blue. Fully reversible, it is a casual model with a modern twist.

With its two removable interior pockets, the Pochette Felicie in Monogram Empreinte is the stylish solution to carry and organize your daily essentials. Much more than a wallet, it can be transformed into a glamorous shoulder bag or clutch thanks to its removable gold chain.

The Saint Michel bag combines two iconic materials - Monogram canvas and Epi leather - in a small, chic shape that is perfect for everyday essentials. The adjustable strap allows it to be carried on the shoulder or across the body, and its flap can be personalized with the owner's initials.

Louis Vuitton’s holiday window displays inspired these illustrations of animals romping with iconic House trunks and bags. The charms are crafted of coated canvas and leather (the backs can be hot-stamped), with engraved, gold-finished metal pieces.

The elegant, envelope-style Pallas wallet in Monogram canvas is given a fresh, feminine feel by brightly colored leather trim. Louis Vuitton's emblematic S-lock guarantees security, while inside there is ample space for all everyday essentials.

The spirit of travel imbues this collectible edition of the Keepall 45, designed expressly for the 2017 America’s Cup. Presented in Damier Coastline coasted canvas  – a new super-sized check – stamped with the bold “V Gaston” logo, a House signature since 1901.

Understated, but with a fashionable twist, the new Edge tie in pure silk jacquard picks up a theme from the season’s leather goods and textiles. Offered in classic, wearable colors, it features contrasted intarsia edging and a tonal LV signature.

Inspired by Punk spirit of Spring-Summer 2017 Men Show, this masculine bracelet is available in two Monogram canvas, the iconic brown and a 1896 blueprint's reintepretation : the new Monogram Savane Dune.

In pure, soft cashmere, the Reykjavik Scarf is a luxurious way to wrap up in cold weather. Woven using a jacquard technique to reproduce Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, its generous dimensions also make it perfect for travel.

Timeless design and chic, sporty style are the hallmarks of the new Hyde Park bag in Damier Ebene canvas with Cuir Taurillon trim. This contemporary carryall is roomy, functional and versatile, with twin leather handles and a removable shoulder strap.
A modern interpretation of a classic design, this elegant tie combines tiny dots with a discreet Monogram jacquard background, making it the perfect choice to accessorise a range of looks.
This refined Monogram jacquard tie comes in a summery blend of silk and linen, and in pale, washed colors for a casual yet sophisticated look.

Ideal for tidying everyday objects, this versatile family of trays combines some of the Maison's most iconic signatures. Stain-proof and very durable, the Monogram lining is a very handy addition. It can be personalized with the owner's initial making it the perfect gift.
The Essential V theme reinterprets the graphic V signature of Nicolas Ghesquière's first fashion show for Louis Vuitton. Paved with strass, these feminine stud earrings make a perfect gift.

Strong graphics and nautical accents mark this edition of the Pochette Voyage  created for the 2017 America’s Cup Collection. A sporty reinterpretation of the historical V Gaston cuts boldly across the new Damier Latitude pattern, for a modern and fashion piece. You can slip the Pochette Voyage MM  into your bag as a travel pouch or hand carry it for a trendier look. The spacious interior and gussets mean easy access to all your essentials.

This silk jacquard tie reinterprets Louis Vuitton's iconic Damier pattern in a modern, miniaturised version. Discreetly signed with the LV initials, it is a timelessly stylish accessory that makes an ideal gift.
The new collection of must-have bandoulières features fresh color stories and versatile sizes. The adjustable Monogram Reverse strap customizes bags with a cool, recognizable House signature.

The most versatile of wallets, this Zippy in embossed and smooth leather is the epitome of practicality with plenty of room for money, cards and coins. The braided detail in a contrasting colour incarnates the House’s couture spirit and adds a stylishly luminous touch.

Dressed up in new Epi Platine leather, the Alma BB does double duty: by day, its metallic sheen lends a modern edge to any look; by night, it adds sophisticated sparkle to a party outfit. With an adjustable strap for cross-body wear, at hip or waist height.

For Summer 2017, the Taiga line is pop up by a stripe animation inspired from the historical painting on trunks. As practical as it is sophisticated, it fits comfortably into your pocket or handbag and holds credit cards, bills and papers.

Perfect for every day, the Lockmeto in soft calfskin combines a spacious, functional design with sophisticated, feminine details, including swinging tassels and the LV twist-lock, a signature of the Lockme line.

Nicolas Ghesquière continues to explore the essence of Parisian elegance for Fall-Winter 17, adorning this City Steamer One Handle with small studs along its edges for a stylish bag that evokes the House’s history as luxury trunkmakers.
The curved envelope shape of this Key Holder and soft perforated Mahina leather brings feminine allure to a very practical piece.

Travel in style. With its feminine design in supple canvas and grained leather, the Pallas Beauty Case has a zipped interior pocket and flat pocket to hold your precious belongings. It’s supple enough to fit easily into a suitcase, even when full.

Featuring Creative Director Nicolas Ghesquière’s playful take on classic hotel stickers, this pochette is the stylish solution to carry and organize your daily essentials. It can be carried as a glamorous shoulder bag or clutch thanks to its removable golden chain.

The ideal evening companion, the Soft clutch in black sensual calf leather and exotic python combines style and convenience. Its supple, body-friendly shape is enhanced by emblematic Louis Vuitton details: an LV turn-lock closure and removable nautical-inspired chain.

Ideal for casual and urban wear, this belt in Monogram canvas features a new, Western-inspired version of the iconic LV Initiales buckle.
For the dynamic businesswoman, the Montaigne MM is ideal. Its smartly designed interior is structured to carry all the essentials, while Monogram Empreinte leather adds a touch of sophistication.

This Pocket Organizer is a modern tribute to Louis Vuitton’s classic signatures, mixing colors and materials for a look as playful as iconic. Functional and ultra stylish, it fits easily into any pocket and holds credit cards, bills and papers.

This timeless, versatile sleeve is the perfect travel companion. Allowing to smartly organize luggage interiors, it can also be slipped into a city bag. Its supple shape and wide opening make it highly functional to hold various personal belongings from small accessories to electronic devices and their chargers.

Key holder and bag charm, this versatile accessory is both playful and trendy. The knotted cordon is a perfect match for our leather goods lines colors, while the LV circle signature adds a touch of sophistication.

With its strong and graphic design, this soft stole is the perfect piece for the Ivy League theme of this season's collection. A playful piece with a vintage vibe, inspired by American college sport teams.

This eye-catching silk tie features a playful design of trunks and vintage cars inspired by the Louis Vuitton archives.

Inspired by the House’s first wallets, the Josephine wallet is a playful and modern variation of a classic design. This exceptionally elegant version is crafted in supple Monogram Empreinte leather. As always, it fits easily into most small bags and clutches.

The spirit of travel imbues this collectible edition of the Keepall 45, designed expressly for the 2017 America’s Cup. Presented in Damier Cobalt Latitude – a new super-sized check – stamped with the bold “V Gaston” logo, a House signature since 1901.

Inspired by the iconic rabbit, often played by Jeff Koons in his work, this bag charm will spice up any Louis Vuitton bag thanks to its original shape and bright colours. Louis Vuitton’s refinement is expressed through the work of the metallic structure and the choice of the leather.

This iconic new design plays on the all-over multicolor revamped Monogram print from the FW17 range. Crafted from silk twill, it is a perfect gift that also well-suited to sophisticated looks and more casual attitudes.
Glossy, cute and girly, the smallest Chain Louise blends iconic elegance with ultra-feminine charm. Additional functionality and versatility thanks to a delicate removable chain.

Designed in collaboration with the Japanese designer Hiroshi Fujiwara, the BRAZZA WALLET combines both House heritage - with the Monogram pattern - and modernity with fine details -  two reflective bands and a black one - for a result both sporty and fashion. Its generous size makes it ideal to carry all your cards and receipts while slipping easily in your jacket's pocket.

The iconic Louis Vuitton canvas is the perfect blank page to express the uniqueness of this Masters Collection’s piece of art. Sophisticated and feminine, the Montaigne bag is twisted for the first time with this exclusive collaboration: gold Monogram serti, reflective metallic letters and colored trimmings. An exclusive leather lining embossed, printed and filled with gold tells you more about this unexpected collaboration.

The Saint Michel bag combines two iconic materials - Monogram canvas and Epi leather - in a small, chic shape that is perfect for everyday essentials. The adjustable strap allows it to be carried on the shoulder or across the body, and its flap can be personalized with the owner's initials.

This season the Capucines is reinterpreted with a delicate flower print which also appears on Louis Vuitton shoes and ready-to-wear collection. This animation which reminds the impressionist painting touch, embellishes the Capucines bag in a very feminine way. the elegant bouquets are printed on a timeless black calf leather.

The season’s colorful “travel stickers” theme animates these World Tour fancy accessories: a modern mix of pop imagery and House emblems for an arty, playful charm.The leather backs of the pieces can be hot-stamped with the owner’s initials, for a bag charm or key holder with a personalized touch.

In shiny metallic grey Monogram embossed patent calf leather, this Zippy Wallet gives off an evening feel that will up your fashion quotient. The Zippy is one of our most practical and versatile wallets with numerous compartments and an all-round zip closure.

This colorful stole reinterprets the famous universal bandana pattern to incorporate Louis Vuitton's Monogram flowers. In soft, airy cotton, it is perfect for hot days in the city and can also be worn as a pareo at the beach.

A timeless branded model that offers two belts in one thanks to its reversible option. The iconic LV initials buckle can be associated with Monogram canvas for a more casual look, or with bright red leather for a highly colored silhouette.

The famous Louis Vuitton silk square becomes the expression of the elite collaboration with Jeff Koons , highlighting the exceptional and exclusive craftsmanship. The re-creation of this Masterpiece is featured on a silk twill base embellished with stunning and refined gold embroideries.

Versatile and right on trend, the Double V is made from noble fine-grained leather and iconic Monogram canvas. The round and voluptuous shape of the bag is perfectly contrasted by the bold V-shape flap, making the Double V a unique bag. It can be carried by hand or over the shoulder thanks to the removable strap.
This sleek and elegant clutch with its discreet yet recognizable House signatures is a classic that will bring a dose of glamour to any evening outfit.
Inspired by the handle-fasteners on Louis Vuitton's bags, the Nanogram bracelet features a trompe-l'œil buckle and loop. It is finely engraved with the Monogram pattern.

These supple bracelets reinterpret Louis Vuitton's iconic signatures on small delicate medals, in a tribute to the Maison's history. A perfect gift, they are available in a variety of shapes with different colors ideal to mix and match and accumulate.

This Pochette Voyage is compact, versatile and totally on-trend. It can be slipped into a bag as a travel pouch or hand-carried for a trendier look.

The new Saint Placide chain bag combine Monogram canvas with supple, colored leather, accented by a gleaming golden clasp borrowed from historic House trunks. The perfect size for day-to-night wear, it easily fits a long wallet and other essentials.

The functional adhesive surface, naturally integrated into its slim shape, holds the phone securely to protect it from the bumps and knocks of modern life.

With a range of emoticons inspired by iconic Louis Vuitton symbols, this playful ink pad offers a fun way to express your mood on paper. With its singular nod towards texting culture, it brings writing closer to the digital age. Until 4000 stamps with one refill.

A delicately feminine interpretation of the new Essential V signature, this luminous strass bracelet is ideal to mix and match with other pieces in the line. A perfect gift, it fits any complexion.

The most versatile of wallets, this Zippy in embossed and smooth leather is the epitome of practicality with plenty of room for money, cards and coins. The braided detail in a contrasting color incarnates the House’s couture spirit and adds a stylishly luminous touch.

The printed stripe that cuts across the Damier Graphite coated canvas brings a fun and strong twist to one of our most classical wallets. Large enough to fit your daily essentials, the Brazza slips easily into almost any pocket.

The Junot bag, with its trendy pompom and its young and fresh shape, perfectly suits the code of the Monogram Empreinte line. The feminine Rose Fizzy braided detail underlines Louis Vuitton's Couture spirit and brings a trendy twist to the bold Kaki bag.

Inspired by the African theme of the Spring/Summer 2017 men's show, this soft, airy stole combines Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram with animal motifs created by British artists Jake and Dinos Chapman. A special printing technique is used to produce the refined watercolor effect.

Effortlessly stylish, the Alma PM is one of our iconic designs. Looking marvellously elegant in shiny Monogram Vernis leather, it is still an ideal size for everyday use.

Discreetly woven with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, the Monogramissime tie is a timelessly elegant choice in an array of classic or seasonal colors. A matching pocket square is also available.

The essential business companion, this Enveloppe Carte de Visite in supple Epi leather is ideal for carrying business or credit cards. It fits easily into almost any pocket. Its press-stud closure ensures that your business or credit cards stay safe.

The essential clutch refreshed: the highly feminine shape of the Mira Chain in Monogram Vernis is for women searching for a chic bag with multi-carry options. The delicate chain finishes this highly desirable day-to-evening piece.

Meet your new everyday bag: a zipped messenger besace in Damier Ebene canvas whose thoroughly modern shape and flawless functionality make it completely essential.

Available in a slimmer version, the Historic bracelet in Monogram Canvas is declined in two new hues of pink  as well as in the classic  Monogram canvas. Made to mix, match and stack, these signed pieces are perfect for gifting.

Travel with peace of mind, tracing your luggage in the main worldwide airports with the Louis Vuitton Echo connected device (sold separately).
